\id SIR BURH - Bible en mashi du Congo
\toc3 Burh
\toc2 BurhSira
\toc1 OBURHIMANYA BWA MWENE-SIRA
\mt1 OBURHIMANYA BWA MWENE-SIRA
\iot Enshokolezi
\ip Oburhimanya Mwene-Sira ayigîriza burhenga kuli Nyamuzinda, buyigîriza okukenga Nyamuzinda bunalêrha akalamo kinjà. Eci citabu c’oburhimanya bwa Mwene-Sira cayandikagwa na Yezu, mugala wa Sira (\xt 50, 27\xt*). Omwinjikulu acihugula omu Cigereki erhi ali alama e Mîsiri. Amango ali e Yeruzalemu abona n’amasù gâge kurhi Abayahudi banji bali bamâvuna amarhegeko g’idini erhi bantu bayishig’iyîma omu cihugo câbo bàrhuma.
\ip Nyamuzinda amumolekera mpu ayandike eco citabu lyo Abayahudi barhag’iheza obuyêmêre bwâbo, mpu lyo bashimba Amarhegeko n’enyigîrizo z’oburhimanya bwa kurhenga mîra. Abakengêza akalamo k’Israheli n’ak’abarhegesi bâge lyo abarhwâlihya omu mango g’amalibuko.
\ip Mwene-Sira akengêza ebisômerîne Nyamuzinda ajiraga. Nyamuzinda ajira eciragâne na Nûhu, Abrahamu, Yakôbo, Mûsa, Aroni na Daudi; ciragâne n’olubaga lwîshogwa, ci cinayêrekîre milala miguma miguma, nshôkano ya nsiku nyinji.
\ip Bulya ali mwîrhonzi w’okuli, Mwene-Sira alangâlira oku olubaga lwâge lwarhenga omu bujà. Okurhenga omu bujà lwayîsh’ibà luhembo lwa Nyamuzinda nka lwankashimba amarhegeko gâge.*
\iot EBIRIMWO
\io1 1. Oburhimanya omu kalamo kw’omuntu: cigabi \ior 1, 1—42, 14\ior*\f + \fr 1, 0 \ft Ngasi habulisire omulongo omu LXX, rhuli rhwahazâbûla n’oburhabâle bwa Vulgata (https: / /www.academic-bible.com/en/online-bibles/biblia-sacra-vulgata/read-the-bible-text/bibel/text/lesen/stelle / 43 / 220001 / 229999/ch / 549aad1a89fa5e1a4109a70598f4606e /) na Ebibliya Ntagatîfu, Verbum Bible, Kinshasa, 1992\f*
\io1 2. Oburhimanya en’igulu n’omu ngasi mango: c. \ior 42, 15-25\ior*
\io1 3. Okuyûshûla: c. \ior 51, 1-30\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Akanwa k’omuhinduzi
\p \vp 1\vp* Abandisi b’ecitabu c’Amarhegeko; Abalêbi \vp 2\vp* n’abandi bandisi bali enyuma zâbo bàrhusigîre enyigîrizo nkulu bwenêne ziyêrekîne obumanye n’oburhimanya bw’Israheli. \vp 3\vp* Co cirhumire Israheli akonkwa. \vp 4\vp* Na bulya omuntu akwânîne ayîgîrire n’okusoma, \vp 5\vp* na hano akola ayigîrîre, naye arhondêre okuyigîriza abandi b’embuga, \vp 6\vp* omu nderho n’omu myandiko yâge: \vp 7\vp* naye shakulûza wâni Yezu, erhi abà amâsimika omu kucîyigîriza \vp 8\vp* ecitabu c’Amarhegeko, \vp 9\vp* Abalêbi, \vp 10\vp* n’ebindi bitabu bya bashakulûza, \vp 11\vp* abona akol’âhalûsire kurhali kunyi, \vp 12\vp* arhondêra naye okuyandika binwa biguma-by’okuyigîriza n’okurhimanya, \vp 13\vp* mpu ly’abantu balonza okuyigîrira n’omurhima nkana, banalonzize okushimba aga mahano, \vp 14\vp* babone kurhi balama n’okushimba irhegeko bwinjà. \vp 15\vp* Nkuhûnyirage nâni we musomi, \vp 16\vp* osome eci citabu bwinjà, \vp 17\vp* omanye! olole bwinjà, \vp 18\vp* onabè wa lukogo \vp 19\vp* aha wakabona \vp 20\vp* ntamanyir’ihindula olulimi omu lundi, ciru akabà mpu ncîsêzize. \vp 21\vp* Kuli kuderha oku birhagenda kuguma, \vp 22\vp* ebinwa byarhanzir’iderhwa omu cihabraniya, ntâko wakabiderha omu lundi lulimi; \vp 23\vp* ciru, \vp 24\vp* n’erhi wankalola ecitabu c’Irhegeko oku ciri, Abalêbi, \vp 25\vp* n’ebi­ndi bitabu; \vp 26\vp* erhi bihindulwa omu lindi iderha birhaciyumananaga lwoshi lwoshi n’iderha lirhanzi-rhanzi. \vp 27\vp* Omu mwâka gwa makumi asharhu na munâni, nyakufà mwâmi Yergeti ali oku ntebe, \vp 28\vp* najà e Mîsiri, n’oku ndi eyo, \vp 29\vp* narhimâna ecitabu cirimwo enyigîrizo nkulu bwenêne. \vp 30\vp* nâni nacîsêza, nacîshwêkerera n’emisî yoshi nti kuhika mpindule eci citabu. \vp 31\vp* Nacîsêzize obudufu n’omûshi haguma n’obulenga bwoshi, \vp 32\vp* ago mango nti \vp 33\vp* lyo nyukiriza omukolo nanguyêrekane, \vp 34\vp* nti abandi nabo, balya bali kuli, ihanga, banalonzize okucîyigîriza, \vp 35\vp* babone kurhi bayinjihya engeso zâbo, banalame nk’oku Irhegeko linarhegesire.
\cp 1
\ms1 I. Ebiderhwa biluga
\s1 lhwe ly’oburhimanya
\p 
\v 1 Oburhimanya bwoshi emwa Nyamuzinda burhenga\f + \fr 1, 1 \ft Olwîko lw’omuzî gw’oburhimanya ndi ogumanyire, Nyamuzinda yêne oyishi ebyâge, yênène onabimanyisa abalonzize: lolà \xt Ayu 28, 12-28\xt*\ft .\f* hôfi naye bubà ensiku n’amango.
\v 2 Ndi wankahasha okuganja omushenyi gw’enyanja, emirhônyi y’enkuba erhi ensiku zibà ensiku n’amango?
\v 3 Ndi okola ohisire aha amalunga gahekera, ndi oyishi obugali bw’igulu, nîsi ndi okola ojirisâgarha aha okuzimu kuhekîre?
\v 4 Oburhimanya bwalemirwe embere lya byoshi, obukengêre-burhimanya burhali bwa mango n’ene.
\v 5 Enshôko y’obushinganyanya, kabà kanwa ka Nnâmahanga omu mpingu; n’enjira zâge go marhegeko g’ensiku n’amango.
\v 6 Ndi wafululîrwe ecisiki c’obumanye? Obuhirhi bwâge ndi obumanyire?
\v 7 Ndi bafulûlîre obumanye bw’obushinganyanya? N’obuhirhi bw’enjira zâge, ndi obumanyire?
\v 8 Omurhimanya anali muguma, ali na wa kuyôbohwa nk’atamîre oku ntebe yâge.
\v 9 Nyamuzinda ly’izîno lyâge, ye walemaga oburhimanya, àbulola anabukereka, àbugabanya emikolo yâge yoshi,
\v 10 àbuhira omu ngasi ciremwa nk’oku analonzize, àbugabira abantu bamuzigira.
\p 
\v 11 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda\f + \fr 1, 11 \ft Okurhînya Nyamuzinda kurhali kurhînya kwa bwôba, ntemu ya kumuyâka, ci kurhînya kwa bukenge, kula omuntu arhînya ababusi bâge, erhi nnawâbo n’obwo abazigire, bulya ahâli nku­lwe, harhakulwa. \f* kuli kulimba kuli na kuj’irenge, buli bushagaluke eri na nsirha ya busîme.
\v 12 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda kushagalusa omurhima, kusîmîse omuntu amwemwerhwe, kunamuhè akalamo karhali kanyi.
\v 13 Omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, obuzinda bwâge murhûla, olusiku lw’okufà kwâge mugisho,
\v 14 Omurhondêro gw’oburhimanya kuli kurhînya Nyamuzinda; oburhimanya bwalemirwe n’abemêzi, buli nabo kurhenga omu nda ya bannina.
\v 15 Oburhimanya bwayûbasire ekarhî k’abantu, bwagwika eciriba c’ensiku n’amango, bwanacishwekera oku bûko bw’abantu.
\v 16 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda bwo bushwinjiro bw’oburhimanya, bujira n’amalehe galalusà abantu.
\v 17 Bunahire obugale omu nyumpa zâbo, n’enguli zâbo buzibumbe muhako.
\v 18 Obushwinjiro bw’oburhimanya kuli kurhînya Nyamuzinda, kunahâne omurhûla n’amagala.
\v 19 Nyamuzinda abwîne, abubwîne anabukereka, adubula obumanye n’obukengêre, àlengeza irenge ly’abarhimanya.
\v 20 Omuzî gw’oburhimanya, kurhînya Nyamuzinda, ebibabi byâbwo kalamo kanene.
\v 21 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda kunarhenze ebyâha, omuntu ocîhangâna muli okwo, anacikûlekwo oburhè bwa Nyamuzinda.
\v 22 Amagene g’omubî garhamuha lubanja, obuzirho bwâgo ekuzimu buhêka.
\v 23 Omuntu w’omurhima gurhulwîre kulinda alinda amango, n’erhi gayisha gubè mwishingo.
\v 24 Arhabadukira omu binwa, n’abandi banabone oku ali wa bukengêre.
\s1 Oburhimanya n’obwimâna
\p 
\v 25 Omu cibîkiro c’oburhimanya mubà bizibu binji by’obumanye, ci omunya-byâha arhakwirirwa obukunda-Lulema.
\v 26 K’ohubîre oburhimanya? Shimba amarhegeko, Nyamuzinda akushobôza-bwo.
\v 27 Bulya okurhînya Nyamuzinda buli burhimanya zinali nyigîrizo, eci Nyamuzinda azigira bwikubagirwa n’obutûdu.
\v 28 Orhabâga ntumwa omu biyêrekîre okurhînya Nyamuzinda, n’omu kukulikira okurhînya Nyamuzinda, orhabâga wa mirhima ihiri.
\v 29 Orhabâga ndyâlya omu masù g’igulu, onalange akanwa kâwe.
\v 30 Orhacîhiraga enyanya, bulya warhoga, enshonyi zikugwârhe, bulya Nyamuzinda anakajalûla ebikuli emurhima, omu karhî k’endêko, akushenye oku idaho, Ntyo kumanyîkane oku orharhînya Nyamuzinda, n’oku omurhima gwâwe guyunjwîre bulyâlya\f + \fr 1, 30 \ft nâni nacîsêza, nacîshwêkerera n’emisî yoshi nti kuhika mpindule eci citabu, kuli kuderha oku ecitabu c’Oburhimanya càli ciyandike omu cihebraniya, hali abaderha oku babwîne ehisharhi hya kulico omu cihebraniya aha Masada, hôfi n’Enyanja y’Omunyu.\f*.
\c 2
\s1 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda omu malibuko
\p 
\v 1 Mwâna wâmi, okacîhambira okukolera Nyamuzinda, ocîrheganye n’oku malibuko.
\v 2 Bà n’omurhima gushingânîne, obè na ntwâli, orhazigaga bakuhabula amango g’amalibuko.
\v 3 Omusêremwo, orhamujâga kuli, ly’okuzibwa omu lusiku luzinda.
\v 4 Ngasi ebi akurhumire, obiyankirire, omu buzamba bwâwe, okazibirembera,
\v 5 bulya amasholo muliro bagarhangulamwo, n’abashinganyanya omu cibêye c’obwîrhôhye barhangulirwa.
\v 6 Langâlira Nyamuzinda, akurhabâla, jà n’obulangâlire omu njira ekubûsire.
\v 7 Mwe murhînya Nyamuzinda, mulangâlire obwonjo bwâge, murharhengaga omu njira yâge lyo mulekihirima.
\v 8 Mwe murhînya Nyamuzinda mumulangâlire n’oluhembo lwinyu lurharhêreke.
\v 9 Mwe murhînya Nyamuzinda, mulangâlire aminjà gâge, mulangâlire obusîme bw’ensiku n’amango n’obwonjo bwâge.
\v 10 Mulole amâburhwa ga mîra, mubone: Ndi mwayumvîrhe olangâlîre Nyamuzinda agalibulabula? Erhi ndi mwayumvîrhe amusêzirekwo, Nyamuzinda agalimurhiba? Erhi ndi wamulakire, abula kumuyumva?
\v 11 Nyamuzinda arhahimwa lukogo, abâ wa bwonjo, anakûle ebyâha, acize n’amango g’amalibuko.
\v 12 Buhanya bw’ab’emirhima myôba, n’ab’amaboko gahozire, buhanya bw’omunya-byâha w’olugendo lw’okurhebana.
\v 13 Buhanya bw’omuntu w’omurhima mwôlo n’orhajira buyêmêre, bulyâla arhakabona câfungira.
\v 14 Buhanya bwinyu mwe mwarhibire omurhima, kurhi mwajira amango Nyamuzinda ayishimmurhangula?
\v 15 Abarhînya Nyamuzinda barhavuna omu kanwa kâge, njira yâge abamuzigira bakulikira.
\v 16 Abarhînya Nyamuzinda balonza okumusîmîsa, amarhegeko\f + \fr 2, 16 \ft Amarhegeko: omuntu ozigira Nyamuzinda arharhama acîdôsa mpu kàshimba irhegeko lirebe erhi nanga, bulya okuzigira Nyamuzinda n’okumuyumva byo biguma.\f* gâge lubà lûma lw’abamuzigira.
\v 17 Abarhînya Nyamuzinda, omurhima gwâbo yêne guyôrha gulinga, banayîsh’icîrhohya omu masù gâge.
\v 18 Rhuyâkire omu maboko ga Nyamuzinda, ahâli h’okucîkweba omu g’abantu, oku obukulu bwâge buli kwo n’obwonjo bwâge buli.
\c 3
\s1 Sho na Nyoko
\p 
\v 1 Bâna bâni, munyumve, nie sho, mushimbe oku mmubwizire, mwacira.
\v 2 Nyamuzinda nk’ahà omushamuka irenge, anamuhè abâna, yenazibuhya obuhashe bw’omuzîre omu bagala.
\v 3 Omwâna okenga îshe erhi mwenda alyuzire,
\v 4 omwâna okuza nnina erhi buhirhi abîsire.
\v 5 Okenga îshe, naye âbona obusîme omu bâge bâna, olusiku lw’okushenga, Nyamuzinda ayumva omusengero gwâge.
\v 6 Okuza îshe, âbona akalamo k’ensiku n’ensiku, osîmîsa nnina erhi Nyamuzinda akenzire.
\v 7 Ababusi bâge kw’abakolera nk’owakolera Nyakasane.
\v 8 Okenge sho omu bijiro n’omu nderho zâwe, wabona oku omugisho gwâge gwakuhikako.
\v 9 Obwangà bw’omushamuka kuyûbaka buyûbakira abâna bâge, enfûlago ya nnina wa muntu yôhe kushâba eshâba.
\v 10 Sho akabîha, orhacîshingaga, bulya nt’irenge warhenza omu bubî bwa sho.
\v 11 Irenge ly’îshe wa muntu erhi ry’omuntu yêne, nnina wa muntu akashekerwa erhi omuntu yêne oshekîrwe.
\v 12 Mwâna wâni, rhabâla sho omu bushosi bwâge, orhamujiraga burhè amango acizîne.
\v 13 Ciru obukengêre bwâge bwakazambaha, obè n’omurhima gw’olukogo, orhamugayaguzagya w’eciri musole.
\v 14 Aminjà wâjirire sho garhakayibagirwa, garhuma wabona ciru n’obwonjo oku byâha byâwe.
\v 15 Nyamuzinda âkukengêra olusiku lw’amalibuko, ebyâha byâwe kwo byâhirigirha kul’olubula lujonga oku izûba.
\v 16 Kw’ali nk’ojâcîre Nyamuzinda omwâna oyîbagîre îshe, n’ôjira nnina mungo, ali mwâna wahehêrîrwe emwa Nyakasane.
\s1 Obwîrhôhye
\p 
\v 17 Mwâna wâni, okole n’obutûdu omukolo gwâwe, wârhona kulusha omurhonyi.
\v 18 Oku obukulu bwâwe buli, kwo n’obwîrhôhye\f + \fr 3, 18 \ft Ly’arhona emwa Nyamuzinda: omukulu walonza okusîmîsa Nyamuzinda abè mwîrhôhye, amanye endalwè y’obukulu: lolà \xt Mat 20, 26-28\xt*\ft .\f* bwâwe bunabâge, ly’orhona emwa Nyamuzinda.
\v 19 Abantu b’obucîbone n’abany’irenge bali banji, cikwône abîrhôhye bwo amanyîsa amahwe gâge.
\v 20 Bulya Nyamuzinda abà mukulu, ci bîrhôhye bamuharâmya.
\v 21 Orhakâgicîhambira ebi orhagale, orhasingirizagya ebikulushire misî.
\v 22 Akanwa wabwîzirwe, okasêzeko omurhima, ebiciri mahwe byôhe, orhacîrhamagya mpu wabisâgarha.
\v 23 Orhacîrhamagya n’ebilushire obukengêre bwâwe, ciru ebi wayigîrizibwe bikola binji oku bukengêre bw’omuntu.
\v 24 Bantu banji bahabusire n’obucîbone, okucîkunga kwâbo kwabahabula enkengêro.
\s1 Obucîbone
\p 
\v 25 Okubula emmonyi kwo na kubula obulangashane, okabula obumanye, orhacîshomagya mpu wayigîriza.
\v 26 Murhima-arhumva buhanya afâna, n’osîma entambala arhayihumba\f + \fr 3, 26 \ft Kunazâze ebyâha: ojira bwinjà bundi ajirwa, omuntu ojirira owâbo aminjà Nyamuzinda orhumire, naye Nyamuzinda amubabalira, lolà \xt 1 Pet 4, 8\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 27 Murhima-arhumva arhahwa burhè, n’osîma ebyâha bindi abona.
\v 28 Obuhanya bwa cibone burhabukwa, bulyâl’obubî bwamumezizemwo emizî.
\v 29 Omuntu mwenge emurhima adôkeza omugani, n’okubwîra owayumva, kw’omuntu murhimanya acîfinja. Okurhabâla ab’obuligo
\v 30 Amîshi ganazimye engulumira, n’okuhà ow’obuligo Kunazâze ebyâha.
\v 31 Kujira-bwinjà ali mubîsi, olusiku abâ buligo, arhâbule carhabâla.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Mwâna wâni, orhayîmaga omukenyi ehyamubîka, orhalungumarhazagya abâli buligo.
\v 2 Orhalibuzagya omushalye, ow’obuligo orhahîraga okamulîsa n’amagala.
\v 3 Orharhindibuzagya owarhindibusire, orhalegerezagya n’omukenyi olikuhûna.
\v 4 Orhakumîraga omukenyi orhindibwîre, orhakengulaga omukenyi.
\v 5 Orhakengulaga omuntu olagîrîre, omanye irhondo orharhumaga bakusigira enfûlago.
\v 6 Bulya erhi omuntu olagîrîre akakusigira enfûlago omu bulagîrire bwâge, Nyamuzinda wamulemaga anamuyumva.
\v 7 Obè musîmwa eka, okazikenga abakulu.
\v 8 Orhege omukenyi okurhwiri, akakulamusa, nâwe omulamuse n’obutûdu.
\v 9 Ofungire oyu badwîrhe barhindibuza, orhabâga mwôba nka watwa olubanja.
\v 10 Obè îshe w’enfûzi, orhabâle abakana. Ntyo wâbà nka mwene Ow’Enyanya, akusîma kulusha oku nyoko akusîma.
\s1 Oburhimanya kulera bulera
\p 
\v 11 Oburhimanya bunalere abâna bâbwo\f + \fr 4, 11 \ft Ababulonza: Oburhimanya budesirwe nka muntu, lolà \xt Mig 1, 25; 8, 12; Luk 7, 35\xt*\ft .\f*, bushîbirire ababulonza.
\v 12 Omuntu ozigira oburhimanya erhi buzîne azigîre, abantu babukulikira kurhenga sêzi, bayumva obusîme.
\v 13 Owabuhisirekwo, ayîma omu irenge, ngasi hantu akaja, ajâne n’omugisho gwa Nyamuzinda.
\v 14 Abakolera oburhimanya, Nyamuzinda bakolera, n’ababusîma, basîmwa naye.
\v 15 Omuntu oyumva izù ly’oburhimanya, bwinjà atwa olubanja, omwîra wâbwo agwêrhe eciyimangîre.
\v 16 Ocîkubagira oburhimanya kushobôla abushobôlako, n’iburha lyâge libuyimemwo.
\v 17 Kulya kubà bwàmârhangimuhêka omu njira y’ebinzongonzongo, bumuyôbohye yêshi ashukume, bumulibuze, bumukome yêshi, kuhika abè wa kucîkubagirwa, yêshi akangavuke,
\v 18 buzinda, bumugalule obwo, bumushubize omu njira ekubllsire, bumumanyîse amahwe gâbwo.
\v 19 Omuntu akacîkenyagula, bunamurhibe, bumuleke agende lwâge.
\s1 Hali enshonyi n’enshonyi
\p 
\v 20 Mwâna wâni, lolà eburhambi n’obundi, ocîzibuke amabî, orhacîgayaga kulya kw’obuho.
\v 21 Bulya hali enshonyi ziheka omuntu omu câha, hali n’enshonyi ziri irenge n’inêma.
\v 22 Orhabâga mukali kuli we wêne okurhalusire, oleke n’okubà nshonyi kwarhuma wacîheza.
\v 23 Orhamîraga akanwa kankaciza, orhafulikaga oburhimanya bwâwe.
\v 24 Bulya binwa bimanyîsa oburhimanya, n’ekanwa yo erhenga ihano.
\v 25 Orhaderhaga okurhali, ci oyumve enshonyi z’okubà muhwinja.
\v 26 Orhabâga nshonyi z’okuyêmêra ecâha câwe, orhahîraga okaheka muhûsi gw’olwîshi kwo ebikanyâli.
\v 27 Orhacîrhegega omusirhe, orhahîraga okazimbira omugale olubanja.
\v 28 Olwîre obushinganyanya kuhika okufà, nâwe Nyakasane Nyamuzinda akulwira.
\v 29 Orhabâga ntwâli omu binwa, ogalibà mwôlo na mwôba omu bijiro.
\v 30 Orhabâga nka ntale omu mwâwe ogalibii mwôba embere za bambali bâwe.
\v 31 Okuboko kwâwe kurhabiduhiraga okuhâbwa, kukanazidohera okugalula.
\c 5
\s1 Obuhirhi n’obucîbone
\p 
\v 1 Orhacîkubagiraga obuhirhi\x - \xo 5, 1 \xta Lolà \xt 11, 24; Luk 12, 15-21.\x*, orhaderhaga, erhi: «Nalamirako ebi».
\v 2 Orhayêmêraga enyifinjo n’emisî yâwe yakuhêka omu magene g’omurhima.
\v 3 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Ndi wampasha?», bulya Nyamuzinda arhâbule kwàkuhana.
\v 4 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Ci nabwîne najira ecâha, kurhigi nabîre?», bulya Nyamuzinda ayishivumbika gwahalâla.
\v 5 Orhacîkubagiraga okubabalirwa, olinde oyûshûla ebyâha oku bindi.
\v 6 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Nyamuzinda arhahimwa bwonjo, k’arhambabalira?» bulya nêci ali wa bwonjo, ci ye lumbikunira, n’obukunizi bwâge kurhibuka burhibukira abanya-byâha.
\v 7 Orharhindiraga bwashubirira Nyakasane, orhalindaga ensiku zacikonya, bulyâla oburhè bwâge ye cirhibuka, wakabona wamagenda omu nsanya olusiku lw’obuhane.
\v 8 Orhacîkubagiraga ebirugu bizimbano, birhakucize hano obuhanya buyisha.
\s1 Ogwârhe obuzibu onasimike
\p 
\v 9 Orhakâgiyêrûlira ngasi mpûsi, orhakulikiraga ngasi njira, (omunya-byâha w’enderhera-habiri yeki ojira ntyo).
\v 10 osêze buzibu ebikuli emurhima, obè na kanwa kaguma.
\v 11 Obè mumvîrhiza mubidu, ci orhabâga wa kuhalabuka omu kushuza.
\v 12 Akabà omanyire eci washuza, oshuze owinyu, ci âkaba nanga, obumbe akanwa.
\v 13 Ekanwa erhenga obukuze, erhenge n’enshonyi, n’olulimi lunayîse nnalwo.
\v 14 Oleke okujà kwaderha abandi, orhabâga murhimbuzi wa kalimi, bulya oku enshonyi zigwârha omushambo, kwo n’obuhane bugwârha endyâlya.
\v 15 Omu hinene n’omu hinyi ocîlange oku byâha, orhahindukaga mushombanyi n’obwo wali mwîra.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Bulya okuderhwa kubî n’olubaga lwoshi, ziri nshonyi bwenêne, kw’ali ntyo omunya-byâha w’enderha-kubirhi.
\v 2 Orhacîrekêreraga ebwa murhima gw’amagene, gwakanakuyâgaza nka mpanzi nkali,
\v 3 erhi gukuyône, gukunînibuze gurhakusigire ehishulo, obone wamacibêra karhî-kumu.
\v 4 Murhima guli magene, lushilmyo oku muntu, gunarhume abashombanyi bâwe bakushekera.
\s1 Obwîra
\p 
\v 5 Akanwa kinjà kanalêrhere omuntu bîra banji, oluderho lw’obutûdu lunarhume omuntu ashuzibwa bwinjà.
\v 6 Okômere bantu banji, ci nka muhanûzi walonza, orhôle muguma omu cihumbi.
\v 7 Nka walonza omwîra, orhangimurhangula, orhayirukiraga wâmubwîra amahwe gâwe.
\v 8 Bulya omwîra w’ebijingo, anakurhibemwo sêzi ehibanja hikujakwo.
\v 9 Mwîra-ngwêrhe anahinduke mushombanyi-ngwêrhe, akubere enda, enshonyi zikugwârhe.
\v 10 Mwîra-ngwêrhe, analire oku mêza gâwe, hano ohanyagala, akuyâke.
\v 11 Amango ogwêrhe, we ye aha mwâwe erhi aha mwâge,
\v 12 lindag’okene, obè mubisha omu babisha, akuyâke wakanamulola omu masù.
\v 13 Ocîzibuke abashombanyi bâwe, ci omanye n’abîra bâwe.
\v 14 Burhabâle bunene, omwîra nkana, okumubona kuli kuhirhira.
\v 15 Omwîra nkana arhagulwa, ntâye wankabona ebi amugula.
\v 16 Mavurha ga buzîne, omwîra mwinjà, abarhînya Nyamuzinda bône bamubona.
\v 17 Omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, alonza abîra binjà, bulya oku omuntu ali kw’anayinjibana.
\s1 Okuyiga oburhimanya
\p 
\v 18 Mwâna wâni, kurhenga eburhò bwâwe, osîme okucîyigîriza, kuhika obè wa mvi, wabona oburhimanya.
\v 19 Kul’omuhinzi n’omurhwêzi banajira, nâwe oshîbirire oburhimanya, olingûze oku bwayêra, warhama nsiku nsungunu z’okuhinga, ci amango g’okusârûla, wâyumva osîmire.
\v 20 Kurhamya barhamya abahwinja, ecingolongolo cirhabukwirirwa.
\v 21 Kuzidoha buzidohera nk’ibuye lizirho, arhimangibukabulira.
\v 22 Bulya nêci ihano likwânîne izîno lyâlyo, lirhabona ngasi ye.
\v 23 Yumva, mwâna wâni, enkengêro zâni, orhalahiraga ihano lyâni,
\v 24 Oyêmêre emigozi y’oburhimanya ekushwêke amagulu, n’empogo yabwo ekuje omu igosi.
\v 25 Oburhege ecirhugo buzidoherekwo, orhacîdirhibulaga mpu bwakushwêka.
\v 26 Obujè hôfi n’omurhima gwoshi, ojè omu njira yabwo n’emisî yoshi.
\v 27 Okulikire amashando gâbwo, obulongereze, wâbona oku bwacimanyîsa, orhacihulikaga hano obuhikakwo.
\v 28 Bulya aha buzinda wâburhamukiramwo, gubè mwishingo gwâwe.
\v 29 Eyàli migozi eshube mpenzi, n’ezàli mpogo gabè magerha ga mulimbo.
\v 30 Ogwali muzigo gw’obujà gubè mwambalo gw’irenge, eyàli migozi ya kushweka zibè nnigi za mulimbo.
\v 31 Okubundi oburhimanya obuyambale nka mwambalo gwa lusiku lukulu, ohwinje bwinjà, obuyambale buny’ishungwè ly’ebwâmi.
\v 32 Mwâna wâni, erhi wankalonza wanacîyîgîriza, n’obutûdu bwâwe bwakuhisa oku bukengêre.
\v 33 Wâyiga akabà osîma okuyumvîrhiza, akabà oyishirhega amarhwîri, wâbà murhimanya.
\v 34 Osîme okujà ah’abashosi bali, n’okabona omurhimanya, omukomekwo obwîra.
\v 35 Oyumvîrhize ngasi kanwa karhengako Nyamuzinda, emigani mizibu erhakufumaga.
\v 36 Mang’okabona omuntu murhimanya, onalamukire aha burhambi bwâge, amagulu gâwe gamutwire ec’olusò.
\v 37 Amarhegeko ga Nyamuzinda okazigagerêreza, okazigashîbirira bwaca bwayira. Ye wakuzibuhya omurhima, n’oburhimanya odwîrhe wacîfinja wâbushobôla.
\c 7
\s1 Amahano ga ngasi lubero
\p 
\v 1 Oleke okujira amabî, n’amabî garhakuyâlule;
\v 2 oyâke obulyâlya, n’obulyâlya bwâkuyâka.
\v 3 Mwâna wâni, oleke okurhwêra omu mpinga y’obulyâlya, ly’olek’isârûla akal’ibala.
\v 4 Orhasengeraga Nyamuzinda entebe ya burhanzi, orhahûnaga na mwâmi ecikono c’irenge.
\v 5 Orhacîkungaga mushinganyanya embere za Nyamuzinda, n’embere za mwâmi orhahimhaga amarhimanya.
\v 6 Mwâna wâni, orhahambiraga omukolo gw’obucîranuzi akabà orhankahashimanyula obulyâlya, bulya omugale anakuhira olunda lwâge, obone wamabà ndyâlya nâwe.
\v 7 Orhacîshûbulaga omu ndêko y’olugo, orhabâga wa busha embere z’olubaga.
\v 8 Orhayêmêraga bakukulula kabiri mpu ojire amabî, bulya n’eliguma orhalifume.
\v 9 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Ka Nyamuzinda arhâlola entûlo zâni, erhi k’arhâziyankirire hano nzirhûla emund’ali».
\v 10 Nka washenga oleke okucîdirhibula, orhalekaga n’okuhâna entûlo y’omukenyi.
\v 11 Oleke okushekera omuntu ohanyagîre, bulya hali amango ôwamuhebagakwo\f + \fr 7, 11 \ft Owamuhebagakwo: hali amango Nyamuzinda arhangula omuntu n’amalibuko, lolà Ayubu.\f* obwo buhanya ankacimuzûsa.
\v 12 Orhakazâgisingira mwene winyu obunywesi, n’omwîra wâwe kwo n’okwo.
\v 13 Omanye okunywerha, bulya ntà minjà garhengamwo.
\v 14 Orhabâga muvôle omu ndêko y’abashosi, oleke n’orhunwa rhunji-rhunji omu masâla.
\v 15 Orhayâkaga emikolo mizibu, ciru n’omukolo gw’enfuka, bulya Ow’Enyanya ye wagujiraga.
\v 16 Orhacîhiraga oku lukere lw’abanya-byâha, omanye oku obukunizi burhâlegame
\v 17 Obè mwîrhohye bwenêne, bulya omuliro n’emivunyu bwo buhane bw’enkola-maligo.
\v 18 Omanye omwîra wankamugera ebirugu, nîsi erhi mwene winyu omugere amasholo g’e Yofiri.
\v 19 Omukazi nkana na murhimanya, orhahîra okamushomba, obwinjà bwâge bulushire amasholo cicîro.
\v 20 Oleke okurhindibuza omujà okozire bwinjà, nîsi erhi mwambali wâwe ocîhanganyire.
\v 21 Ozigire omujà\f + \fr 7, 21 \ft Obuhuru bwâge: omujà ocîkenzire akwânîne alolwe nk’abandi bantu, ahabwe okubà ntagengwa kwâge nk’akola amanyire obuhuru co cici. Lolà Filemoni.\f* w’obukengêre nk’oku ocîzigira wêne, orhabulaga bwacîmwirikira.
\s1 Abâna
\p 
\v 22 K’ojira amasò\f + \fr 7, 22 \ft Amasò: masô ga bintu, nkâfu, bihuzi…\f*? Ogashibirire; akabà galimwo obunguke, ogalange bwinjà.
\v 23 K’ojira abâna? Obalere bwinjà, obagombye kurheng’eburhò bwâbo.
\v 24 K’ojira abanyere? Obashîbirire omubiri bwinjà, ci kwône obayêreke obusù bukali.
\v 25 Oyâluse mwâli wâwe, kuli kwinjà bwenêne, ci omuhè omulume mwinjà.
\v 26 Ka mukazi nkana ojira? Omanye wankamuhulusa, n’akabà oyu ogwêrhe arhali ye, orhacîkubagiraga-ye.
\s1 Ababusi
\p 
\v 27 Okenge sho n’omurhima gwoshi, n’amalibuko nyoko\f + \fr 7, 27 \ft Nyoko àbwîne: okenge sho na nyoko, liri irhegeko lya Nyamuzinda, lolà \xt Murh 20, 12\xt*\ft … okukengêra amalibuko nyoko abwîne we rhumire kurhume kandi wamukenga kulusha.\f* abwîne orhahîra okagayîbagira.
\v 28 Gerêreza oku bo bakuburhaga: mbwîraga bici wabagalulire oku minjà bàkujirire?
\s1 Abadâhwa
\p 
\v 29 Orhînye Nyamuzinda n’omûka gwâwe gwoshi, okenge n’abadâhwa bâge\f + \fr 7, 29 \ft omûka: iroho, buzîne: abadâhwa bâge: omudâhwa akwânîne olukengwa bulya ali murhumisi wa Nnâmahanga, lolà «omuganda akengerwa nnawâbo».\f*.
\v 30 Owakulemaga omuzigire n’emisî yâwe yoshi, n’abarhumisi bâge orhabahabaga.
\v 31 Orhînye Nyamuzinda, okenge n’omudâhwa, omuhè omwanya gwâge bamutwîrîre: omwâka muhyâhya, enterekêro y’okucîyunjuza, entûlo y’oluziha, enterekêro y’okushukûlwa, n’ebirhanzi n’ebitagatîfu.
\s1 Abakenyi n’abahanyagîre
\p 
\v 32 Olambûle enfune, ohè omukenyi, ly’obona omugisho mwimâna.
\v 33 Ohè ngasi oyîsa omûka, ciru n’abafîre nabo orhabayîbagiraga\f + \fr 7, 33 \ft Okukuza abafîre: abafîre bacikwânîne okukengwa bulya bali muli Nyamuzinda, lolà \xt Tob 1, 17; 12, 12\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 34 Orhayâkag’abadwîrhe balaka, ofè mungo gw’abalaka.
\v 35 Orhayôbohaga okushîbirira abalwâla, okwo kwarhuma nâwe wâsîmwa.
\v 36 Omu bijiro byâwe byoshi, kengêra obuzinda bwâwe, na ntyo wayâka ebyâha.
\c 8
\s1 Okucîrhonda n’okugerêreza
\p 
\v 1 Orhalwîsagya omukulu, bulya akanakulagîriza.
\v 2 Orhalwâga mwe n’omugale, bulya ankakuhima kuhonga: omanye oku amasholo gahezize banji, galembya ciru n’omurhima gw’abâmi.
\v 3 Orhajâga kadali mwe na kadegende, kuli kuhira enshâli oku cîko.
\v 4 Orhajiraga obuzâla mwe n’omuntu walezirwe kubî, bulya yêhe anajâcira na bashakulûza b’omuntu.
\v 5 Orhakalihiraga omunya-byâha ocîyunjuzize, kengêra oku rhweshi rhwabîhire.
\v 6 Orhagayaguzagya omushosi, bulya nîrhu rhwankacishosihala.
\v 7 Orhacîshingiraga okufà kw’owundi, kengêra oku olufù luli lwîrhu rhweshi.
\s1 Okw’abakulûkulu
\p 
\v 8 Orhagayaguzagya akanwa k’abakulûkulu, kanji-kanji ogaluke omu binwa byâbo, bulya bo bakuyigîriza oyîgîrire, omanye n’obulenga abantu bashigamo.
\v 9 Orhakengulaga ebinwa by’abashosi, bulya bo barhanziriyîgira oku babusi bâbo, bo wâyîgirakwo okucîrhonda, n’obulenga bw’okushuza nka mugula.
\s1 Okucîrhonda
\p 
\v 10 Orhakolêzagya enshâli z’omunya-byâha, bulya engulumira y’omuliro gwâge yakuyôca.
\v 11 Omanye obukali bw’owundi muntu bwakakuhabîsa, gwakanabà murhego gwarhuma walogorha.
\v 12 Orhahâga omuntu okulenzire misî akantu mpu wamuhoza, n’okamuhoza oderhe oku wanahezirwe. 7. 36: Wayâka ebyâha: oyôrhe oli mwinjà ngasi lusiku ly’ôbà n’iragi ly’okuhà mwinjà olusiku luzinda.
\v 13 Orhayîmangiraga owâlya omwenda gukulenzire buli, okamuyîmangira onacîrheganyagye n’okulyûla.
\v 14 Orhajâga lubanja mwe n’omucîranuzi, bulya hano balutwa, ye baluhà.
\v 15 Orhabalamaga mwe n’ecishungu, bulya akuhêka olunda orhîshi: okw’ali kw’anagenda, arhabwîrwa: isirhe lyâge lyânakuyîrhira omu mpinga mwe naye.
\v 16 Orhajâga kadali mwe n’omuntu okunira duba, orhanageraga mwe naye aharhabà nyumpa, bulya akômerîre okubulaga omukò.
\v 17 Ihwe lyâwe orhalibwîraga encinganyi, bulyâla cirhakamanyibîka ihwe lyâwe.
\v 18 Ecijiro c’okuyôrha ciri mahwe-mahwe, orhacikolaga embere z’ow’e­mbuga, bulyâla orhamanyiri bici akakusingira.
\v 19 Orhabohôleraga ngasi yêshi omurhima gwâwe, orhacîkebagwa n’iduba mpu akola wâwe.
\c 9
\s1 Abakazi
\p 
\v 1 Orhayâgalagwa na mukâwe, orhamuhâga enkengêro z’okukujirira kubî.
\v 2 Orhacîhânaga emw’omukazi, wakanabona yekola okukulîre.
\v 3 Orhashimbaga omukazi w’ecishungu, wakanagwa omu mirhego yâge\f + \fr 9, 3 \ft 9, 3: Emirhego yâge: lolà \xt Mig 7, 6-27; 23, 27; 29, 3\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 4 Orhakômeraga omukazi mwîmbiza, wakanagwârhwa omu menge gâge.
\v 5 Orhasingirizagya omunyere, wankanahanirwa haguma naye.
\v 6 Orhacîhiraga omu nfune z’embaraga, yakanakuyûsa ebirugu.
\v 7 Orhasingirizagya hoshi-hoshi omu lugo, orhakômeraga n’enjira zàhàmbire.
\v 8 Omuhya mwinjà, orhahîra okamukonolera amasù, orhanahîraga okasingiriza mukà bêne. Banji barhebirwe n’iranga ly’omukazi, amagene gâbo gayâka nka muliro.
\v 9 Oleke amazâla haguma n’omukazi ogwêrhe omu mwâge, omurhima gwâwe gwankanahya n’obwinjà bwâge, obone amagene gamakuhira ecîko.
\s1 Oku omuntu ayôrha omu bandi
\p 
\v 10 Orhalekaga omwîra wa mîra, omuhyâhya arhamulushe. Omwîra muhyâhya, mavu ga cibabe, linda gahole ly’oganywa bwinjà.
\v 11 Orhayâgalagwa n’okubêrwa kw’omubî, orhamanyiri obuzinda bwâge.
\v 12 Orhakungaga okubêrwa kw’ababî, kengêra oku barhabule bwahanirwa hano igulu.
\v 13 Oyâkire ogwêrhe obuhashe bw’oukuyirha abantu kulî, ntyo ecôbà c’olufù cakurhengamwo. N’erhi wankamuyêgêra, omulâbe bwinjà, omanye akurhenzamwo omûka. Omanye bwinjà oku emirhego ekuzonzire, n’oku elugerêro oli.
\v 14 Okômerane mwe n’omulungu wâwe nk’oku onahashire, onakazidôsa abagula ihano.
\v 15 Olonze okukâshambâla mweshi n’abantu nkana, n’enshambâlo yâwe eyêrekere irhegeko ly’Ow’Enyanya.
\v 16 Abashinganyanya babè bo bîra mulîra haguma, orhanalimbiraga okurhali kurhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 17 Bushanja bwa mulenga bukengwa, yêhe muntu okulîre olubaga akwânîne abè mulenga omu binwa.
\v 18 Kishiderha kuyôbohwa ayôbohwa eka, na kadegende arhabonwakwo.
\c 10
\s1 Abarhegesi
\p 
\v 1 Omurhegesi murhimanya kulanga alanga ecihugo omu njira nyinjà, n’obukulu bw’omurhimanya bunarhinde bwinjà.
\v 2 Oku mwâmi ayîmire, kw’anashîgwa, n’oku omurhambo ali, kwo n’abantu bâge banahimba.
\v 3 Mwâmi muhwinja, buhanya oku bambali, bukengêre bwa barhegesi buyinamula ecihugo.
\v 4 Nyamuzinda ye nn’oburhegesi bw’igulu, amango abwîne go anagoshôla omurhegesi okwânîne.
\v 5 Okubêrwa kw’omuntu emwa Nyamuzinda kurhenga, ye hà abajira amarhegeko irenge.
\s1 Okulwîsa obucîbone
\p 
\v 6 Oleke okubîkira owinyu akarhinda ciru ankabîha, oleke okuhingira omujina.
\v 7 Obucîbone bugayîsa Nyamuzinda n’omuntu, bombi kandi barhabona oku bulyâlya.
\v 8 Ecihugo cinalye ecâbo oburhegesi, obulyâlya, okuniga n’ensaranga birhumire.
\v 9 Cirhuma obudaka n’oluvù bicîbona, n’obwo oku acizîne erhi n’obulà mîra bwabayaga?
\v 10 Endwâla y’omujânyi erhumva bufumu, mwâmi ene, irhondo erhi afîre.
\v 11 Owafîre gukola munyama gwa bigûku, nsimba na mivunyu.
\v 12 Okuleka Nyamuzinda, n’okurhenzako Lulema omurhima, yo ntangiriro y’obucîbone.
\v 13 Omurhondêro gw’obucîbone co câha. Bulyâla ecâha lyo igwârhiro ly’obucîbone, n’omwîra waco buhanya alêrha eka. Co carhumire Nyamuzinda amuhà obuhane budârhi, kuhika aha buzinda.
\v 14 Nyamuzinda arhenzize abagale oku ntebe, ahebakwo ahatûdu.
\v 15 Nyamuzinda àkûzire abacîbonyi, n’aha mwâbo ahiraho abîrhôhye.
\v 16 Nyamuzinda ashâbire ebihugo by’amashanja, abishâba kuhika oku ciriba ciri omu idaho.
\v 17 Hali n’amango abimanywîre, abishâba lwoshi, abizâza omu igulu birekikengêrwa.
\v 18 Obucîbone burhali bulume, n’obukunizi bw’okuyîrha burhali bw’oku bûko bw’omukazi.
\s1 Abantu bakwânîne olukengwa
\p 
\v 19 Bûko buhi bukwânîne olukengwa? Bûko bw’omuntu. Bûko buhi bukwaninc olukengwa? Bûko bw’abarhînya Nyamuzinda. Bûko buhi bukwânîne okugaywa? Bûko bw’omuntu. Bûko buhi bukwânîne okugaywa? Bûko bw’abavuna irhegeko.
\v 20 Omurhegesi anakengwe na bene wâbo, n’abarhînya Nyamuzinda banakuzibwe naye.
\v 21 Okurhînya Nyakasane gw’omurhondêro gw’okuzihwa; obucîbone n’obuzibu bw’omurhima gw’omurhondêro gw’okugayaguzibwa.
\v 22 Omugale, omurhonyi, nîsi erhi omukenyi, alimbîre okurhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 23 Kurhakwânîni okugayaguza omukenyi w’obukengêre, kurhashigânîni kandi okuhà enkola-maligo okukengwa.
\v 24 Omurhegesi, omucîranuzi bali bakulu, kukwânîne okubakenga, ci ntà mukulu olushire omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 25 Omujà murhimanya anashigwe n’abalengerîre, n’omuntu wayigîrizibwe bwinjà arhacîduduma.
\s1 Obwîrhôhye n’okuli
\p 
\v 26 Omanye wakacîbona bwenge nka oli omu mukolo, omanye wakacîkunga n’obwo oli omu bulagîrire.
\v 27 Omuntu wâkola, abè mugale ye mukulu, aha muntu ogenda ocîkunga n’obwo ntyo alâla.
\v 28 Mwâna wâni, ocîkunge n’olugero, olole oli wa lugero lunganaci.
\v 29 Omuntu ocîbîhire yêne, ndi wakamunywêra emizimu? Nîsi ndi wankakenga ocîgayire yêne?
\v 30 Omukenyi akengerwa murhima gwâge, n’omugale bamukengêre ebirugu byâge.
\v 31 Mukenge omu bukenyi, hano agâla lyôhe kurhi? Mugaywa omu bugale, lyôhe hano akena kurhi?
\c 11
\s1 Embuga: galangala erhi na malunde
\p 
\v 1 Omukenyi nk’ali murhimanya, irhwe ayînamula, n’ekarhî k’abakulu abwârhala.
\v 2 Orhakungiraga omuntu mubî obulî, orhanagayiraga omuntu amagala manyi.
\v 3 Olujuci lubà lunyi omu bibalala ci ebi lujira birhahimwa bununu.
\v 4 Orhalimbiraga emyambalo yâwe, orhacîbonaga bamâkukûnga: bulya emikolo ya Nyamuzinda erhahimwa bwinjà, ci kwône eri mifulike omu masù g’abantu.
\v 5 Kanji abâmi barhenzibwe oku ntebe, n’ecigolo cayambala ishungwè lyâbo.
\v 6 Kanji baciri-misî bayandazîbwe burhaba, na bannahano bakulu bashuba bashizi.
\s1 Okugerêreza n’okuyisha bunyi-bunyi
\p 
\v 7 Orhaganyagya embere orhangule bwinjà, gerêreza burhanzi, obuliganya.
\v 8 Orhashuzagya orhanaciyumva, orhatwîraga owinyu omu binwa.
\v 9 Orhakalihiraga olubanja lurhakuyêrekîri. orhajâga omu ntambala y’abanya-byâha.
\v 10 Mwâna wâni, oleke okuhambalikanya emmanja, zikalugirira orhazifume, ciru wankalibirha, orhashegûke, n’okuyâka kurhakufumye.
\v 11 Abacîkanangula ho bali: barhame, balibirhe, ci oku balibisire, kwo n’emunda bajà yabayâka.
\s1 Okulangâlira Nyamuzinda
\p 
\v 12 Hali abazamba bahûna oburhabâle: bakenyi ba birugu ci bakenyi bagale, Nyamuzinda kurhonya abarhonya, anabayînamule omu buligo bwâbo.
\v 13 Nyamuzinda anarhume bashubiyînamula amalanga, abandi hasômerwe obwo.
\v 14 Aminjà n’amabî, akalamo n’olufù, obukenyi n’obugale byoshi emwa Nyamuzinda birhenga.
\v 15 Obushinganyanya. obwenge n’okumanya irhegeko rhubihâbwa na Nyakasane, obuzigire n’ebijiro binjà byoshi emwâge birhenga,
\v 16 isirhe n’obumînya byalemeragwa abanya-byâha, banyankola-maligo, obuhanya buli bwâbo.
\v 17 Enshôkano za Nyamuzinda zishobôlwa n’abamukunda, n’oburhonyi bwâge bubalusize ensiku zoshi.
\v 18 Hali abantu bagala erhi kubîkirira okujinika kurhumire, lolaga oluhembo lwâbo\f + \fr 11, 18 \ft Oluhembo lwâbo: en’igulu emwa mugulûza, ntà kucîbona, lolà \xt Ayu 27, 16\xt*\ft … \xt Luk 12, 16\xt*\ft .\f*:
\v 19 Olusiku baderha, erhi: «Nakarhamukaga, birhali binyi ebi, nâlamira aha», barhamanyiri nsiku inga zisigîre: bàbisiga, bafè, abandi babirye.
\v 20 Mwâna wâni, ocîsêgereze oku mukolo gwâwe, okazigushîbirira, olinde oshosihaliramwo.
\v 21 Orhayâgalagwa n’emikolo y’omunya-byâha, ocîkubagire Nyamuzinda, osêre oku mukolo gwâwe. Bulya kuli kulembu emwa Nyamuzinda, okugaza omukenyi bunobuno, mwa kano kanya.
\v 22 Omugisho gwa Nyamuzinda lwo luhembo lw’omuntu omurhînya, kano kanya, omugisho gwa Nyamuzinda gwamanajako obwâso.
\v 23 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Bici ndagirirekwo? Kurhenga ene, ebyâni biri binganaci bulya?»
\v 24 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Ka ntakola mugale, kurhi nacibà?»
\v 25 Olusiku lw’iragi omuntu arhakengêra amalibuko, n’olusiku lw’obuhanya, omuntu anayibagire iragi.
\v 26 Kwo kuderha oku, emwa Nyamuzinda, kuli kulembu, olusiku lw’okufà, anahembe ngasi muntu nk’oku ebijiro byâge binali.
\v 27 Hisanzi hitya hya malibuko hinayibagize obwîgusi, n’omu kanya kazinda k’omuntu mwo emikolo yâge ebonekera.
\v 28 Orhakungaga iragi ly’owundi anacizîne, bulya omuntu amanyirwa aha buzinda bwâge\f + \fr 11, 28 \ft buzinda bwâge: okufà bwinjà ly’iragi, ofè oli murhonyi emwa Nyamuzinda; ah’obugale bwankakurhanga, bwankakuzinda.\f*.
\s1 Okucîlanga oku mubî
\p 
\v 29 Enyumpa yâwe erhabâga ishubûkiro lya ngasi yêshi, bulya amenge g’omubî gali manji.
\v 30 Kula bagwârha enkwâle, bayihira omu irhonga, kwo guli omurhima gw’omucîbonyi, ye mujishamba walinda oku wafà.
\v 31 Omunywesi anahindule chinja hihi, n’ehinja hirhabula ishembo emund’ali.
\v 32 Isasi ly’omuliro linayâse ecibêye, omubî anacîbundike àkol’alingihuma omukò.
\v 33 Omanye omubî bulya ye kabindi-afunikira-obubî, omanye akuhirakwo akafinjo.
\v 34 Ow’embuga omuhire aha mwâwe, kuyôkêra ohayôkîre, wabona oku akukoza oku ba-aha-mwâwe.
\c 12
\s1 Aminja
\p 
\v 1 Okajira aminjà, omanye na ndi ogajirire, galeke okuhera busha.
\v 2 Aminjà. ogajirire omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, bulya akugalulirago, yêne erhi Nyamuzinda.
\v 3 Orhajiriraga entagoyôla omu bubî aminja, n’omuntu orhakwîrirwa okujira ehy’obuzigire.
\v 4 Ohè omuntu ozigira Nyamuzinda, oleke enkola-maligo, orhayirhabâlaga.
\v 5 Aminja ogajirire omwîrhohye, oleke cîbone ojacira Nyamuzinda. Omuyîme ciru ebi alya, orhamuhâga, ankanakulenga misî; bulya omunkwa gwâge mabî kabiri, oku minjà goshi wamujirîre.
\v 6 Ciru Nyamuzinda naye arhabona oku banya-byâha, ababî kuhana abahana.
\v 7 Ohè omuntu mwinjà, oleke omubî.
\s1 Abîra n’abarhali bo
\p 
\v 8 Amango oli mugale, kuli kuzibu okumanya omwîra w’okuli, ci linda okene, omushombanyi arhacîfulike.
\v 9 Amango omuntu ali omu iragi, abashombanyi bâge banadikîrire, hano ajâkwo obuhanya, ciru n’omwîra anamuyâke.
\v 10 Orhacîkubagiraga omushombanyi, kul’ecûma cijâkwo engisha, kwo n’obubî bwâge buli,
\v 11 Ciru akacirhohya akanayisha abunda-bunda, omanye orhacîkubagiragaye. Omuyôrhekwo kula bakombêza ecilolero, kengêra oku engisha zâge zirhayimangirhenge.
\v 12 Orhamuhiraga hofi nâwe, bulya anakurhenzaho, ahaje. Orhamubwârhazagya ekulyo kwâwe, bulya anakunyaga entebe, obone buzinda ly’okola wayumva ebinwa byâni, ocîyunjuze obwo, aka kanwa okakengêre.
\v 13 Mbwîra ndi wakabêra omugwâsi w’enjoka lukogo nka yamamuluma, erhi ndi wankalubêra abajà balwîsa ebiryanyi?
\v 14 Kwo biri ntyo oku muntu oyinjibana omubî, n’oshangîra obubî bwâge.
\v 15 Amango ociyimanzire buzibu, arhankacîyerekana, oleke obè nka warherera obone oku akujira.
\v 16 Omumînya anajire ebinwa by’olubohôlolo, ci emurhima gwâge bulyo bwa kukukwêba omu nyenga adwîrhe alo­nza. Omubisha anarhoze emirenge, ci amango ahashire, arhashukira.
\v 17 Amango olikwo obuhanya, onamubone ye murhanzi, omanye mpu kurhabâla ali, n’obwo kuholêreza.
\v 18 Anadunde irhwe, akome na kagasha, ci arhahundûla binwa, n’obusù bwâge nzinzibalè.
\c 13
\s1 Okujà haguma n’abinyu
\p 
\v 1 Omuntu akahuma oku bulembo, bunamunanîrekwo, n’okômera omucîbonyi anamushushe.
\v 2 Orhabarhulaga omuzigo orhagale, orhayinjibanaga omuzibu n’omugale kulusha we. Cici cankarhuma wahira enyungu y’ibumba haguma n’ey’ecûma? N’obwo erhi zankahukulana, ey’ibumba yanabereka?
\v 3 Omugale anabè amanyagana abulinalîmbirana, omukenyi ananyagwe ehyâge, abulihisengera.
\v 4 Omugale amango omukwânîne anakukolêse. n’amango wamanyihya obushiru anakujandike,
\v 5 amango ocigwêrhe ehyâwe, buciri bwîra, ci erhi analinzire, buzira nshonyi, mpu akunyagehyo.
\v 6 Amango alagîrîre oku burhabâle bwâwe, anakurhonye, akuyêreke amasheka, olangâlîre, akubwîre ebinwa binjà, mpu: «bici olagîrîrekwo?»
\v 7 Kurhâhanga arhakubonêsa nshonyi hano akol’agaba, ciru anakunyage kabiri-kasharhu, na buzinda akuhè ebinioko. Hano akulangira, akuyâke, adunde irhwe acîzongere.
\v 8 Omanye orharhebagwa, balekikubonêsa nshonyi erhi buhwinja bwâwe burhuma.
\v 9 Okabona omugale akuhamagala, onabè nk’orhumvîrhi, wabona oku akuyimbîrira.
\v 10 Orhacîhunikaga bulya banakugalula nyuma, kandi orhabêraga kuli bwenêne bulya banakuyîbagira.
\v 11 Orhakômeraga omugale, omanye ebinwa byâge binji-binji. Orhayêmêraga ebinwa byâge binji-binji byo biri bya murhego, oku ali mpu ashagalusire, n’obwo alikwo akuyenja.
\v 12 Omanye omurhunzi w’ebinwa, arhakushurhîsa, akushwêkêse.
\v 13 Omanye-omanye, bulya obuhanya bukulusize omu njira.
\v 14 Erhi wankayumva okwo amango ol’îrò, onazûke; omu kalamo kâwe koshi, ozigire Nyakasane onamuyâkûze akuciza.
\s1 Omugale n’omukenyi
\p 
\v 15 Ngasi cintu cizîne coshi cisîma ecâbo, na ngasi muntu kwo n’okwo.
\v 16 Ensimba erhahambarha erhali ya bûko bwâyo, n’omuntu naye wâbo muntu ayinjibana.
\v 17 K’onabwîne oku eciryanyi cakayumvanya n’omwâna-buzi? Omuntu mubî n’orhînya Nyamuzinda, nabo kwo na kuguma.
\v 18 K’onabwîne oku omurhûla gwankabà ekarhî ka mpunga n’akabwa? Kwo na kuguma ntà murhûla ekarhî k’omugale n’omukenyi.
\v 19 Ensimba nto byo biryo by’entale emuzirhu, ntyo, abakenyi yo minyama y’abagale.
\v 20 Emw’omucîbonyi obwîrhôhye kuli kushûbuka, ntyo, omugale naye arhabona oku mukenyi.
\v 21 Omugale abè nk’asârhala kwône, abîra hâge banamugwârhirire, ow’obuligo akahirima, ciru n’abîra bâge banamusige.
\v 22 Omugale akasarhala, banamugwârhirire banji, akaderha ebirhali byo, banakongôrheze. Ow’obuligo akasârhala, banamulongôze, na ciru akaderha ebinwa binjà, barhabihiramwo izù.
\v 23 Omugale akabumbula akanwa, boshi banahwekêre, n’akanwa kâge kamanyikane hoshi-hoshi. Omukenyi akabumbula akanwa, banaderhe, mpu: «hya ngahi ehi?». Akasârhala banamususunike oku idaho.
\v 24 Obugale buli bwinjà nka burhalikwo câha, omu iderha ly’enkola-maligo obukenyi buli bubî.
\v 25 Murhima guhà omuntu iranga, gulijire linjà erhi libî.
\v 26 Omurhima mwinjà bwo na busù bwinjà, okusinga emigani gubà mukolo muzibu.
\c 14
\s1 Iragi ly’okuli
\p 
\v 1 Iragi ly’omuntu erhasâgijira ecâha omu nderho, n’orhayumva omurhima gw’ebyâha byâge gwamulya.
\v 2 Iragi lyâge omuntu orhacîtumuzizi cici, omuntu orharhiba murhima.
\s1 Okuyâgalwa n’obujinisi
\p 
\v 3 Obugale burhakwânana nshâhu, n’oku muntu w’amagene, ebirugu binji birigi bya cici?
\v 4 Ohaka n’ishali lyamuyîrha, bandi ahakira, ebyâge byalîbwa n’abandi.
\v 5 Owacîyîrha yêne, ndi akaciza? Owayôboha ciru okuhuma oku byâge.
\v 6 Ntà mwîsi mubî kulusha ocîyîrha yêne, lwo luhembo lw’okumînya kwâge.
\v 7 Okujira aminjà kwâge kunabè nka kuhugwa, buzinda anayêrekane obumînya bwâge.
\v 8 Ali mumînya omuntu w’amasù g’oluhubo, kukengula akengula n’okugayaguza abandi.
\v 9 Omuyâgalwa arhasîma ehi agwêrhe, amagene kuyumya gayumya omurhima.
\v 10 Omujinisi arhalîka bulye, n’amêza gâge cizombo.
\v 11 Mwâna wâni, nk’ogwêrhe onalye, orhûle na Nyamuzinda entûlo ahûnyire.
\v 12 Orhayîbagiraga oku olufù omu njira luli, n’oku omulâli gw’ab’ekuzimu ntâye osâgikubwirago.
\v 13 Ojirire abîra bâwe aminjà oku orhacifa, ohâne nk’oku onahashire.
\v 14 Orhalahiraga iragi lya buno, orhanenaga ehinja omurhima gucifinjire.
\v 15 Kàli obugale bwâwe bandi wâbusigire? N’ebirugu byâwe kàli iragi lyâbigaba?
\v 16 Ohûne, onahâbwe. osîme, arhali ekuzimu yo balongeza obusîme.
\v 17 Ngasi mubiri kwo gukoya nka bwikunjè, okufà liri irhegeko ly’ensiku n’amango.
\v 18 Kul’obona orhwâsi rhw’omurhi gujagalîre, rhurhaliholoka rhurhalishoga, kwo n’amâburhwa g’omubiri n’omukò gali, oku baguma bafà abandi bâburhwa.
\v 19 Ngasi bushanja bukoya kuhwa bunahwa, na nnabwo bombi bagendanwa.
\s1 Iragi ly’omuntu murhimanya
\p 
\v 20 Iragi lyâge omuntu okengêra oburhimanya, n’orhimanya n’obukengêre bwâge,
\v 21 agerêreze emurhima enjira z’oburhimanya, anakulikire amahwe gâbwo.
\v 22 Kw’abushimba nka muhivi, oku njira yabwo alingûkiza;
\v 23 anajè ah’idirisha lyabwo, atamale aha lusò lwâbwo;
\v 24 acumbike eburhambi bwâbwo, agwîke omulindizo omu côgo câbwo;
\v 25 ayûbake eburhambi bwâbwo, abwârhale omu kahwenyenye k’omurhûla.
\v 26 Abuyâbuze abâna bâge, naye yêne ayâkire omu mashami gâbwo.
\v 27 Omu cihôho câbwo mwo akaziyâkira idûrhu, na ntyo ajè omu irenge lyâbwo.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Kw’ajira ntyo omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda; ôyankirira irhegeko burhimanya ashobôla.
\v 2 Kwo bumuyankirira nka kula nnina wa muntu amuyankirira, bumuyankirire nka muhya wayankirira ibà;
\v 3 bumulîse akalyo k’obwîrhonzi, bumunywese amîshi g’oburhimanya;
\v 4 abuyegemere, arhanacidundagane, abusêrekwo, arhanacibulabule.
\v 5 Bumulengereze enyanya ly’abâbo, omu karhî k’endêko, bumubumbûle akanwa.
\v 6 Ayumve omurhûla anabone ecimanè c’obusîme, ahabwe irenge ly’ensiku n’amango.
\v 7 Abasirhe ntà mango babuhikekwo, n’abanya-byâha barhakabubona.
\v 8 Oburhimanya burhabonanako n’obucîbone, n’abanywesi barhabukwirirwa.
\v 9 Obukuze burhaba omu kanwa k’omubî, bulya Nyamuzinda arhamuhiribwo.
\v 10 Bulya oburhimanya bwo buyêrekana obukuze, na Nyamuzinda ye bulangûla enjira.
\s1 Obuhuru bw’omuntu
\p 
\v 11 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Nyamuzinda warhumire najira ecâha», bulya Nyamuzinda arhankajira ebi ashomba\f + \fr 15, 11 \ft Ebi ashomba: omuntu agwêrhe obuhuru, anacîshoga ehi omurhima gumuhire; yêne anacijâmwo, aderhe «nalonza hirebe, najira hirebe; ntâlonza, ntâjire…» buzira kusêzibwa na ndi, Omuntu arhankashobeka Nyamuzinda mpu ye wamujirîsize amabî: lolà \xt Yak 1, 13-14\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 12 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Nyamuzinda warhumire nahabuka», bulya ntâco ajira n’omunya-byâha.
\v 13 Ntà bikabulirwa Nyamuzinda akwîrirwa, n’abantu bamurhînya barhabikwirirwa…
\v 14 Kurheng’aha murhondêro ye walemaga omuntu, anamuleka omurhima gwâge gumuhè.
\v 15 Nk’olonzize, amarhegeko wanagakulikira, okubêra omu njira nyinjà okuhashire.
\v 16 Embere zâwe, ahebireyo omuliro n’amîshi, lambûla okuboko, orhôle eci olonzize.
\v 17 Embere z’abantu, eri obuzîne n’olufù, muli byombi, eci balonzize co banacîshoga.
\v 18 Bulya oburhimanya bwa Nyamuzinda burhajira lugero, byoshi ahashire na byoshi abona.
\v 19 Amasù gâge gayêrekîre balya bamurhînya, amanyire yêne emikolo yoshi y’abantu.
\v 20 Ntâye akol’arhegesire mpu abè nkola-maligo, na ntâye akola ayêmêrire mpu abè mugoma.
\c 16
\s1 Obuhanya bw’ababî
\p 
\v 1 Orhacîfinjaga okuburha ba-bunji-bwa-busha, orhacîshingiraga abâna b’ebyâbi.
\v 2 Orhacîshingaga ciru bankaluga, nka barharhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 3 Arhalangaâliraga okulama kwâbo, arhalangaâliraga n’enjira balimwo, bulya muguma nkana ye mukulu aha cihumbi, n’aha omuntu akaburha enkola-maligo, akacîfira buzira mwâna.
\v 4 Omuntu muguma nkana anabumbe olugo, iburha ly’ababî kuhwa linahwa.
\v 5 Niene nabwîne n’amasù gâni bintu binji bishushana; nanayumva n’amarhwîri gâni ebiri bizibu.
\v 6 Omuliro gucîtuzire omu ndêko y’endyâlya, n’obukunizi buzûsire omu ngabo y’abagoma.
\v 7 Nyamuzinda arhababaliraga balya ba ciri-misî ha mîra, bagomaga erhi kulimbira emisî kurhuma\f + \fr 16, 7 \ft Muhimbo gwa busha: lolà \xt Murh 6, 1-7\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 8 Arhababaliraga olugo Loti\f + \fr 16, 8 \ft Loti: mwene wâbo Ahrahamu: lolà \xt Murh 19, 1-29\xt*\ft .\f* aliyûbasiremwo, erhi obucîbone bwa benelwo bwamamugayîsa.
\v 9 Arhabaga bwonjo oku bûko bw’emihera\f + \fr 16, 9 \ft Emihera: ab’e Kanâni barhanzi, balya barhashangîraga na Nyamuzinda w’okuli:\f*, boshi baholoka erhi byâha byâho birhuma.
\v 10 Akujirira n’engabo ya bihumbi magana galindarhu\f + \fr 16, 10 \ft murhima gwâbo mubî: lolà \xt Lub 12, 37\xt*\ft . \f*, balya bacîhindulaga\f + \fr 16, 10 \ft Emihera: ab’e Kanâni barhanzi, balya barhashangîraga na Nyamuzinda w’okuli.\f* erhi buzibu bwa mirhima yâbo burhuma.
\v 11 Ciru ankabîre muntu muguma cikanyi-cirhagomba, okumuleka arhahanyirwi kwanasômerana, bulya obwonjo n’obukunizi biri bya Nyamuzinda, nn’olukogo ye na nn’oburhè.
\v 12 Obwonjo bwâge buluga, ci n’obukali bwâge burhali bunyi, anatwe olubanja lw’abantu nk’oku emikolo yâbo enali.
\v 13 Arhaleka buzira kuhana omunya-byâha n’amabî gâge, arhanalindîsa busha omuntu omurhînya.
\v 14 Abà wa lukogo lunji, ci ngasi muguma ashobôla nk’oku ebijiro byâge binali.
\v 15 Nyamuzinda adundaguzize omurhima gwa Faraoni mwâmi w’e Mîsiri mpu lyo amanyîsa emikolo yâge hano igulu.
\v 16 Obwonjo bwâge bucîyêrekana oku biremwa byoshi, obulangashane n’omwizimya abijirire abantu boshi.
\s1 Oluhembo ho luli
\p 
\v 17 Orhaderhaga, erhi: «Ka ntacîfulika oyo Nyamuzinda, eyo nyanya ndi wânkengêra?» «Ndi wajà anfukula omu karhî k’entuliri y’abantu?» «Ndi ntâye ekarhî k’ebiremwa binji\f + \fr 16, 17 \ft Binji ntya: lolà \xt Murh 3, 10; 4, 9\xt*\ft .\f* ntya».
\v 18 Lolà: empingu, enyanya kurhaluka amalunga, ekuzimu n’igulu, okuyisha kwâge kwamâbigezamwo omusisi.
\v 19 Caligumiza entondo n’eciriba c’igulu, byamâgeramwo ogwa nyugunyu embere zâge.
\v 20 Ci kwône barhakengêra ebyo byoshi, ndi ogerêreza ogw’enjira zâge?
\v 21 Ciru n’omusirûla gurhabonekana, hôfi emikolo yâge yoshi gali mahwe.
\v 22 «Emikolo y’obushinganyanya\f + \fr 16, 22 \ft Eri kuli: owalinda endagâno ya Nyamuzinda ahîre omurhima omu nda, ntà kuderha mpu amâlegama. arhâciyishe!\f*, ndi wayimanyîsa? Ndi wayirinda? Bulya endagâno eri kuli».
\v 23 Zo nkengêro z’omuntu w’obukengêre bwofi ezo, omuhwinja n’omuhabà barhalôrha elirhali isirhe.
\s1 Omuntu omu biremwa
\p 
\v 24 Nyumva, mwâna wâni, oyigîrire, ebinwa nakubwîra obirhege omurhima.
\v 25 Nakuyêreka olugero lw’enjira, nacîhangana nkuyumvîse omanye.
\v 26 aha murhondêro, erhi Nyamuzinda alema ebiremwa byâge\f + \fr 16, 26 \ft Ebiremwa byâge: lolà \xt Murh 1, 1\xt*\ft : okulemwa kw’igulu.\f*, oku ayûsirema, agabira ngasi ciguma aha cabêra.
\v 27 Ebiremwa byâge abihà olukere lw’ensiku n’amango, kurheng’emurhondêro gwâbyo kuhika okuli kw’amango. Ebiremwa byâge birhafà ishali, birhafà murhamo, na ntà mango bireka omukolo gwâbyo.
\v 28 Ntâco cisagihukula ecâbo, na ntà mango bibula kumuyumva.
\v 29 Nyamuzinda asinza igulu obwo, aliyunjuza ebinja byâge.
\v 30 Alihiramwo ngasi bûko bwa nsimba, n’omu idaho zânâshubire.
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 Nyamuzinda arhenzize omuntu omu budaka, na buzinda omu idaho amushubiza\f + \fr 17, 1 \fk Amushubiza\ft : lolà \xt Murh 2\xt*\ft : omuntu kufà afà.\f*.
\v 2 Abantu àbatwîrîre ensiku n’amango gagerêrîre, abahà obuhashe oku byoshi\f + \fr 17, 2 \fk byoshi\ft : lolà \xt Murh 1, 28\xt*\ft .\f* biri en’igulu.
\v 3 Nk’oku yêne ali, abahà emisî, abalema bamushushire\f + \fr 17, 3 \fk Bamushushire\ft : lolà \xt Murh 1, 27\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 4 Aha ngasi ciremwa okuyôboha omuntu, ly’omuntu akulira ensimba n’ebinyunyi.
\v 5 Bashobôla okukolêsa mahashe arhanu ga Nyakasane, nka buhashe bwa kali ndarhu, bàhâbwa okukolêsa obwenge n’obushinganyanya nka buhashe bwa kali nda, buhugûla ago mahashe gâge.
\v 6 Abalema bagwêrhe akanwa, olulimi, amasù, amarhwîri, abahà omurhima gw’oburhimanya.
\v 7 Abayunjuza bumanye n’obukengêre, abamanyîsa ehibî n’ehinja.
\v 8 Abahir’obumoleke omu murhima, mpu babone obunji bw’emikolo\f + \fr 17, 8 \fq Emikolo yâge\ft : lolà \xt Rom 1, 19-20\xt*\ft .\f* yâge.
\v 9 Anabahà okujira obukuze bw’ebisômerîne byâge, ensiku n’amango.
\v 10 Bakuze izîno lyâge limâna, baganîre obunji bw’ebi ajizire.
\v 11 Anabahè obumanye, kandi anabamanyîse irhegeko ly’akalamo.
\v 12 Ajira haguma nabo endagâno y’ensiku n’amango, abamanyîsa enkengêro\f + \fr 17, 12 \fq Enkengêro zâge\ft : Marhegeko Nyamuzinda ahâga Mûsa.\f* zâge.
\v 13 amasù gâbo gabona obunji bw’irenge lyâge, amarhwîri gâbo gayumva obunene n’obwinjà bw’izù lyâge.
\v 14 Ababwîra, erhi: «Mucîlange oku bubî bwoshi», abahà amarhegeko bakulikira ngasi muguma oku wâbo.
\s1 Nyamuzinda mutwî w’emmanja
\p 
\v 15 Olugendo lwâbo kubona alubona ensiku zoshi, ntà mango lucîfulike aha arhalubone.
\v 16 Kurhenga oburhò bwâbo, enjira yâbo erhabayêrekeza oburhali bubî, ciru barhanahashaga okuhindula omurhima gwâbo guli nk’ibâle, gubè murhima gwa muntu.
\v 17 Ngasi lubaga aluhîre omurhambo wâlurhegeka, Israheli yêhe guli mwanya gwa Nyamuzinda yêne.
\v 18 Bulya ye murhanzi, amulera omu bwôrhere nkana, omu kubà amuyunjuzize bulangashane bw’obuzigire bwâge, arhacimulikiriraga.
\v 19 Ebijiro byâbo byoshi biri nk’izûba embere zâge, amasù gâge garhahusa kwalola olugendo lwâbo.
\v 20 Obulyâlya bwâbo burhacifulisiri amasù gâge, ebyâha byâbo byoshi biri embere za Nyamuzinda.
\v 21 Cikwône Nyakasane abà mwinjà, ayishi n’eciremwa câge, Arhabiherêrekeza erhi kubilîkirira, ci kulanga abilanga.
\v 22 Okuhâna kw’obuzigire kuli kubîka kw’omuntu, kunalange ecijiro cinjà nka mbonyi y’isù.
\v 23 Olusiku Nyamuzinda abahemba ho luciri, abavangulire omugisho gw’oluhembo lwâbo.
\v 24 Abacîyunjuzize anabahè omurhima gw’okugaluka, arhûlirize abacîzigulusire.
\s1 Mucîyunjuze
\p 
\v 25 Ogaluke emunda Nyamuzinda ali, oleke ebyâha byâwe, omushenge bwinjà, oleke okumugayîsa.
\v 26 Oshubire Ow’Enyanya, oleke obulyâlya, oshomhe lwoshi lwoshi obulenzi.
\v 27 Bulya ndigi wankajikuza Nyamuzinda ekuzimu, akabà abazîne barhamukuzizi, bamuhà irenge lyâge?
\v 28 Obukuze burhaba emw’emifù nk’oku burhaba emw’abarhahali, ozîne agwêrhe n’amagala ye Nyamuzinda.
\v 29 Nêci, obwonjo bwa Nyamuzinda bubà bunji, olukogo lwâge oku bantu bayêrekîre emund’ali.
\v 30 bulya omuntu arhankabà na byoshi, mwene-omuntu arhali karhafà.
\v 31 Bici bimoleka kulusha izûba? Kurhahanga lirhafulikwa n’ecitù. Omubiri n’omukò maligo byaka­nakola.
\v 32 Nyamuzinda ye lolà ngasi buhashe buli enyanya emalunga, abantu boshi bunabà budaka na luvù.
\c 18
\s1 Nyamuzinda abà mukulu
\p 
\v 1 Nyamubâho ensiku n’amango ye walemaga byoshi.
\v 2 Nyamuzinda yêne mushinganyanya.
\v 3 Ntà wundi omulushire, ye rhegeka igulu n’akashanashanwe, byoshi bikenga obulonza bwâge, bulya ye mwâmi wa byoshi, oku buhashe bwâge ye berûla ebitagatîfu n’ebirhali bitagatîfu.
\v 4 Ndi àhîre obuhashe bw’okuderha ebijiro byâge, na ndi wankavûlula ebinja byâge?
\v 5 Ndi wankagera obuhashe bw’obwâmi bwâge, na ndi wankaganira obwonjo bwâge?
\v 6 Ntâco omuntu ankanyihyakwo na ntâco ankayûshûlakwo, ntâye wankavûlula ebinja bya Nyamuzinda byoshi.
\v 7 Erhi omuntu ayûsa, gwo gukola murhondêro, erhi kwo kukola kurhangira, n’erhi ahusa kubè kurhângâla\f + \fr 18, 7 \fk Kurhângâla\ft : ebya Nyamuzinda birhaheka, omuntu akwânîne alole, asômerwe, kandi aharâmye owabijiraga.\f*.
\s1 Omuntu abà ntâye
\p 
\v 8 Omuntu abà cici? Abà wa bici? Ngahi ayinjihira na ngahi abihira?
\v 9 Akalamo kâge? Emyâka igana nk’eri minji.
\v 10 Murhônyi gudômwa omu nyanja, mbeke ya mushenyi, kwo eyo myâka eri embere z’ensiku n’amango.
\v 11 Co cirhuma Nyamuzinda alember’abantu, co cinarhuma anabarhulirako olukogo lwâge
\v 12 Abwîne, amanyire oku obuzinda bwâbo bubà buligo, co cirhuma aluza obwonjo.
\v 13 Omuntu ababalira omulungu wâge, ci Nyamuzinda yêhe ababalira ngasi muntu yêshi, anahanûle, akubûle, ayîgîrize, arhange kul’omungere anajira obusò bwâge\f + \fr 18, 13 \ft Obusò bwâge: Nyamuzinda arhahimwa lukogo oku bantu, lolà \xt 2 Mak 6, 13; Bush 12, 19\xt*\ft …\f*.
\v 14 Olukogo lwâge lubà oku bantu bakulikîre enjira yâge, balya balongereza okushimba amarhegeko gâge.
\s1 Okuhâna kulimwo kubiri
\p 
\v 15 Mwâna wâni, aminjà ojirire omuntu orhagakulikizagyako bijâci, n’ebi wahâna, orhabihânaga wanacîduduma.
\v 16 Olumè lunanyihye idûrhu bulya? Akanwa kinjà kalushire okuhâna.
\v 17 Nêci, akanwa kinjà kalushire okuhâna, ci omuntu nkana byombi haguma abihira.
\v 18 Omusirhe anabè arhahâna anabulijâcirana, n’omwâgalwa anahâne ehi alakira.
\s1 Okucîrhonda n’okulalira
\p 
\v 19 Embere ojè lubanja, orhangidôsa emirhima, ocîbuke oku orhacilwâla.
\v 20 Ocîyâze embere ojè lubanja, hano olujà, bakulîka.
\v 21 Ocîrhohye embere olwâle, yêrekana oku ocîyunjuzize nka wamajira ecâha.
\v 22 Harhajiraga ecakuhanza kwayûkiriza eciragâne câwe bwacibona, orhalindaga olufù mpu lyo ôbà mwinjà.
\v 23 Gerêreza embere olaganye Nyamuzinda, olekiyôrha nk’owarhangula Nyamuzinda.
\v 24 Kengêra obukunizi bw’ensiku nzinda, amango g’okucîhôla, amango Nyamuzinda akengulana.
\v 25 Amango oyêzize, kengêra ecizombo, n’amango ohirhire, kengêra obukenyi n’obuligo.
\v 26 Kurhenga sêzi kuhika bijingo, akasanzi karhayimanga, byoshi kugera bigera duba embere za Nyamuzinda.
\v 27 Omurhimanya kucîlanga acîlanga muli byoshi, omu nsiku z’obugoma, anacîlange oku bulenzi.
\v 28 Omuntu w’obukengêre yêshi ayishi oburhimanya; owabuhisirekwo kukûnga abukûnga.
\v 29 Abantu b’obukengêre n’abadesi nkana nabo bashibirire oburhimanya, n’ebi baganîra eri migani ekwânîne obushinganyanya.
\s1 Okucîrhegeka kw’omuntu
\p 
\v 30 Orhayêmêraga amagene g’àbakulula, oshube oku nyîfinjo zâwe.
\v 31 Okushimba enshumi z’amagene gâwe, kwanarhuma abashombanyi bâwe bakushekera.
\v 32 Omanye wakarhonya obununîrizi bw’amasîma, orhayinjibanaga ab’enkômedu ziri ntyo.
\v 33 Orhajiraga ensiku nkulu n’ensaranga mpozanyo, amango enshoho yâwe eri nyûmu.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Omuntu ojira ntyo arhakagala, n’ogaya ehinyi agwêrhe, bukenyi ahingira.
\v 2 amamvu n’abakazi b’ebishungu byo bihûsa abalume omurhima, n’omwîra w’embaraga arhabâ nshonyi\f + \fr 19, 2 \ft Omu kukulikira La Bible de Jérusalem, otremolet.free.fr, rhukûzire emilongo yalijire yashubîrirwa kabiri n’okuleka emihenge y’olukere lukûlisirwe kuli milongo miguma miguma omu mandiko g’ecigereki garhenga muli LXX \f*.
\v 3 Oyo muntu guli munyama gw’ebigûku n’emivunyu, n’ecirala cirhafuma aho.
\s1 Omanye okudegenda
\p 
\v 4 Oyêmêra dudaduba erhi wa murhima mwangu, n’ojira ecâha yêne ocîkolera amabî.
\v 5 Osîma amabî ayishihanwa.
\v 6 Orhakwîrirwa kalimi afuma lunji.
\v 7 Omwanzi gwa bene orhagubwîraga owundi, ntâye wakushombera okwo.
\v 8 Gwa bene orhagubwîra ndi: oli omwîra wâwe, oli omushombanyi wâwe, nkaba libè irhegeko emund’oli ly’okuderha.
\v 9 Bânakurhega amarhwîri, bâkukemerane, buzinda bakushombe.
\v 10 Ka bakubwîzire omwanzi? Ocibêre nshinda. Yaah! Orhabashe!
\v 11 Mwanzi musungunu baguhè omwêrûzi, gumuheke nka mukazi wabiga-bigwa n’emikero mibishi.
\v 12 Omwanzi babwîra ecinganyi, guli nka mwampi bamulashire omu cibero.
\s1 Wayumvîrhe, gendaga olole wêne
\p 
\v 13 J’emw’omwîra wâwe: kwankanabà ntâko anajizire, n’akabà hali oku anajijire, arhacishubirire.
\v 14 J’emw’omulungu wâwe, kwankanabà ntâkwo anadesire, n’akabà hali oku anadesire, arhacikuderhe.
\v 15 Ja wêne emw’omwîra wâwe: bulya abantu barhahimwa kunywerha, orhayêmêrezagya ngasi coshi bakubwîzire.
\v 16 Kanji olulimi lufuma omuntu n’obwo arhakulonzagya, ndi akanwa karhasâgifuma?
\v 17 Genda oshambâze mulungu wâwe embere omujise lubanja, kulikira amarhegeko g’Ow’Enyanya orhajira burhè.
\v 18 Amarhegeko ga Nyamuzinda gwo gubà murhwe gw’olukogo lwâge, n’obushinganyanya buyunguka obuzigire bwâge.
\v 19 Okumanya amarhegeko ga Nyamuzinda\f + \fr 19, 19 \ft Okashimba amarhegeko gâge wâbà n’olukogo lwâge, n’obushinganyanya bwâwe bwâkulêrhera obuzigire bwâge.\f* n’okugakulikira yo njira y’a­kalamo, abajira ebimusîmîsa banahumbûle oku murhi gw’obuzîne bw’ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Oburhimanya bw’okuli n’oburhali bwo
\p 
\v 20 Ngasi burhimanya kubà kurhînya Nyamuzinda, na ngasi burhimanya bubâmo okuyûkiriza irhegeko n’okumanya obuhashe bwâge.
\v 21 Omushizi obwîra nnawâbo erhi: «Ntâjire ehi walonza», ciru ankahijira buzinda, kugayîsa agayîsa omuhà eci alya.
\v 22 Okumanya amabî burhaba burhimanya, n’ihano ly’abanya-byâha burhaba bwîrhonzi.
\v 23 Hali obulenga burhali bwo, musirhe, omuntu orhajira burhimanya.
\v 24 Owabà na bwenge bunyi akanarhînya Nyamuzinda, ye mukulu aha mwenge-mwenge wavuna irhegeko.
\v 25 Hali obulungu bw’obulyâlya, hali abanywerha mpu lyo babona eci balonza.
\v 26 Hali abantu bagenda bajonjoboka n’omungo, n’obwo kwa bwengûza.
\v 27 Obone akube igosi, abè nka wa bihuli, ye na murhanzikola amaligo hano abona obulyo.
\v 28 Hali onunirwa n’obuzamha bw’okujira ecâha, hano abona akasanzi k’okucîjira erhi na yêshi oyo.
\v 29 Ebusù omuntu amanyirwa, omuntu nkana abonekana emalanga.
\v 30 Myambalo y’omuntu emanyîsa omukolo gwâge, n’olugendo lwâge luyêrekane al muntu muci\f + \fr 19, 30 \ft Rhwamâyimangira oku milongo 30 eri omu Ebibliya Ntagatîfu, Verbum Bible, Kinshasa, 1992, n’obwo LXX ahisire oku milongo 35\f*.
\c 20
\s1 Okuhulika n’okuderha
\p 
\v 1 Hali ebinwa by’obukali birhalusire, hali n’okuhulika kuyêrekana omuntu w’obukengêre.
\v 2 Okukaliha kwo kukulu aha kubîka obukunizi.
\v 3 Omuntu ocîshobeka yêne erhi buhane afumire.
\v 4 Kw’ali nk’enshahu yashimba okugwârha omunyere, omuntu wacîhambira okutwa olubanja n’akadali.
\v 5 Lebè acîhulikire, abonekana murhimanya, oku lebè w’engamîzi acîshombanya n’omuvovo gwâge.
\v 6 Lebè ahulisire kubula eci aderha, na lebè ahulisire kulinda agâge mango g’okuderha.
\v 7 Omurhimanya mango agera g’okuhulika, ci kadegende n’omusirhe barhishigera mango.
\v 8 Kadesi acîshombanya, n’omanya mpu yêne oyishiderha, nshombo acîzûkiza.
\s1 Ebisômeza biluga
\p 
\v 9 Lebè ânacirira omu buhanya; hali oyu obuhanya buciza, haligi n’amango obucire bulêrha nyamanjà.
\v 10 Hali okuhâna kurhayunguka, haligi n’okuhâna kuyunguka kabiri,
\v 11 Hali amango irenge lirhohya omuntu, haligi n’abantu balengerera omu buligo bwâbo.
\v 12 Hali ogula birugu binji n’ensaranga nsungunu, n’obwo bamukanzire kali nda kulusha.
\v 13 Omurhimanya anasîmirwe ebinwa byâge, n’okuhâna kw’omuhwinja kuhere busha.
\v 14 Ebi omusirhe ahâna birhaciza, bulya abikonolîre amasù mpu omugalulire kali kangana halya.
\v 15 Oku arhahanyiri bici, abulihûna kulusha, anahâne nk’owahamagaza, ene akuhoze, irhondo ayishikulyûza: aba wa kukobwa.
\v 16 Omusirhe anaderhe, erhi: «Ntajira mwîra, mbona mpâna ci ntabona cavuga omunkwa,
\v 17 abalya ebyâni bajira akalimi kabî». Owa bene oyo barhahwa barhamushekera.
\s1 Akanwa kabî
\p 
\v 18 Okusârhala n’amagulu kwo kukulu aha kusârhala n’olulimi; isârhala lya bene eryo lirhahumba mubî.
\v 19 Omuhwinja kw’ali nka lulibi, ebinganyi bilujire lwimbo.
\v 20 Ecihwinja cirhatwa mugani gwâkungwa, cihabe amango abandi bagutwa.
\v 21 Hali oyu obukenyi bubêra mpenzi ya kurhanga ecâha, amango g’okurhamûka, omurhima gurhamulya.
\v 22 Hali ocîheza erhi nshonyi zirhuma, acîheze mpu akenga omusirhe.
\v 23 Hali olaganyiza omwîra wâge omu bwôba, hayishizûka enshombo y’obumâma.
\s1 Obunywesi
\p 
\v 24 Okunywerha kubà kucîshûbula bwenêne, kurhahwa ekanwa k’ebinganyi.
\v 25 Ecishambo co cikulu aha munywesi mukulu, cikwône bombi kuhera banahera.
\v 26 Enkômedu y’okunywerha bubà buhanya, n’omunywesi nshonyi zirhahwa zirhamubumbiri.
\s1 Obukulu n’embaka z’omurhimanya
\p 
\v 27 Omurhimanya acîkengêsa n’ebinwa byâge, n’omuntu mwenge ye abakulu basîma.
\v 28 Omuhinzi kusârûla asârûla, n’osîmwa n’abakulu, anatumule anabuli babalirwa.
\v 29 Okushegulwa n’okurhûlwa binarhume abagula bahûrha amasù, kubè kubashwêka akanwa mpu bakanaderha.
\v 30 Oburhimanya bufulike n’obuhirhi bubishe, bunguke buci bijira?
\v 31 Omuntu wafulika isirhe lyâge, ye mukulu oku wafulika oburhimanya bwâge.
\c 21
\s1 Embero z’ebyâha
\p 
\v 1 Mwâna wâni, ka wajizire ecâha? Orhacishubiriraga, ohûne obwonjo oku byâha byâwe byoshi bya mîra.
\v 2 Oyâke ecâha kula onayâka enjoka: okaciyegera, cakuluma, amîno gâco gali nka ga mpangaza, go gazigulula abalume.
\v 3 Ngasi câha ebà ngôrho ya môji abiri, aha yatwâga hanajè akafinjo.
\v 4 Obukali n’entambala, kwo n’enyumpa ya cibone eshâbûka ntyo.
\v 5 Omusengero gw’omukenyi omu marhwiri ga Nyamuzinda guhika, n’okushuza kwâge kurhalegama.
\v 6 Orhasîma bamukalihire, kajira ka banya-byâha akulikira, orhînya Nyamuzinda yêhe murhima agalula.
\v 7 Kishiderha anajè irenge hoshi-hoshi, ci omuntu w’obukengêre arhahabiri obuzamba bw’okwo.
\v 8 Okuyûbaka aha mwâwe n’ebirugu bya bene, kuli kucîhumbira enshinda wanabona nko’olunda amabuye omu mpondo.
\v 9 Endêko y’ababî, nsinga ya muliro, obuzinda bwâyo kukwêbwa ecîko.
\v 10 Enjira y’ababî erhahimwa kukoma, ci ekuzimu\f + \fr 21, 10 \fk Ekuzimu\ft : lolà \xt Mat 7, 13\xt*\ft .\f* ehêka.
\s1 Omurhimanya n’omusirhe
\p 
\v 11 Omuntu oshîbirira irhegeko kushuba ashuba oku magene gâge, obwimâna bw’okurhînya Nyamuzinda bubà burhimanya.
\v 12 Hali oyâbirwa n’okucîyigîriza, kubula irhwe kurhuma, ci haligi n’ôbà agwêrhe eyo nshôkano y’irhwe emurhindibuze.
\v 13 Omurhimanya ebà nyenga ya bumanye, n’obulonza bwâge, iriba lya nshongôle.
\v 14 Omurhima gw’omusirhe, ndaha mbêre, yo erhabîka bici.
\v 15 Omuntu mwenge akayumva akanwa kinjà, anakabîke emurhima, ayûshûlekwo n’akâge; leka omusirhe akayumve, asheke, kwo na kuyîbagira.
\v 16 Ebinwa by’omusirhe bibà nka muzigo guyâbire omubalama, ci ekanwa k’omurhimanya binjà biyirhenga.
\v 17 Akanwa k’omuntu nkana basîma okukâyumva omu ndêko, oku adesire, ngasi muguma anakuhire emurhima.
\v 18 Nyumpa ya mushaka bwo burhimanya bw’ecihwinja, n’obumanye bw’omusirhe, binwa birhagwêrhi nda na mugongo.
\v 19 Emw’omusirhe, enjira ly’akalamo gubà mugozi emagulu, kabangiro emaboko.
\v 20 Omusirhe nk’asheka, analinzi basha, ocîkenzire yêhe kugera agera amasheka gâge.
\v 21 Emw’omuntu nkana, irhegeko gali masholo ga bulimbi, ngolo ekuboko kulyo.
\v 22 Ecinganyi cinacîshokoze okudâha, omuntu mwenge arhangibà nk’alinda;
\v 23 ecinganyi cinakâhengûliza oku lumvi, omuntu ocîkenzire anabè nk’acîyêgûla.
\v 24 Okuyumvîrhiza aha lumvi kubà kwa muntu orhaleragwa, nshonyi kubonêsa omuntu.
\v 25 Akanwa ka bakadegende karhahwa kujumbulusa ebinwa bya bene, enderho z’abarhimanya zôhe zijira olugero.
\v 26 Omurhima gw’ebinganyi ekanwa gubà, ci akanwa k’abarhimanya, murhima gwâbo.
\v 27 Omubî anahehêrere omushombanyi wâge, n’obwo yêne ocîhehêrire.
\v 28 Omuntu ohambâra abâbo, yêne ocîkolera amabî, kushombwa ashombwa n’abalungu bâge.
\c 22
\s1 Omwolo
\p 
\v 1 Omwôlo kwo ali nk’ibuye banîrekwo, ngasi wagera na kuheba olushungûrho.
\v 2 Omwôlo kwo ali nka camvu ca njalira, mazingonoko, ngasi ogahumakwo kuhôrhola anahôrhola enfune.
\s1 Emifiriri y’abâna
\p 
\v 3 Zibà nshonyi z’omulume okuburha ecirala c’omurhabana, ci okuburha ecirala c’omunyere kôhe kulengana bwenêne.
\v 4 Omunyere nkana, buhirhi bw’owamuyanka, ci omunyere mubî, mungo gw’owamuburhaga.
\v 5 Cikala-nshonyi w’omunyere, îshe na nnina azibonêsa, bombi kukaga bamukaga.
\v 6 Obukali burhagwêrhi lugero, lwimbo lwa mishîbo, ci okushûrha n’okuhanûla bubà burhimanya bukwânîne\f + \fr 22, 6 \ft Bukwânîne: okuhana n’okushûrha: lolà \xt Mig 13, 24; 19, 18; 22, 15; 23, 13-14; 29, 15-17\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 7 Abâna bagwêrhe ecibâlya banali bîrhonzi, banabuke ababusi bâbo omungo.
\v 8 Abâna bagayanyi na mbula bukenge, banajâcize obwôrhere bwinjà bw’omulala gwâbo.
\s1 Oburhimanya n’isirhe
\p 
\v 9 Okuyigîriza omusirhe kubà kuhanga orhujo, kubà kuzûsa omuntu wafîre n’îrò.
\v 10 Okuhanûla omusirhe, kubà kuhanûla omuntu oli îrò, buzinda akudôse, mpu: «Bici ebyo?»
\v 11 Olakire ofîre: agenzire, arhakàcibona izûba, olakire omusirhe: arhacigwêrhi murhima, gwahûsire; kunyi wâlakira ofîre, bulya kurhamûka ajire, ci kuli omusirhe, olufù lwo lukulu aha kalamo kâge.
\v 12 Emishîbo y’ofîre zibà nsiku nda, ey’omusirhe n’omubî, nsiku zoshi z’akalamo kâbo.
\v 13 Orhabwîraga omusirhe binwa binji-binji, orhajâga ciru emund’ali, omanye akulêrhera embaka za busha, omanye akuzinza. Omuyâke, wabona omurhûla, ebihenyango byâge birhacikulibuze.
\v 14 Bicigi bizirho kulusha amabuye? Kurhi biderhwa? Cingolongolo.
\v 15 Omushenyi, omunyu, enundo y’ebyûma, byo byangu by’okubarhulwa aha cingolongolo.
\v 16 Oburhungiri buyûbake n’emirhi mizibu, burhagagajwa na musisi, omurhima gurhanziricîdôsa gubulihiga, gurhahombagana omu mango g’entambala.
\v 17 Omurhima guyêgemîre enkengêro z’oburhimanya, guli nka kulya bayinjihya olukûta n’irangi lyananîra bwinjà.
\v 18 Orhubuye rhutya-rhutya ah’irhwêrhwè ly’olukûta, rhurhalindira mpûsi, omurhima gw’ecingolongolo ebi gugerêreza byo binaguyôbohya.
\s1 Obwîra
\p 
\v 19 Bakashûrha isù, linadwe emirenge, bakahika omuntu oku nyomvu y’omurhima, banamanye ecikuli.
\v 20 Obanda irongo, abalaza orhunyunyi, ohangâla omwîra, bwîra ayîrha.
\v 21 Akabà wayômolîre omwîra engôrho, orharhâga omurhima, kwankanabà acigaluka;
\v 22 akabà waderhire omwîra kubî, orhayôbohaga, mwanaciyumvanya; ci omuhè rubanda, hoshi aho, obwîra bunafè.
\v 23 Mulungu wâwe akenyîre, mulole bwinjà, hano agâla, wasîma haguma naye; akajakwo obuhanya, orhamurhibagamwo, hano afuma olwo, mwe naye mwagabâna ebyâge.
\v 24 Engulumira mugî guyishokolera, kwo n’okwo bijâci bishokolera omukò.
\v 25 Ntakabà nshonyi z’okufungira omwîra, ntakanacîfulika ye.
\v 26 Akabâga ye n’enganya, abandi bakuyumva bamujire ndyâlya.
\s1 Obè masù
\p 
\v 27 Lêro ndi wakampira omulanzi oku kanwa, ahîre omu binwa byâni ecinwa c’obukengêre, lyo ndekisârhala byo birhumire, olulimi lulekimpeza?
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 Yâgirwa Nyamuzinda, we Larha we na Nnawâbo akalamo kâni, orhandekaga omu magene gâhyo, orhayêmêraga nasârhala muli byo.
\v 2 Lêro ndi wayêreka enkengêro zâni omu za omurhima gwâni, aguyêreke ihano ly’oburhimanya, aleke okuntogoza amango mpabusire, ndekiyûbakwa n’ebyâha.
\v 3 Ntyo, amabî gâni garhayushuke, ebyâha byâni birhaluge, ndeke okuhirima omu maboko g’abashombanyi bâni, omushombanyi wâni abule aha angwârhira.
\v 4 Nyakasane-k’emirenge, Larha na Nyamuzinda w’akalamo kâni, ontabâle nyâke obucîbone.
\v 5 Oncînge oku bwâgalwa,
\v 6 amagene n’amîru mabî garhampimaga, orhanampânaga emunda enyifinjo mbî ziri.
\s1 Endahiro
\p 
\v 7 Mwe bâna, muyumve ebinwa byâni, obikulikîre arhakabulabula.
\v 8 Omunya-byâha yêne ocîshwêka n’ebinwa byâge, byo bihirimya omuhambûzi n’omucîbonyi.
\v 9 Lek’enkômedu y’okucîgasha, orhakômerere okulahira izîno ly’Omwimâna.
\v 10 Kul’omubôyi barhangula ngasi kasanzi arhafuma mpimbo, kwo n’omuntu ocîgasha n’okuderhaderha izîno lya Nyamuzinda, arhafuma ecâha.
\v 11 Omuntu osîma okucîgasha ali mubî, obuhanya burharhenga aha mwâge. Akajira ecâha, ecâha câge cimuhonere; akaderha mpu ahalîza, abîhire kabiri; akalahira ebirà, arhafungirwe, obuhanya bwamuhandira aha ka.
\s1 Ebinwa bibî
\p 
\v 12 Hali iderha liyâkuza olufù, okwo ntà mango kubâge muli bene Yakôbo, bulya abantu nkana barhakwirirwa ntyo, barhacîjandika n’omu câha.
\v 13 Orhakômerezagya akanwa kâwe eby’obûmaguza, byo bibamo akanwa k’ecâha.
\v 14 Kengêra sho na nyoko amango oli ekarhî k’abakulu, omanye wacîjandaga embere zâbo, kubè kuyôrha nka cingolongolo, obone wamacînfinja abarhaburhagwa, otumuze olusiku waburhagwa.
\v 15 Omuntu wakômerîre ebinwa bibî arhakubûlwa.
\v 16 Hali bibiri biluza ebyâha, n’ecâha kasharhu cilerhe oburhè;
\v 17 gala mîru gayôca nka muliro, garhatwîka garhanayîgusiri, omuntu ocîfinja omubiri gwâge yêne, arhâlèkè n’omuliro gurhacimuyôca, oku muntu mûmaguza, ngasi biryo erhi binunu, lufù lwo lwamutwa amîru.
\v 18 Omuntu ojirira ecâha aha ncingo yâge, n’okuderha, erhi: «Ndi wambona? Omwizimya gundi eburhambi, ebizimbêro bincîkirize, ntâye wambona, bicigi nayôboha? Ow’Enyanya arhankakengera ebyâha byâni».
\v 19 Oyo masù ga bantu gône ayôbohire, arhamanyiri oku amasù ga Nyamuzinda, galushire izûba bumoleke kali bihumbi ikumi, oku ganabône ebijiro by’abantu byoshi, gahike n’omu ngasi hyongobana.
\v 20 Embere aleme, ali ayishi ebintu byoshi, n’erhi ayûsa kwo n’okwo.
\v 21 Oyo muntu omu lugo ahanirwa, obuhanya bwamamurhibukira amango arhalâlîri.
\s1 Omukazi mugonyi
\p 
\v 22 Omukazi ohemukira ibà naye kw’ali ntyo, anamulêrhere omwâna w’embuga mpu yo nfula.
\v 23 Burhanzi avunyire irhegeko lya Nyamuzinda, kandi abîhîre îba; n’obwa kasharhu acîshûbwîre n’okuhusha, haguma n’okwôla kujishunda abâna embuga.
\v 24 Omu ndêko bâheka olubanja lwâge, n’abâna bâge babasingirize.
\v 25 Abâna bâge barhâmerekwo muzî, amashami gâge garhajekwo hiciza.
\v 26 Bakazimukengêrera okuhehêrerwa ahehêrîrwe, na ntâye wamukûle enshonyi.
\v 27 Ntyo, abâli enyuma zâge bamanya oku okurhînya Nyamuzinda kwône kushingânine, n’oku ntà cinjà cilushire okushimba amarhegeko gâge.
\c 24
\s1 Oburhimanya bwaderha nka muntu
\p 
\v 1 Oburhimanya bukolaga bwacivuga, bukolaga bwarhangifekembera omu karhî k’olubaga\f + \fr 24, 1 \ft Oburhimanya bwaderha: ahâla oburhimanya kwo buli nka muntu, n’eci cigabi kwo ciri nka murhima gw’eci citabu. Lolà \xt Mig 8, 22\xt*\ft . Omu Liturjiya katolika, ebi binwa Ekleziya ebiyêrekezize Bikira Mariya.\f*.
\v 2 Bwamâderha ntya omu ndêko y’Ow’enyanya, bwamâyêrekana irenge lyâbwo embere z’Obuhashe, erhi:
\v 3 «Ndi nkonôka y’oku Kanwa k’Ow’Enyanya, nayisha nacîbulula nka lwikungu nabwîkira igulu.
\v 4 “Aha mwâni, emalunga, entebe yâni gwàli mulunga gwa bitù”.
\v 5 “Niene, kuno na ndi, nazungulusire engo y’emalunga, najîre kuli kuhika ekuzimu”.
\v 6 “Obwâmi bwâmi bwagandazize omu nyanja, omu igulu, oku ngasi lubaga n’oku ngasi cihugo”.
\v 7 “Emwa boshi nalonzize ahantu nâdêkerera, nalonzize ngahi nâgwîke icumbi lyâni”.
\v 8 “Lêro Lulema w’igulu anacimpa irhegeko, owandemaga angwikîsa ihêma lyâni, àmbwîra”, erhi: “Yûbaka muli Yakôbo, ojè omu kashambala k’Israheli”.
\v 9 “Embere ly’amango, kurhenga omurhondêro ly’andemaga, ensiku n’amango erhi ho mbà”.
\v 10 “Omu cihando citagatîfu, embere zâge nagashâniza, na ntyo nacumbika omu Siyoni\f + \fr 24, 10 \ft Narhumikîre omukolo omu ka-Nyamuzinda guli mukolo gwa Burhimanya: lolà \xt 24, 23\xt*\ft …\f*,”
\v 11 “nabêra omu Kinjà k’olugo, omu Yeruzalemu mwo obuhashe bwâni bubà”.
\v 12 “Namezire emizî emw’olubaga lw’irenge, omu kwa Nyamuzinda, omu cishumba câge”.
\v 13 “Nakuliremwo nka nduluma y’e Libano, nka murhi oku ntondo ya Hermoni”.
\v 14 “Nakula nka mubô gw’En-Gadi, nka mirhô ya bwâso bw’e Yeriko, nka muzêti gunagîrîre omu lubanda, nakula nka nduluma ya murhi”.
\v 15 “Obwehe bwâni buli nk’obw’ecinamoma na nk’obw’omusipalata, akisûnunu kâni kali nk’ak’enshangi ntumîrira, nk’ak’egalbanumo, onikisi n’obubâni, nka cidûrhu ca nshangi omu Cihando”.
\v 16 “Nalandiza amashami nka murhi gwa terbenta, mashami ga bwinjà n’irenge”.
\v 17 “Kwo ndi nka muzâbîbu gulandizize emirhô minjà-minjà, n’obwâso bwâni ebà mburho y’irenge n’obuhirhi”.
\v 18 “[Nie nnina w’obuzigire nkana, nie nnina w’olukengwa, nnina w’obumanye n’obulangâlire; nahîrwe lwoshi abâna bâni boshi, balya Yêne agoshôlaga kurhenga ensiku n’amango.]\f + \fr 24, 18 \ft Obushinganyanya bwayishigererwako Yezu Kristu. Lolà \xt Ywn 14, 6\xt*\ft .\f*”
\v 19 “Muyishe emwâni, mwe mucînyifinja, mulye oku mburho yâni”.
\v 20 “Bulya okunkengêra kulushire obununu bw’obûci, akashambala kâni ko kinjà aha cigukulu c’obûci”.
\v 21 “Abandya barhakaleka okushwîra emunda ndi, n’abanywa barhakagambwa”.
\v 22 “Oyumva ebi mmubwîra, arhankabibêra burhè, n’abajira emikolo yâni barhakahirima omu câha”».
\s1 Oburhimanya n’Irhegeko
\p 
\v 23 Ebyo byoshi citabu c’Endagâno ya Nyamuzinda w’Enyanya eco. Irhegeko lyàmanyisibagwa na Mûsa, ko kashambala kàsigiragwa endêko za Yakôbo.
\v 24 Murhalekaga okucîzibuhya muli Nyakasane, mumusêrekwo lyo amuzibuhya, Nyakasane w’Emirhwe yêne Nyamuzinda, buziraye, ntawundi mu­ciza.
\v 25 Er’Irhegeko lyo liluza oburhimanya nka mîshi ga Pishone, nka kula olwîshi lwa Tigre luyunjula amango emyâka eyêzire;
\v 26 lyo liluza obukengêre nka mîshi g’Efrati, nk’aga Yordani amango bakalala;
\v 27 lyo lihâna enjira nk’olwîshi lwa Nili, na nka Gihîni omu nsiku bahumbûla emizâbîbu.
\v 28 Oku omurhanzi arhaciyûsa okulimya, kwo n’omuzinda aciri kulî nalyo.
\v 29 Bulya obukengêre bwalyo bulushire enyanja bunji, n’emihigo yalyo yo miri kulusha enyenga.
\v 30 Niono, kwo ndi nka mubunda gwârhenga omu lwîshi, nka hîshi hihesire omu ishwa ly’amasîma.
\v 31 Nàdesire, nti: «Nkola nadômerera omu kwâni, ngeze amîshi omu ishwa lyâni». Lêro nabona omubunda gwâni gwahinduka lwîshi, n’olwîshi yashuba nyanja.
\v 32 Nkolaga nalomeka enjira kurhenga sêzi, akamole kabone kuhika emahanga.
\v 33 Navangula enyigîrizo nka bulêbi, zihike n’oku maburhwa gali nyuma.
\v 34 K’obwîne: arhali nie nacîlongeza, ci nakolera balya boshi bazilonza.
\c 25
\s1 Emigani
\p 
\v 1 Hali bisharhu omurhima gwâni gucîfinja, birhahimwa kusîmîsa Nyamuzinda n’abantu; okuyumvanya kw’abaguma, enyumpa omulume na mukâge bayumvanyamwo.
\v 2 Haligi na bantu basharhu omurhima gwâni gurhabonakwo, na nkayumva oku ho bacibà nnânshologorhwe; omukenyi w’obucîbone, omugale munywesi, omushosi w’enkonola-masù bagwârha omu mwa bene.
\s1 Abashosi
\p 
\v 3 Amango orhabikaga ociri musole, bici wabonage okola mushosi?
\v 4 Alà nka zayinjiha emvi zigwêrhe ihano! Okumanya ihano kw’abakulûkulu nako kuyinjiha.
\v 5 Alà nka bwayinjiha oburhimanya bw’abashosi, n’obukengêre bwinjà bw’abakulu b’er’igulu.
\v 6 Irenge ly’abashosi kuli kulya kubà «Babwîne binji», okulimba kwâbo kunali kulya «Babwîne binji», okulimba kwâbo kunali kulya kurhînya Nyamuzinda. Okurhînya Nyamuzinda bwône bukulu
\v 7 Hali bintu mwenda nkengîre\f + \fr 25, 7 \ft Abashombanyi bahirime: Nnawîrhu Yezu Kristu arhegesire rhuzigire abantu boshi, ciru n’abashombanyi bîrhu, lolà \xt Mat 5, 44; Luk 6, 27-35\xt*\ft .\f*, nambwîne oku birimwo iragi, n’eca kali ikumi nakubwiraco: Omuntu obona omwîshingo omw’iburha lyâge, ye obona omu kalamo kâge oku abashombanyi bâge baherêrekera;
\v 8 Iragi lyâge ojira omukazi mwîrhonzi, omuntu orhahingan’empanzi na punda, omuntu erhasâgijira ecâha omu nderho, omuntu wabwîne omushigo mwinjà.
\v 9 Iragi lyâge owahisire oku bwîrhonzi, n’obwîra owayumva.
\v 10 Nêci, ali mukulu owahisire oku burhimanya, ci ntâye ocilushire orhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 11 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda kurhalusire byoshi, owahisire aho, bici ankagererwakwo?
\s1 Abakazi babî
\p 
\v 12 Okurhînya Nyakasane gwo gubà murhondêro gw’obuzigire bwâge, ci, oku buyêmêre barhondêrera n’okumusêrako.
\v 13 Oyâgalike ci orhayâgalikaga omurhima! oshimbe obumînya, ci orhashimânaga obumînya bw’omukazi!
\v 14 Bubè buhanya, ci burhabâga bwa kuhubuka emw’omubisha! bubè bulyâlya, ci burhabâga bwa kuhubuka emw’omushombanyi!
\v 15 Ntà bwôge bubî kulusha amanjokanjokà, ntà nshombo nkulu kulusha ey’omubisha.
\v 16 Okubêra haguma n’empangaza erhi enkuba-joka, kwo kukulu aha kubêra nyumpa nguma n’omukazi mumînya.
\v 17 Obumînya bw’omukazi bunamuhindule obusù, abange enzizi, omanye mpu akola ciryanyi.
\v 18 Oku ibà ali oku mêza haguma n’abalungu bâge, erhi adwîrhe adwîra n’omu nda nk’ihiri.
\v 19 Obumînya bwoshi ntabwo buhisire oku buminya bw’omukazi: mâshi! abona eci abanya-byâha babona!
\v 20 Nsinga ya mushenyi omu magulu g’omushosi, ye mukazi w’akalimi aha mw’omulume w’omurhûla.
\v 21 Omanye warhebwa n’iranga ly’omukazi, orhahîra okaleka omukazi akubuza murhima.
\v 22 Kurhahimwa kujira omuntu burhè, kumubulîse obukenge, kunamubonêse nshonyi, okuyumva mpu mukà lebè yekola obîka ibà.
\v 23 Burhè omu murhima, burhè emalanga, cibande cifulike, gwo mukolo gw’omukazi mumînya. Maboko gahozire, madwî gakomanya, ye mukazi ohanyagaza îba.
\v 24 Ecâha oku mukazi càrhondêreraga, na mukazi warhumire rhweshi rhukafà.
\v 25 Orhasîkûliraga amîshi, orhahâga n’omukazi mumînya oluhyà lw’okuderha.
\v 26 Akabà arhayumvîrhiri oku munwe erhi omu masù, omuyâke.
\c 26
\s1 Omukazi mwinjà n’omubî
\p 
\v 1 Iragi lyâge omulume ojira omukazi nkana, omubalè gw’ensiku zâge gwayûshûka kabiri.
\v 2 Omukazi nkana busîme emw’ibà, ibà alama n’omurhûla emyâka yâge yoshi.
\v 3 Omukazi nkana ebà nshôkano yâgoyâgo, eshobâlwa n’abalume barhînya Nyamuzinda.
\v 4 Babè bagale erhi bakenyi, busîme buli emurhima gwâbo, ensiku zoshi busù bwa nshagali.
\v 5 Hali bisharhu nyôboha: n’eca kani musisi cingezâmwo: obunywesi bulumira eka, okunyagwa kw’olubaga, okuhêka owundi lubanja oku busha: ebyo bibà bibî kulusha olufù;
\v 6 ci kuli nka kurhîngamira omuntu, gali malumwa omukazi okuyâgalwa n’owâbo, okwo kwoshi abâ nyamanjà olêrhwa n’akalimi.
\v 7 Omukazi mumînya, murhamba gwa mpanzi bashwêsire kubî; okacîhamba mpu wamugombya kuli kugwârha cilumira-habiri.
\v 8 Omukazi mulalwè ali wakujira omuntu burhè, enshonyi acîbonêsa zirhayibagirwa.
\v 9 Omukazi w’ecirala omu masù abonekera, kukema-kema kwâge kumuyêrekana.
\v 10 Omanye omunyere oyengehusire kubî, orhamufume hano abona obuzamba bwâwe.
\v 11 Omanye amasù gahwîremwo enshonyi, orhacisômeragwa hano gakuhira omu mashumi.
\v 12 Kw’ayâshama aka mubalama enyôrha egwêrhe, amîshi ashimanyire go ananywa, obugonyi bwâge ntaho arhabuhêka, omubiri gwâge aha ngasi mulindizo agurhege ngasi myampi-izinga.
\v 13 Obwinjà bw’omukazi busîme bulêrhera ibà, obukengêre bwâge misî bumuyûshûlira.
\v 14 Omukazi orhaderhêra ebà ngalo ya Nyamuzinda, oyu balezire bwinjà ntâco ankagererwakwo.
\v 15 Omukazi ocîkenga abà mwinjà kabiri, ow’omurhima gucîre arhagwêrhi buhirhi akagererwako.
\v 16 Kul’izûba lishoshôka oku ntondo za Nyamuzinda, kwo n’obwinjà bw’omukazi buyôrha omu nyumpa alimo.
\v 17 Kula akamole kanayôrha emugamba omu ka-Nyamuzinda, kwo n’iranga linjà linayôrha oku mubiri gw’omwâna hya.
\v 18 Mitungo ya masholo omu ciriba c’ebyûma, amagulu minjà oku rhunsisirha rhuzibu.
\v 19 «Mwâna wâni, omanye wahemula obusole bwâwe n’emisî yâwe orhayihâga abanya-mahanga.
\v 20 Hano ôbà wamalonza ishwa liyêra kulusha agandi g’omu cihugo, orhwêremwo emburho yâwe, kucîkubagira oburhwa bw’obûko bwâwe kurhumire.
\v 21 Ntyo, abâna wânasige bayishikâcîkunga, bulya bamanyire oku ziri ntwâli.
\v 22 Omukazi omuntu arhizagya arhali ciru nka bikâyiza, omukazi w’obuyumpa abà muzibu nka mulunga (gwa lufù).
\v 23 Omukazi w’ecishungu ayishigabirwa omunya-byâha, omukazi mwîrhonzi ayishihâbwa omuntu orhînya Nyakasane.
\v 24 Omukazi mûmaguza wahwîre kw’enshonyi kuzigira azigira okuhemuka, omukazi orhayûmaguza bwinjà ayôrha, ciru na nk’ali n’ibà.
\v 25 Entwâli y’omukazi erhakengwa kulusha akabwa, cikwône omukazi mwîrhohye kuyôboha ayôboha Nyakasane.
\v 26 Omukazi okengêsa ibà abâ murhimanya omu masù ga boshi, cikwône obonêsa ibà nshonyi, kugayaguzibwa agayaguzibwa omu bucîbone bwâge. Ali muny’iragi omulume ojira omukazi nkana, bulya omubalè gw’ensiku zâge hano igulu gwayûshûka kabirhi.
\v 27 Omukazi oderhaderha na w’akajamwe gubà mushekera gutula entambala, ngasi mulume ojira owamwen’oyo arhahwa ntambala omu kalamo kâge.»
\s1 Ebintu by’oburhè
\p 
\v 28 Hali bibiri nyumva bindumire n’eca kasharhu candwâza ecirungula: okubona owafungiraga ecihugo afà bushosi omu buligo, okubona abantu barhimanya bahirwakwo akagayo, omuntu ocîrhenza omu njira nyinjà ajà omu y’ecâha, yêhe ngôrho ya Nyamuzinda yamuyîrha.
\s1 Oburhunzi
\p 
\v 29 Oku murhunzi, okuhima amashumi kuli kuzibu, omugulirwa, kuzibu okuyâka ecâha.
\c 27
\p 
\v 1 Banji bahirima omu câha erhi kusîma obunguke kurhuma, owalonza obugale arhafà bwonjo.
\v 2 Banafunde omurhi ekarhî k’amabuye gagwârhîne, ekarhî k’okugula n’okuguza ecâha ciyijà.
\v 3 Omuntu orhasêzizi okurhînya Nyamuzinda, enyumpa yâge erhi yanajire oku idaho.
\s1 Enderho
\p 
\v 4 Nka bashebula ensheke zinasigale oku kayungiro, kwo n’okwo binwa bya muntu bimanyîsa ishembo lyâge.
\v 5 Omubumbi muliro arhangulamwo obuzibu bw’enyungu zâge, omuntu naye binwa byâge bamurhangulamwo.
\v 6 Ishwa limanyirwa oku mburho yarhengamwo, kwo n’okwo ebinwa by’omuntu bimanyîsa eciri emurhima gwâge.
\v 7 Orhakungaga omuntu embere oyumve eci adesire, aho ho wamugwârhira.
\s1 Obushinganyanya
\p 
\v 8 Erhi wakakulikira obushinganyanya, wanabuhikakwo, obuyambale obwo nka mwambalo gwa lusiku lukulu.
\v 9 Ecihungu cirhagwa aharhali câbo, obushinganyanya bulonza obukulikire.
\v 10 Entale kulingûza eringûza omunyama gwâyo, ecâha naco cisîma abalyâlyanya.
\v 11 Ebinwa by’omuntu nkana ensiku zoshi kurhimanya, ci ecingolongolo kwo cihinduka nka mwêzi.
\v 12 Nk’oli mwe n’ebingolongolo, onagere amango, ci nk’oli mwe n’abantu nkana, ogende buzira bwôba.
\v 13 Ebinwa by’abahwinja bibî bya kushologosa, okusheka kwâbo erhi kucishingira byâha.
\v 14 Ebinwa by’osîma okucîgasha, binarhume emviri ziri oku irhwe ly’omuntu zagurumanwa. Okulongôla kwâge kunafuke abantu amarhwîri.
\v 15 Okulongôla kw’abacîbonyi mukò kubulaga, n’ebijâci byâbo bibî bya kushaza.
\s1 Amahwe
\p 
\v 16 Omuntu obêra amahwe arhalangâlirwa, na ntà mwîra nkana abona.
\v 17 Osîme onalangâlire omwîra wâwe, ci olusiku wâbera amahwe gâge, erhi na hoshi aho obwîra bwamâfà;
\v 18 bulya kwo wayîsire obwîra nka kula bayîrha omubisha.
\v 19 Kul’omuntu akanalîka akanyunyi afumbîrhe, kacîbalalira, kwo nâwe walîsire omwîra, orhâcimubone.
\v 20 Orhamukulikiraga, mîra akol’ali kulî, acîgendîre kula akashafu kayâka omurhego.
\v 21 Banarhube ecihulu, bababalire n’ecijâci, ci omuntu wabasize ihwe, nanga.
\s1 Obulyâlya
\p 
\v 22 Omuntu okomakomya erhi bulyâlya adwîrhe asinga, na ntâye wamurhanga.
\v 23 Amango ali embere zâwe, ye lûbika, ebinwa byâwe binamurhwe yêshi, buzinda akunioke, akuderhere oku orhadesire, aderhe mpu wajâcire lebè.
\v 24 Nshomba binji, ci oyo muntu ntamubonakwo, na Nyamuzinda arhamusîma.
\v 25 Obanda ibuye emalunga, ah’irhwe acibandalyo, olibandira obulenzi yêne ocîrenganya.
\v 26 Ohumba omwîna, agurhogeramwo, orhega omurhego gunamugwârhe.
\v 27 Ecibî cirha nnaco, arhamanya ciru olunda cahubuka.
\v 28 Akanege n’ebijâci bibà bya mucîbonyi, ci kwône olwihôlo lumulingûzize nka ntale.
\v 29 Omu murhego bagwa abantu bacîshingira okuhanyagala kw’abantu binjà, abôla amagala gabalya embere bafè.
\s1 Obumvu
\p 
\v 30 Obumvu n’obukunizi nabyo bindi bikabulirwa, bimera omu ishwa ly’enkola-maligo.
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 Omuntu ocîhôla naye arhâfume olwihôlo lwa Nyamuzinda, Nyamuzinda ye yishi oku ebyâha biganjwa.
\v 2 Babalira owinyu obubî bwâge, lyo nâwe, hano oshenga, obabalirwa.
\v 3 Kurhi omuntu obikîre owâbo obumvu akashenga mpu Nyamuzinda amufumye?
\v 4 Omuntu orhaba bwonjo oku wâbo, kurhi akashenga mpu yêhe abâge ye babalirwa?
\v 5 Ye muntu kwône abîkîre owâbo omujina, ndigi yeki abwîne wamubabalira?
\v 6 Kengêra obuzinda, oleke okushombana, kengêra okufà n’okubola, oshimbe n’amarhegeko.
\v 7 Kengêra amarhegeko, oleke okubîka omujina, okuze endagâno y’Ow’enyanya, oyîbagire ecijâci.
\s1 Entambala
\p 
\v 8 Oyâke entambala, wayâka ecâha, omuntu w’amagene ye nyankozi omu bâbo.
\v 9 Omubî kavango ahira omu bîra, ye côkêza-malambo ekarhî k’abantu barhulwîre.
\v 10 Oku enshâli ziri kwo n’omuliro gugulumira, oku entambala ekozîbwe, kw’enaluga. Omuntu arûkûza nk’oku emisî yâge enali, n’oku obugale bwâge buli, kw’anakunira.
\v 11 Entambala y’obushâlashâla enazûse omuliro, ennongwè y’obuhwinja enabulage omukò.
\v 12 Bûha oku isèsè omuliro guyâke, ogutwîreko guzime, obonereho obuhashe bw’akanwa kâwe.
\s1 Olulimi
\p 
\v 13 Omanye kadegende n’enderhera-habiri, abo bombi bahezize abantu balicîbêrire omu murhûla.
\v 14 Akalimi kàyimusize bantu banji, kabashandâza cihugo omu cindi; kahongwîre ebishagala bizibuzibu, kashâbira n’abarhwâli.
\v 15 Akalimi kahulusize abakazi omu mwâbo, kabanyagîsa emyâka yâbo.
\v 16 Oyumvîrhiza omudesi-wagwo arhaja îrò, anabule omurhûla.
\v 17 Bashûrhe omuntu akarhi, kasiga omubambu, bamushûrhe akalimi, kamujonjaga yêshi.
\v 18 Bantu banji bafîre n’engôrho, ci abafîre n’akalimi bo banji kulusha.
\v 19 Iragi lyâge oyu karhasâgihikakwo, oyu karhali omu njira yâge, oyu karhasâgijira mujà wako, oyu karhasâgiziriringa n’emigozi yako.
\v 20 Obujà bwâko bubà bujà buzibu, n’emigozi yako, migozi ya budagulè.
\v 21 Olufù lwâko, lufù lubî bwenêne, ekuzimu yo nkulu kuli lwo.
\v 22 Akalimi karhahasha abantu barhînya Nyamuzinda, engulumira yako erhabayâsha.
\v 23 Abacîrhenza kuli Nyamuzinda, yo minyama yako, engulumira yako erhazima muli bo, kwo kabahiva nka ntale, kabashangule nka ngwi.
\v 24 Yumva: oyûbake ecôgo c’emishûgi aha mwâwe, osêze ebirugu n’obugale bwâwe.
\v 25 Ohire enderho zâwe oku munzâni, ozigere, ohire omurhemere n’igufuli oku kanwa.
\v 26 Omanye wakasârhalira ekanwa, olekigwa omu maboko g’okugungezize.
\c 29
\s1 Okuhoza
\p 
\v 1 Okuhoza owinyu kuli kumufà lukogo, okumurhabâla kuli kushimba amarhegeko.
\v 2 Kuli kwinjà okuhoza owinyu amango alagîrîre, ci kukwânîne okulyûla amango mwalagânîne.
\v 3 Orhatwâga omu kanwa kâwe, onayumvanye n’abandi, n’amango wa­ lagîrira, wabona oburhabâle.
\v 4 Banji bahoza bamanye mpu kubêrwa, bayumîrize balya babàhozagya.
\v 5 Embere ly’okuhoza, kurhângishisha nyakuhôzibwa, kukunga obugale bwâge, olusiku lw’okulyûla lulegerere, lubè lwa mirongwè, oyumve mpu amango gali mabî!
\v 6 Ka balyûla Nyakulyûza akabona ecihimbi c’ebyâge erhi abirîrwe. Akabà arhalyûzirwi, ebirugu bimuhere. kandi abè n’omushombanyi w’obumâma, oku alyûla ajâcira n’okutulagula, ebijâci gubè gwo munkwa bwo na bukenge.
\v 7 Bantu banji --burhali bulonza bubî - balahira kuhoza, barhalonza ebyâbo bihere.
\s1 Okuhâna
\p 
\v 8 Obè wa lukogo oku b’obuligo, orhabayumukizagya aha mwâwe bali­nda oburhabâle.
\v 9 Oshimbe irhegeko, orhabâle omukenyi; alagîrîre, orhamugalulaga maboko mûmu.
\v 10 Ebirugu byâwe bije emwa mwene winyu n’omwîra, birhaboleraga e­ mwîna busha.
\v 11 Okolêse obugale bwâwe nk’oku Nyamuzinda arhegesire, wâgala kulusha.
\v 12 Okuhâna guli muhako gwâwe, gwakuciza amango g’obuhanya.
\v 13 Okuhâna kwo kukulu aha mpenzi nzibu, ah’itumu lyôji, kwâkulwira e­mbêre z’omushombanyi.
\s1 Okucîhâna cikinja
\p 
\v 14 Omuntu nkana anacihâne cikinja erhi wâbo orhuma, bulya okumulîkirira ziri nshonyi nkulu.
\v 15 Orhayîbagiraga aminjà g’owakufungiraga, acîhâna yêne ahâli hâwe.
\v 16 Omubî arhakengêra obwinjà bw’omufungizi, n’omugambanyi anayibagire omuciza.
\v 17 Ecikinja cakenyize àbali bagale, cabahêka eyi n’eyi nka mulaba gw’omu nyanja.
\v 18 Caluliza abantu banênênè, bahabukira omu bihugo, emahanga.
\v 19 Omuminya anashwîre okucîhâna cikinja, mpu ly’ayunguka, n’obwo buhanya ashwirîre.
\v 20 Orhabâle owinyu nk’oku onahashire, ci omanye nâwe wâhirima.
\s1 Okubà cigolo
\p 
\v 21 Akantu karhanzi k’okulama: mîshi, kalyo, mwambalo n’enyumpa y’okulâla.
\v 22 Okubêra mukenyi aha mwâwe, omu nyumpa yâwe y’obukere, kwo kukulu aha kukâyigurhira omu nyumpa nyinjà ya bene.
\v 23 Ogale erhi okene, osîme, orhacijiraga cigolo.
\v 24 Kalamo kabî, okuhandûla ene n’irhondo, aha wankajà, ntà kubumbûla akanwa;
\v 25 oli ho cigolo, n’enshonyi zâwe haguma, n’ebinwa bakubwîra, bya kanego:
\v 26 «Bwîra oyo w’ekulî, ayishe arheganye amêza. arhujirîre ebi rhwâlya».
\v 27 «Ewani sho! orhenge omwo, bulya mwâja owundi w’olukengwa: mwene wîrhu ambalamîre, mwo nanamuhandîsa omwo».
\v 28 Nshonyi ezo muntu w’obukengêre okucinaguzibwa ntyo oku cihando, n’okulolwa nka muntu oli omu mwenda.
\c 30
\s1 Okulera
\p 
\v 1 Omubusi ozigira omwâna wâge arhamurhogoza, irhondo erhi olya mwâna yekola cimala-mungo.
\v 2 Olera bwinjà omwâna wâge âsîma, bâmukûnga ekarhî k’abîra bâge.
\v 3 Oyigîriza bwinjà omwâna wâge, buyâgalwa azukiza omushombanyi wâge, ci busîme ekarhî k’abîra bâge.
\v 4 Ciru îshe w’omwâna mulere akafà, kurhali kufà afîre, bulya asizire oli nka ye.
\v 5 Acizîne, abwîne obusîme muli ye, buno akol’afà, ntà burhè.
\v 6 Asizire entwâli y’okucîhôla oku bashombanyi, asigîre abîra bâge owa­bavuga omunkwa oku minjà bamujirîre.
\v 7 Orhogoza omwâna wâge, acîrheganye n’okukârhuba ebibande, ngasi kuyâma, omurhima gumukangalale.
\v 8 Enfarasi nshwêke kubî enagâmbane, karhagobaga naye kubî akula.
\v 9 Nêci, orhogoze omwâna, kwône acikukanga, omushâse kwône, wâcicîlakira.
\v 10 Orhashekaga mwe naye âkaba orhalonza okulaka mwe naye, wâcizinzibala obusù.
\v 11 Orhamulekêreraga amango acikula, orhazibaga mpu orhagibona obubî bwâge.
\v 12 Omuyumvîse bwinjà oku acikula, ciru n’okumushûrha amango aciri mwâna, bulya cikaba cigamba arhakâkuyumva, n’oburhè bukugwârhe.
\v 13 Lera onahêrhe bwinjà omwâna, ly’oleka okuyishirhindibuka n’obugamba bwâge.
\s1 Amagala minjà
\p 
\v 14 Omukenyi muzibu w’amagala minjà, ye mukulu aha mugale w’amagala magalugalu.
\v 15 Amagala minjà n’emisî bilushire obuhirhi bwoshi bw’igulu, amagala mazibu galushire obugale.
\v 16 Ntà buhirhi bulushire amagala, na ntà bugale bulushire obusîme bw’omurhima.
\v 17 Olufù lwo lukulu aha kalamo k’omutula, obuluhûke bw’ensiku n’amango bwo bwinjà aha ndwâla erhafuma.
\v 18 Okuhira entûlo aha nshinda, kwo kuguma n’okuhira ebiryo oku kanwa kabumbe,
\v 19 Ebi barhûla ensalamu êrhalya erhanahinya, bibà bya cici? Ntyo kw’ali omuntu Nyamuzinda ashimbire.
\v 20 Analabaganye, ayîse mutya. Kw’ali nka kulya bashahula omuntu babulimuhà omukazi, abande enani.
\s1 Obusîme
\p 
\v 21 Orhabâga we nnaburhè, orhacîrhegega entanya zilêrha omutula.
\v 22 Busîme bw’omurhima ko kalamo k’omuntu, bushagaluke kwo kuyûshûla ensiku zâge.
\v 23 Orhebe entanya zâwe, orhûlirize omurhima, ohive oburhè: bulya omugungunu gwâyîsire banji, ntà bunguke gwankalêrha.
\v 24 Amagene n’obukunizi binanyihye akalamo, entanya zinabiduhye obushosi.
\v 25 Nka omurhima gushagalusire, ebiryo binazigire omuntu, ehi omuntu àlyaga himugwe bwinjà.
\c 31
\s1 Obuhirhi
\p 
\v 1 Okubula îrò buhirhi bukulêrha, kurhamya kunarhamya omubiri, entanya z’obuhirhi îrò zihiva.
\v 2 Entanya z’omûshi zinarhume omuntu arhaja îrò, endwâla nkali enahanze îrò.
\v 3 Omugale akola mpu ly’ebirugu byâge biluga, n’okurhamûka kwâge erhi kucîsîmîsa;
\v 4 omukenyi akola mpu ly’abona eci alya, n’okurhamûka kwâge bushube buligo.
\v 5 Osîma ensaranga arhafuma câha, ohubira obunguke bwo bunamuhubya.
\v 6 Banji ensaranga zayîsire, lufù bàlimo, barhakabuzire bufà.
\v 7 Gubà murhego oku bantu bazisîma, n’abahwinja boshi mo bahwêra.
\v 8 Iragi lyâge omugale oyôsire buzira izâbyo, n’orhashimbûlula masholo.
\v 9 Ye ndi oyo rhumusîme? Ajirîre olubaga aminjà garhankaderhwa.
\v 10 Ndi wajire muli ebyo anarhengamwo mugumagumà? Ndi oyo wabula­ga bujira ecâha n’obwo ali akuhashire? Abula bujirira abandi amabî, n’obwo àkagajizire?
\v 11 Obugale bwâge burhahuligane, n’endêko yâmanyisa aminjà àjizire.
\s1 Ebiryo
\p 
\v 12 K’amêza olikwo gahirhîre? Orhaderhaga n’okucîkunga, mpu: «Nêci, ene nayîgurha, byamâluga!»
\v 13 Kengêra obubî bw’amasù g’obudambyè: ka hali eciremwa cibî kulusha isù? Erilakira obusha!
\v 14 Orhalikiraga okuboko ah’okulalisire ayêrekîze okwâge, orhacîrhunikaga oku cîbo kuguma naye.
\v 15 Manyira owinyu kuli we wêne, na muli byoshi obè murhimanya.
\v 16 Olye nka mugula ehi bakuhîre, oleke okuvûkuza amarhama, n’okucîbonêsa nshonyi.
\v 17 Obè we rhangireka okulya, bugula obwo, orhahubaga zakanaba nshonyi.
\v 18 Akabà muli banji oku mêza, orhacîhâga embere z’abandi.
\v 19 Hitya hiyîgusa omulume! erhi agwîshira, ayîse bwinjà.
\v 20 Hunga bwinjà, ntalya-binene, omuntu asagizûka duba, anayumve irhwe liri lyangu. Enkananga, olushalo, okulumwa omu nda, lwo luhembo lw’omudambyè.
\v 21 Kwankanabà wasêzîbwe okudambiha, yîmuka, ojè embuga, oshale, wayumva okola mwangu.
\v 22 Nyumva, mwâna wâni, orhangayaga, buzinda lyo wayumva ebi nkubwîzire. Obè n’olugero omu ngasi mukolo wakola, wabona oku ntà mango endwâla yakuhikeko.
\v 23 Omushamuka olalikîne akaluza ebiryo bwenêne asîmwa, bânajire nsiku baderha okuhâna kwâge.
\v 24 Ci kwône olalikîne akabijinikira kushekerwa ashekerwa omu lugo, n’obujinisi bwâge kuderhwa buderhwa.
\s1 Amamvu
\p 
\v 25 Orhabâga ntwâli y’amamvu, amamvu gahezize banji.
\v 26 Eluganda, muliro barhangulamwo ecûma, ntyo kw’amamvu garhangula emirhima aha abalume banywera.
\v 27 Amamvu ko kalamo k’omulume, casinga omuntu anywe galya g’olugero.
\v 28 Bushagaluke bwa murhima, busîme bw’omuntu, go mamvu omuntu anywa ensa nyinjà, n’omu lugero lwinjà.
\v 29 Kaheza, go mamvu omuntu anywa nk’ahagula, aganywere amîru n’omujina.
\v 30 Endalwè enazûkize omuhwinja enongwe yamuheza, emuheze, emisî ­enyihe n’okulwa kuhajè, evune enjingo abulilêrha amalwa.
\v 31 Muli oku mêza, orhasholoshonzagya owinyu, orhamushekeraga akaja­ mwo orukara, orhamubonêsagya nshonyi, orhanamujiraga burhè mpu akulyûlage.
\c 32
\s1 Ebiryo by’olusiku lukulu
\p 
\v 1 Bakujizire mukulu w’amêza, orhajiraga bucîbone, obêre ekarhî k’abinyu nka muntu akâbo, obagabulire obulibwârhala nâwe.
\v 2 Wamajira emikolo yâwe yoshi oku enali, bwârhalaga, nâwe osîme haguma n’abinyu, bakusîme, lwo luhembo lw’omukolo mwinjà wakozire.
\v 3 We mushosi, derhaga, kuli kwinjà emund’oli, ci bunyi-bunyi, orhahulisagya enyimbo.
\v 4 Amango bali bayumvîrhiza oluzihwa, orhaluzagya olubî, oleke okuhahabuka.
\v 5 Amango bali oku mêza, olulanga abà namulîsa, kuli nka kula bayûshûla enjuma nyinjà-nyinjà oku magerha.
\v 6 Cifungo ca hibuye hinjinjà omu burhunge bw’amasholo, lwo lulanga lw’omulya mwinjà amango banywa orhwamvu rhwinja.
\v 7 Derhaga, nâwe musole, akabà kwa bulagîrire, akabiri karhali kanyi erhi bakakudôsa.
\v 8 Oyôfihye ebinwa byâwe, oderhe binji omu bisungunu, obè wa kuhulika-kwa-muhya\f + \fr 32, 8 \ft Kuhulika kwa muhya: omuntu anahulike n’obwo arhabuziri eci âderha; ci kwa burhimanya, kuyumvîrhiza ebi abandi baderha.\f*.
\v 9 Orhaderhezagya abakulu nka binyu mûmanîne mweshi, owundi muntu akaderha, oshube oku byâwe binwa.
\v 10 Mukemezo gushokolera omukungulo, inêma lishokolera omuntu murhimanya.
\v 11 Amango gâwe gamahika, gendaga, orhacilegerere, libirhira eka, oleke okûla kusharhira omu njira.
\v 12 Aha ka, ocîmîmise, oshârhe, orhabîhaga omu kuderha buzira lugero.
\v 13 Ovuge Lulema omunkwa kuli byoshi, ye kushobôza aminjà gâge.
\s1 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda
\p 
\v 14 Omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, ayumva akanwa kâge, abamulonza kurhona barhona emwâge.
\v 15 Omuntu odôkereza irhegeko kuyîgusa limuyîgusa, ci endyâlya kusârhaza liyîsârhaza.
\v 16 Abarhînya Nyamuzinda banajirwe bashinganyanya, ebijiro byâbo binjà kwo bimoleka nka kamole.
\v 17 Omubî arhaziga bamuhanûla, arhabula igwârhiro ly’okujira obulonza bwâge.
\v 18 Omuntu nkana arhagaya ihano, mubî-ogayana yêhe arhabà lugwêgwè.
\v 19 Orhajiraga bici buzira kugerêreza, ntyo orhacîyunjuze kw’ebi wajizire.
\v 20 Orhageraga omu njira y’ebikunguzo, orhagijà wasârhala.
\v 21 Orhacîkubagiraga enjira ekubûsire,
\v 22 n’abâna bâwe nabo arhacîkubagiragabo.
\v 23 Ocîlange wêne muli byoshi, okwo nakwo kuli kushimba amarhegeko.
\v 24 Omuntu ocîkubagire irhegeko, kushimba ashimba ebi lirhegesire, olangâlira Nyamuzinda arhabulabula.
\c 33
\p 
\v 1 Orhînya Nyamuzinda, obubî bunamugere kulî, ciru n’amarhangulo gâbwo anagafume.
\v 2 Oshomba irhegeko arhali murhimanya, n’oli mpu alishimbire arhanalishimbiri kw’ali nka bwârho omu mulaba.
\v 3 Omuntu w’obukengêre kucîkubagira acîkubagira irhegeko, oku bwâge likwânîne okuyemerwa nka mulêbi.
\v 4 Ogerêreze eci waderha lyo bakuyumva, ocîjè emurhima embere oshuze.
\v 5 Ebibà emurhima gw’ecinganyi kwo biyôrha nka mizizi ya ngâlè, obukengêre bwâge kwo buzunguluka nka masini
\v 6 Enfarasi nto kw’eri nka mwîra olimbira amasheka, bakagerêreza mpu bayishonakwo, eyâne.
\s1 Birhûmâna
\p 
\v 7 Cirhuma ensiku zirhayûmânana? N’obwo omwâka gwoshi, omûshi oku izûba gurhenga?
\v 8 Kuli kuderha oku Nyamuzinda arhayûmanyanyagya ensiku: ye wajiraga ecanda n’empondo n’ensiku nkulu.
\v 9 Akuza anayîmânika nguma-nguma, ezindi azijira nsiku kwône.
\v 10 Abantu boshi barhenga omu budaka, Adamu budaka àlemagwamwo.
\v 11 Nyamuzinda omu burhimanya bwâge ababerûla, abagerera ngasi muguma kwâge-kwâge.
\v 12 Hali baguma agishire, abahira enyanya, abagoshôla, abahira hôfi naye, hali n’abà àkazire, àbarhanya, àbakaga aha bâli.
\v 13 Kul’ibumba liyôrha omu nfune z’omubumbi, alibûmbe oku alonzize, kwo n’abantu bayôsire omu masù ga Lulema, ye bagabira n’obushinganyanya bwâge.
\v 14 Obwinjà buyîmanzire omu masù g’obubî, n’obuzîne buyîmanzire omu masù g’olufù, ntyo n’omunya-byâha omu masù g’omuntu nkana.
\v 15 Osingirize ebiremwa by’Ow’Enyanya byoshi, byoshi bigenda bibiri­ bibiri biyêrekerîne\f + \fr 33, 15 \ft Biyêrekerîne: lolà \xt 42, 24; Murh 3, 1-8\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 16 Niono, nie muzindiyisha, nayirîrwe, nâbà nk’omurhôlogozi wayisha enyuma z’âbasârûla.
\v 17 Omugisho gwa Nyamuzinda gwanjira wa burhanzi, nka musârûzi, nabumba olurhanda.
\v 18 Omanye kwône oku ntakoleraga bunguke bwâni bwône, ci n’obwa ba­lya boshi basîma okuyigîrira.
\v 19 Munyumve, mweshi bakulu b’olubaga, mwe mukulîre endêko, murhege amarhwîri.
\s1 Okubà ntagengwa kw’omuntu
\p 
\v 20 Aha mwâwe, mango ocizîne, orhalekaga mpu omwâna wâwe, mukà­ we, mwene winyu, omwîra wâwe akurhegeke. Orhahâga owundi ebirugu byâwe, kwanabà kucîyunjuza buzinda mango wabihûna.
\v 21 Oku ocizîne onacidwîrhe wayîsa omûka, orhacîjiraga mujà wa ndi.
\v 22 Okuhûnwa n’abâna bâwe, kwo kukulu aha kuyêrekera abâna ôburha wabahûna.
\v 23 Ngasi kantu wajira koshi, oyôrhe we nnako, omanye wankacîshûbula oheze irenge lyâwe.
\v 24 Amango wâbà wamâyunjuza ensiku z’akalamo kâwe, lwo lusiku lw’okufà, ogabe ebyâwe.
\s1 Abajà
\p 
\v 25 Ecihêsi ciri ca byahirwa, karhi na mizigo, omujà ali wa biryo, buhane\f + \fr 33, 25 \ft Abajà: obukenge oku bajà, lolà \xt Efz 6, 9; Kol 4, 1; Flm 16\xt*\ft .\f* na mukolo.
\v 26 Okolêse omujà wâwe, wabona omurhûla, omuleke buzira mukolo, wabona oku naye alonza kurhi ankarhenga omu bujà.
\v 27 Omurhamba n’olukoba, binagombye ecihêsi, obukali n’akarhi binatwe ifêka, ly’omushizi mubî.
\v 28 Omuhè omukolo, akole, aleke okuyôloha, bulya kuyôloha kuyîgîriza amenge mabî.
\v 29 Omuhè omukolo gumukwânîne, n’akakalahira, omuhogeke omugozi.
\v 30 Ci oleke obukali bw’okumînya oku bantu, okulikire obushinganyanya.
\v 31 K’ogwêrhe mujà muguma yêne? Omulole nka ye we, bulya wamulibukîre.
\v 32 Ka mujà muguma yêne ogwêrhe? Omulole nka mwene winyu, bulya omulagîrirekwo.
\v 33 Bulya okamukolêsa kubî, akuyâka, ngahi wacimurhangira?
\c 34
\s1 Ebilôrho
\p 
\v 1 Okulangâlira obusha n’ebirhaboneke, kuli kwa musirhe, n’ebingolongolo byo birhambira ebilôrho.
\v 2 Kuli kugwârha ecizunguzungu na kushimba empûsi, okulegerera oku bilôrho.
\v 3 Ecilolero n’ebilôrho bishushîne, ocîloleremwo, wabona obusù bwâwe.
\v 4 Cinjà cici cirhenga omu izinga? K’okuli kunarhenge omu bunywesi?
\v 5 Okulagula, okukera engoko, ebilôrho, byoshi busha, kahalalo ka mukazi oli izîmi.
\v 6 Akabà arhali Nyamuzinda obirhumire, orhabishîbiriraga.
\v 7 Ebilôrho byarhebire banji, banji balibilangâlîre bahona.
\v 8 Amarhegeko garhanywerha, Irhegeko lyôhe linakulikirwe buzira kurhebana, oburhimanya nabo bubà bwimâna burhabêsha.
\s1 Okubalama
\p 
\v 9 Okubalama kuyigîriza binji, owagezire omu bihugo binji anamanye na binji, n’omuntu wabwîne binji yenayishiganîra.
\v 10 Omuntu orhasâgijà omu malibuko, arhishi binji, ci owagenzire ayishi orhunjirhunji.
\v 11 Nabwîne binji ebwa kubalama, ebi nayumvîrhe byo binji kulusha ebi nakamanyiderha.
\v 12 Olufù lwampushire kanji kanji, nanatwa oku isî, alagi kurhi:
\v 13 Abarhînya Nyamuzinda balama, bulya bamulangalîre, bulya bacîkubagîre owakanabaciza.
\v 14 Orhînya Nyamuzinda arhayôboha cici, arhajuguma, Nyamuzinda ye abà acîkubagîre.
\v 15 Iragi ly’omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, ndi ayimangîrekwo? Ndi ayegemîre?
\p 
\v 16 Amasù ga Nyakasane, gayêrekîre balya bamusîma, ye mulîkûza, mutuga muzibu, ye mâkiro, omu mpûsi y’omu irungu, ye mbohôlolo oku idûrhu ly’akasirahinga\f + \fr 34, 16 \ft Akasirahinga: gala mango izûba lijà omu nkuba karhî, ntâye wahinga erhi idûrhu lirhuma «okuhinga kumuzire».\f*, ye mucîka-ntambala, ye na mukoma-afungira-abâli-bahirima.
\v 17 Kulengereza alengereza emirhima, azibûle amasù, ahûne amagala, akalamo n’omugisho.
\s1 Enterekêro
\p 
\v 18 Okurhûla Nyamuzinda ebizimbano kuli kumushekera, entûlo z’ababî zirhamusîmîsa.
\v 19 Ow’Enyanya arhabona oku ntûlo z’ababî, arhali bunji bwa mbâgwa burhuma ababalira ebyâha\f + \fr 34, 19 \ft Ebyâha: lolà \xt Amo 5, 21\xt*\f*.
\v 20 Kuli kuniga omwâna n’îshe asinza, okurhûla Nyamuzinda ebi wanyagaga abakenyi.
\v 21 Ehitya hy’omukenyi ko kalamo kâge, okumunyagahyo kuli kumuyîrha.
\v 22 Kuli kuniga owinyu okumunyaga ehi alamirakwo, oyîma omukozi oluhembo lwâge erhi mwîsi wa bantu.
\v 23 Muguma ayûbake, owundi ashâbe, bunguke buci barhenzamwo aha nyuma ly’oburhè.
\v 24 Muguma agishe, owundi ahehêrere: muguma ohi Nyakasane ayumva?
\v 25 Owacîshuka kulya kubà anahumire omurhumba akanashubiguhuma­ko, erhi cici acîshukirage?
\v 26 Kw’ali ntyo omuntu ocîshalisa oku byâha byâge, buzinda kandi abishubîrire! ndi okolaga ayumva omusengero gwâge? Bunguke buci burhenzirage muli okwo kucîrhohya?
\c 35
\s1 Amarhegeko n’enterekêro
\p 
\v 1 Okushimba irhegeko kuli kuluza entûlo, okusêra oku marhegeko\f + \fr 35, 1 \ft 35. 1: Amarhegcko n’enterekêro: okurherekêra liri irhegeko, ci arhali hoshi aho, hali agandi marhegeko ganali makulu: obushinganyanya n’obuzigire: lola \xt Luk 11, 42\xt*\ft .\f* kuli kuhâna enterekêro y’omurhûla.
\v 2 Okujira akantu k’obuzigire kuli kurhûla obwâso bw’enshâno, oku­rhabâla abakenyi kuli kuhâna enterekêro y’obukuze.
\v 3 Ecisîmîsa Nyamuzinda kuli kuleka amabî, okuyâka obulyâlya kuli kuhâna enterekêro y’okubabalirwa ebyâha.
\v 4 Orhajaga embere za Nyakasane maboko mûmu, ojire ebyo byoshi bu­lya birhegesirwe.
\v 5 Entûlo y’omushinganyanya ebâ nyinjà aha luhêro, akisununu kâyo e­ mw’Ow’Enyanya kayînamukira.
\v 6 Enterekêro y’omushinganyanya erhahimwa kusîmwa, nta mango yayîbagirwe.
\v 7 Kuza Nyamuzinda n’obushiru, orhayâgalagwa n’omwâka muhyâhya warhûla.
\v 8 Nka warhûla, orhûle oshagalusire, n’entûlo y’abakenyi oyihâne n’obu­sîme.
\v 9 Orhûle Nyamuzinda nk’oku ànakuhîre, ohâne n’obushiru nk’oku ona­gwêrhe.
\v 10 Bulya Nyamuzinda kalembu ahâna, washobôla kali nda kali nk’oku ohânyire.
\p 
\v 11 Omanye wankagèreza mpu wahôngera Nyamuzinda, arhakaziga; orhacîkubagiraga enterekêro y’obushambo.
\v 12 Bulya Nyamuzinda abâ mutwî wa mmanja. yêhe arhajira kabôlo omu bantu.
\v 13 Nyamuzinda arhajira kabôlo ka kulenganya omukenyi, kuyumvîrhiza ayumvîrhiza omulenge gw’oyu badwîrhe bâlibuza.
\v 14 Arhakengula enfûzi emulakire, arhayîbagira n’emirenge y’omukana.
\v 15 K’emirenge y’omukana erhahulula omu marhama gâge bulya, k’e­ndûlù yâge erhabonêsa nshonyi owamulasagya?
\v 16 Omuntu okolera Nyamuzinda n’omurhima gwoshi kurhona arhona, n’izù lyâge enyanya lihika.
\v 17 Omusengero gw’omwîrhohye bitù gurhulukânya, arharhûlirira gurhanacihika.
\v 18 Arhagoheka na Nyamuzinda arhacimushuza, nka Nyamuzinda arhacitwa olubanja lw’abashinganyanya, n’okukubûla enjira y’obushinganyanya.
\v 19 Nyamuzinda arhâlegame, arhâlembere emihera,
\v 20 kuhika avune ezo ncuku omugongo, acîhôle oku mashanja;
\v 21 kuhika aherêrekeze bacîbone boshi, avune akarhi k’oburhegesi bw’e­ ndyâlya;
\v 22 kuhika ahembe ngasi muguma nk’oku ebijiro byâge binali, atwîre abantu olubanja nk’oku emirhima yâbo eri;
\v 23 kuhika atwîre olubaga lwâge olubanja lw’obushinganyanya, alushobôze obusîme bw’obwonjo bwâge.
\v 24 Obwonjo burhahimwa kuyinjiha amango g’amalibuko, nka kula ecitù c’enkuba cinaboneka canda.
\c 36
\s1 Omusengero gw’okulîkûza n’okuyûbaka Israheli buhyâhya
\p 
\v 1 Orhubabalire, Nyamwagirwa, Nyamuzinda w’igulu, lolà, ojugumye amashanja goshi.
\q1 
\v 2 Oshunge amashanja g’ihanga okuboko, gabone oku buhashe onajira.
\q1 
\v 3 Kulya wabayêrekaga oku oli Mwimâna, warhulibuza banasinza, kw’ojirage buno, nîrhu orhuyêreke obukulu bwâwe kuli bo.
\q1 
\v 4 Bakumanye nk’oku nîrhu rhwamanyaga oku ntà wundi Nyamuzinda kuleka We, Nyamwagirwa.
\q1 
\v 5 Oshubîrire okujira ebirhangâzo, ojire ebindi bisômerîne, oyêrekane obukulu bwâwe, okengêse okuboko kwâwe, okulyo kwâwe kuj’irenge.
\q1 
\v 6 Ozûse omungo, obulage omutula, oyîrhe omubisha, oherêrekeze omushombanyi.
\q1 
\v 7 Obiduhye ago mango, kengêra ecihango, ojire rhukuze ebijiro byâwe by’oburhwâli.
\q1 
\v 8 Omuliro gwâwe gw’olwihôlo gusingônole abasigîre, balya barhindibuza olubaga lwâwe baherêrekere.
\q1 
\v 9 Otuntume amarhwe ga balya bakulu b’ihanga, baderha, mpu: «Mâshi rhwêne!»
\q1 
\v 10 Oshubûze emilala ya Yakôbo yoshi, oyigalulire omwanya gwâyo nk’oku byàli burhanzi.
\q1 
\v 11 Nyakasane k’emirenge, babalira olubaga luderhwa izîno lyâwe: babalira Israheli, we wamujiraga nfula yâwe.
\q1 
\v 12 Olukogo lw’ecishagala câwe citagatîfu lukugwârhe, lukogo lwa Yeruzalemi, ho mwâwe orhamûkira.
\q1 
\v 13 Siyoni, omuyunjuze bukuze bwâwe, n’akarhwa-bwâmi kâwe okajire kayunjule irenge.
\q1 
\v 14 Oyîmangîre ebiremwa byâwe birhanzi: oyêrekane okuli kw’obulêbi bwajiragwa oku izîno lyâwe.
\q1 
\v 15 Orhimûle abakulangâlira, kubonekane oku abalêbi bâwe bo ba­ nyamuderha-kubà.
\q1 
\v 16 Nyakasane, oyumvîrhize omusengero gwa bambali bâwe, kulyâla kw’omugisho gwa Aroni oku lubaga lwâwe.
\q1 
\v 17 Boshi, en’igulu, bamanye oku we Nyakasane, Nyamuzinda w’ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Okuhugûkwa
\p 
\v 18 Olurholero luyankirira ngasi kalyo luhâbirwe, ci hali ebiryo binjà kulusha ebindi.
\v 19 Olulimi lumanyira ehisimbisimbi oku bwehe bwahyo, kwo n’okwo omurhima murhonde gurhahaba ebinwa by’obunywesi.
\v 20 Omurhima mubî gunayîrhe mutula, ci omuntu wâbona kucîlanga acîlanga kuli gô.
\s1 Okulonza omukazi
\p 
\v 21 Omukazi arhayîra mulume, ci abanyere babâmwo bamunyerenkana na bacinyere kwône.
\v 22 Obwinjà bw’omukazi kusîmîsa busîmîsa amasù, kwo n’omurhima gw’omulume gulakira.
\v 23 Omukazi ogwêrhe obwinja n’obutûdu ekanwa, ibà ali w’iragi ekarhî k’abandi.
\v 24 Okuyanka omukazi gubà murhondêro gw’obuhirhi, ye murhabâzi oli akâge, nyamwegemerwa wâge.
\v 25 Ishwa lirhajira côgo lirhahwa kuyônwa, buzira mukazi, omulume ye milumbo na muhabuka.
\v 26 Kurhi wakacîkubagira cishambo-ali-magala. Orhali eyo arhali n’eno?
\v 27 Ntyo kw’ali omulume orhajira aha abâ, olâla ah’obudufu bunamushimanyire.
\c 37
\s1 Irumhi mpu bîra
\p 
\v 1 Ngasi mwîra anaderhe: «Nâni ndi mwîra wâwe», ci hali omwîra w’izîno kwône.
\v 2 Ka gurhali mutula munene oku muntu okubona owinyu erhi mwîra ahinduka mushombanyi?
\v 3 Aye! murhima mubî, kurhi weki walemirwe, mpu ohire obuminya omw’igulu?
\v 4 Winyu kwône ali mwîra amango ayôsire bwinjà, hano ensiku zicikwîhindulira, naye acîhindule.
\v 5 Winyu kwône ali mwîra amango akulinzirekwo akantu, amango g’e­ntambala akutulikekwo amatumu.
\v 6 Orhayîbagiraga omwîra w’okuli omu ntambala, omubîke emurhima omu bugale bwâwe.
\s1 Abahanûzi
\p 
\v 7 Ngasi muhanûzi mahano abâna, ci hali abagahânira okulonza obunguke.
\v 8 Omanye omuhanûzi, burhanzi cidôse bulagîrire buci bumugwêrhe - kwankanabà bunguke bwâge bwône alonza, - alekikuhirakwo akarhunzi.
\v 9 Arhakubwîraga, erhi: «Njira nyinjà eyo olimo», abule na bwajà ebulâbi akabona oku byâbà.
\v 10 Orhadôsagya ihano emw’orhakusîma, n’abayâgalwa nâwe orhaba­bwîraga emihigo yâwe.
\v 11 Orhadôsagya omukazi ihano liyêrekîre mukîba, n’omwôba orhamudôsagya ihano ly’okulwa, n’omurhunzi orhamudôsagya ery’okurhimbûla, n’owagula orhamudôsagya ery’okuguza, n’omuyâgalwa orhamudôsagya ery’okuvuga omunkwa, n’omujinisi orhamudôsagya ery’okuhâna, n’omwôlo orhamudôsagya ery’okukola, n’omulimya orhamudôsagya ery’okuyûsa omukolo, omushizi mwôlo orhamudôsagya ery’omukolo muzibu; abo nt’ihano bankakuhà.
\v 12 Ci ohûne ihano emw’omuntu orhînya Nyamuzinda, olya omanyire oku ashimba amarhegeko, olya omurhima guli nk’ogwâwe, olya wakufà lukogo erhi wankayâbirwa.
\v 13 Buzinda, osêre oku ihano ly’omurhima gwâwe, bulya ntà mwîra okurhonya kugulusha.
\v 14 Kanji kanji omurhima gw’omuntu gunamurhonde bwinjà, kulusha bajishamba nda bali oku ntondo.
\v 15 Kulushîsa aho, oshenge Nyamuzinda: ayêrekeze amagulu gâwe omu njira y’okuli.
\s1 Oburhimanya: obw’okuli n’obw’obunywesi
\p 
\v 16 Omurhondêro gwa ngasi cijiro, bukengêre, gerêreza embere orhondêre omukolo.
\v 17 Omuzî gw’enkengêro, murhima, gugwêrhe mashami anni:
\v 18 aminjà n’amabî, obuzîne n’olufù, n’ensiku zoshi olulimi luyôsire lubiyimangire.
\v 19 Wanabona ali mulenga w’okuyigîriza abandi, n’obwo kuli ye yêne ali wa busha;
\v 20 lebè: w’akalimi, ye nyamakobwa, azinda erhi ishali lyamuyîrha,
\v 21 bulya Nyakasane arhamurhonyizi, ntà burhimanya agwêrhe.
\v 22 Lebè abà murhimanya omu nkengêro zâge yêne, n’omu iderha lyâge, obukengêre bwâge liri ishwa liyêra.
\v 23 Omurhimanya w’okuli lubaga lwâge ayigîriza, n’emikolo y’obukengêre bwâge esêzire.
\v 24 Omurhimanya abà ayunjwîre mugisho, abamubona boshi bamuderha w’iragi.
\v 25 Ensiku z’akalamo k’omuntu ziri nganje, ci ez’Israheli zoki zirhankaganjwa.
\v 26 Omurhimanya, ekarhî k’olubaga, ali mwîkubagirwa, izîno lyâge lya­ Nyamubâho ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Onyihye oku mîru gâwe
\p 
\v 27 Mwâna wâni, amango ocizîne, omanye obwôrhere bwâwe, hirharhujirîri, orhahihambiraga.
\v 28 Bulya arhali ngasi kantu kakwânana hoshi arhali na ngasi muntu okômera byoshi.
\v 29 Orhahubiraga ngasi hyanuna, oleke okuziga ebiryo,
\v 30 bulya obudambyè buli bubî, nda-ya-byo arhahwa kulumwa omu nda.
\v 31 Banji balire n’obudambyè, omuntu ocîlanga bwinjà anayûshûla akalamo kâge.
\c 38
\s1 Omufumu (Munganga), amafumu n’endwâla
\p 
\v 1 Okenge munganga, nk’oku akwânîne okukengwa erhi mikolo yâge erhuma, bulya naye Nyamuzinda wamulemaga.
\v 2 Okufuma emwa Ow’Enyanya kurhenga, kwo kuyisha nka nshôkano y’ebwâmi.
\v 3 Obumanye bwa munganga bwo burhuma akananda, bwo bunasômeza abagale.
\v 4 Nyamuzinda analengeze abanyinyi, omuntu wabona arhabagayaguza.
\v 5 Kali karhî lushâli kayinjihagya amîshi\f + \fr 38, 5 \ft Obukulu omu mîshi: lolà \xt Lub 15, 23\xt*\ft : ecisômerine c’e Mara.\f*, kayêrekana obuhashe.
\v 6 Nyamuzinda ye hà kandi abantu obukengêre, kandi ye hà abantu obuhashe, mpu bacîtakîrîre ebinja by’obuhashe bwâge.
\v 7 Anabikolêse, oku kubuka n’okurhûliriza, omufumu anarhôle atuntumire haguma kwône.
\v 8 Ntyo emikolo yâge erhahwa, ye lumîza n’aminjà omu igulu.
\v 9 Mwâna wâni, mango walwâla, oleke okulumbwîja, shenga Nyamuzinda akafumya.
\v 10 Oleke obubî bwâwe, onalange n’enfune zâwe omu bucêse, onashuke omurhima gwâwe ko ebyâha.
\v 11 N’akakengêzo k’obwâso bw’enshâno, orhûle nk’oku obugale bwâwe bunali.
\v 12 Kandi ojè emwa munganga, bulya naye Nyamuzinda wamulemaga, orhamulahiraga, omulagirîrekwo.,
\v 13 Hali amango okufuma kuli omu maboko ga bamuganga.
\v 14 Nabo bakolaga bashenga Nyamuzinda, mpu abashobôze engalo y’okurhûliriza, n’ey’okufumya lyo bamanyigalukira abandi.
\v 15 Omuntu ojira ecâha omu masù ga Lulema, akumbe omu maboko ga muganga.
\s1 Olufù n’emishîbo
\p 
\v 16 Mwâna wâni, olakire owâwe ofîre, olake omutula gwâwe, ci oku bwage omubiri gwâge guli mukembûle, o­rhayîbagiraga n’okukâkenga ecûsho câge.
\v 17 Olake bwenêne, olake omutula gwâwe, oshîbe nk’oku nyakufà anakwânîne\f + \fr 38, 17 \ft Ekanwa ebâbwa: hali ebihugo bijira enkômedu erhi wakabula bulakira omuntu ofîre, banakushobeke mpu we muyisire.\f*, lusiku luguma erhi ibiri, bulya ekanwa k’abantu ebâbwa, buzinda omutula gwâwe gurhûlirire.
\v 18 Bulya omutula gunayîrhe, omurhima gwamarhoga ntà buzibu gucigwêrhe.
\v 19 Wamabisha omuntu wâwe, oyîbagirage omutula gwâwe, omutula gurhalamirwakwo.
\v 20 Orhabîkiriraga omutula emurhima, ogurhenze, kengêra okuhwa kw’a­ kalamo kâwe.
\v 21 Orhayîbagiraga, ejibwa ci erharhengwa\f + \fr 38, 21 \ft Erhagalukwa: ekuzimu.\f*, emirenge yâwe erhagalule nyakufà: nâwe wêne kucîbabaza ocîbabazize.
\v 22 Kengêra aka kanwa kâni, kabà kâwe nâwe: «injo erhi nie ene ali we».
\v 23 Mango wamabisha omuntu wâwe, orhingiba nka waleka okumukengêra, obu omûka gwamurhenziremwo, orhûlirirage nâwe.
\s1 Obushanja bw’amaboko
\p 
\v 24 Oburhimanya bw’omwandisi buyîgwa amango g’okurhamûka, n’orhaliko mmanja ye bà murhimanya.
\v 25 Kurhi akabà murhimanya omuntu ozukira oku ngâlè y’okuhinga, omuntu irenge lyâge lyoshi liri omu kufumbarha akarhi k’okuyâbula, omuntu ojà atunda empanzi anaziregerereko, ôrhaderha ogurhali gwa nkâfu!\f + \fr 38, 25 \ft Empanzi: omuntu orhagerêreza bindi bici ogurhali mukolo gwâge gwône, erya nkômedu n’erya nka masini, acibuzire akantu; oburhimanya buhûnyire omuntu acîdôse «cici cirhuma njira ntya?»\f*
\v 26 Omurhima gwâge guli omu by’okuhinga, n’ebijingo byoshi erhi ayâhirira amanina.
\v 27 Kwo na kuguma n’abanyakasi n’abanya bushanja boshi, bali oku kasi buca-buyira, barhagoheka, abajira obulenga bw’okubinja ebimanyîso\f + \fr 38, 27 \ft Ebimanyîso: kantu kamanyîsa nn’akantu bakananisirekwo, kandi erhi kashè.\f*, bahindulage ene n’irhondo ecimanyîso babijirire: mpu lyo bayumanyanya n’ecisiki, balâle oku cîko mpu lyo bashwinja obushanja bwâbo.
\v 28 Kwo na kuguma n’abatuzi eluganda: obone arhole ecûma, idûrhu ly’omuliro limuyûdukire omubiri, yêshi arhûbanukirwe; okutôrha kw’enyundo kumufuke amarhwîri, arhasinza handi, cirya cûma cône; omurhima gwoshi kwa gulya mukolo gunali, oku cîko alâla mpu lyo ayunjuza.
\v 29 Kwo na kuguma na nababûmbi, aha bushanja bwâge, ayôkoleze n’a­magulu; obushanja bumuli aha nyomvu, n’okucîbûnda guli mulâli;
\v 30 amaboko gabûmbe ibûmba, amagulu galilabarhe, emurhima kukombêza bwinjà kwône, na ngasi bijingo kuhyajira amasiga.
\v 31 Abo bantu boshi bacîkubagire amaboko gâbo, ngasi muguma ali mulenga omu bushanja bwâge.
\v 32 Buzira bo, ntà lugo lwankayûbakwa, ntâye wankabalama erhi kujiyûbaka handi.
\v 33 Ci kwône orhabashimâne omu ihano ly’ecihugo, barhali n’omu lugero lw’abakulu b’endêko. Barhali bazûzi, barhanayumva irhegeko oku ligenda.
\v 34 Barhali bayigîriza, barhali ba kugerêreza bwenêne, barhali b’omu murhwe gw’abajizi b’emigani. Ci kwône bali mutungo omu igulu, n’omusengero gwâbo gubà guyêrekîre obushanja-bwâbo.
\c 39
\s1 Omwandisi
\p 
\v 1 Kundi kundi ayôrha omuntu osêgeza omurhima n’enkengêro oku irhegeko ly’Ow’Enyanya. Kulongereza alongereza oburhimanya bw’abakulûkulu boshi, amango gâge g’okurhamûka, arhamûkire oku bulêbi.
\v 2 Kubîka abîkirira emyanzi y’abantu bajire irenge, asheshere omu rhwonga-rhwonga rhw’emigani.
\v 3 Analongereze okuhundûla omugani, ayumve iralà ly’amahwe g’emi­gâni.
\v 4 Ekarhî k’abakulu yo akolera, wamushimâna haguma n’abarhegesi. Abalame, aj’ihanga, abwîne ebinja n’ebibî bibà omu bantu.
\v 5 Kurhenga sêzi, n’omurhima gwoshi, emwa Nyamuzinda, Lulema wâge ayêrekera, ayînamulîre omurhima emw’Ow’Enyanya, arhenge omu kanwa, ashenge, ahûne obwonjo oku byâha byâge yêne.
\v 6 Omukulu Nyamuzinda akalonza, amuyunjuza mûka gwa bukengêre. Naye yêne aderha ebinwa by’oburhimanya, ashenga avuge Nyamuzinda omunkwa.
\v 7 Abona obumanye n’ihano lishingânîne n’amahwe mafulike agashwêkere oku murhima.
\v 8 Ebi ayigîrizîbwe abiyêrekana, analimbire irhegeko ly’endagâno ya Nyamuzinda.
\v 9 Banji bakûnga obukengêre bwâge, na ntà mango ayîbagirwe. Barhakahusa kumukengera, izîno lyâge lyâlama omu ngasi maburhwa.
\v 10 Amashanja gâganira oburhimanya bwâge, n’endêko ekuze irenge lyâge.
\v 11 Erhi akalama bwenêne, izîno lyâge lyaj’irenge kulusha ecihumbi, n’erhi akafà duba, gurhali muhona.
\s1 Mukuze Nyamuzinda
\p 
\v 12 Nnonzire okushubiderha enkengêro zâni, omurhima gwâni guyunjwîre nka mwêzi mukulu.
\v 13 Munyumve bâna bâni bakungwa, mukûle nka roza ntwêre oku cikunguzo c’olwîshi.
\v 14 Murhengemwo akisûnunu kinjà nka nshangi, muyâse nka mburho, obwehe bwinyu buyûdûke, muyimbe olwimbo, mukuze Nyamuzinda oku mikolo yâge.
\v 15 Mukuze izîno lyâge, muyâlîze irenge lyâge, muyimbe muzihe, muderhe mpu:
\v 16 Nêci mushâna, erhahimwa kuyinjiha emikolo ya Nyamuzinda! oku adesire kwo binabâ. Ntà kuderha mpu: Byo bici ebyo? Cirhumire bibà ntyo? Ngasi kantu kayîgwa omu mango gâko.
\v 17 Oluderho lwâge lwône lunasîke amîshi, lugasingike, izù lyâge linafukule amîshi,
\v 18 oku adesire kunabè, ntâye wankacika ecijiro câge c’okuciza.
\v 19 Ebi abantu bajira byoshi abimanyire, kurhankahashikana habè eci arhabona.
\v 20 Kubona abona kurhenga ensiku n’amango, ntâco cimusômera.
\v 21 Ntà kuderha mpu: Co cici eco? Cirhumire bibà ntyo? Ngasi kantu kagwêrhe eci kalemîrwe.
\v 22 Kul’omugisho gwâge gwalumîraga byoshi nka lwîshi, gwajomya idaho nka nkuba y’ecihonzi,
\v 23 kw’agabira amashanja obukunizi bwâge, ntyo kw’ahindulaga amîshi\f + \fr 39, 23 \ft Agahindula munyu: lolà \xt Murh 19, 24-26\xt*\ft .\f* munyu.
\v 24 Oku enjira zâge zishinganyire oku bantu bamurhînya, kwo zinali za bikunguzo oku bantu babî.
\v 25 Ebinja byalemîrwe abinja kurhenga emurhondêro, n’ebibî ababî.
\v 26 Akantu karhanzi k’obulagîrire omu kalamo k’omuntu: mîshi, muliro, cûma c’omunyu, nshâno, marhà n’obûci, murhobo gw’oku muzâbîbu, mavurha n’omwambalo.
\v 27 Ebyo byoshi bibà binjà oku binjà, ci oku babî, binahinduke bibî.
\v 28 Hali empûsi balemeraga okuhâna, oku bukunizi bwâge ayijira buhanya. amango g’obuhane enayishe n’omuhûsi gwâyo, ejîre omukolo obukunizi bwa Lulema buyirhumire.
\v 29 Omuliro, olubula, ecizombo n’olufù, ebyo byoshi byalemirwe okubà buhane.
\v 30 Amîno g’ebiryanyi, endumira-mucira, enjoka engôrho y’olwihôlo lw’okuheza ababî,
\v 31 byoshi ebà nganda yâge y’okujira oku adesire, biri en’igulu byalinga okurhumwa, hano amango gahika, birharhenguhe.
\v 32 Co carhumaga nyanka omuhigo kurhenga emurhondêro, nagerêreza, nasiga amandiko nti:
\v 33 «Emikolo ya Nyamuzinda yoshi ebà minjà aha nsâ ekwânîne, anashobôze olagîrîre.
\v 34 Ntà kuderha mpu: ehi hirhali hinjà nka hira, bulya ngasi kantu kali kinjà omu mango gâko.
\v 35 Bunôla, n’omurhima gwoshi muyashamage, muyimbe, mukuze izîno lya Nyamuzinda!»
\c 40
\s1 Obuligo
\p 
\v 1 Obuhanya bwajire oku bantu boshi, omucîmba gw’obujà gwarhamize bene Adamu, kurhenga olusiku omuntu arhenga omu nda ya nnina, kuhika olusiku ashubira emwa nnina wa boshi\f + \fr 40, 1 \ft Olukulu: lubanja lukulu, buhanya bwa kufà; nnina wa boshi: budaka, ekuzimu, lolà \xt Ayu 14, 1-2\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 2 Enkengêro zâbo, obwôba bubali emurhima, binali birya bihamba by’olusiku luminya lw’okufà.
\v 3 Mwâmi otamîre oku ntebe y’irenge, na nyakahuku otamîre omu mvungu n’omu luvù,
\v 4 omukulu oyambalîre obugale, ensirha y’obukulu omu irhwe, na hibushangi-bufundike, kuli boshi burhè, mutula, ntemu, musisi, bwôba bwa kufà, ntambala n’enongwe.
\v 5 îrò ly’obudufu, mango omuntu agwîshîre, mpu arhamûka, libà lya kuyîbagiza kwône amaganya:
\v 6 hano omuntu aderha mpu akarhamûkaga, ayumve oku liguma nka gukola mûshi, n’obwo ali îrò, bamugezemwo omusisi\f + \fr 40, 6 \ft Omusisi: kuyôboha okufà ngasi mango ecikango c’olufù câjîre omu bantu, omu nyanja: lolà \xt 40, 10; Muh 1, 7; Murh 3, 19; Lul 146\xt*\ft .\f*, nka muntu washugunusire amatumu.
\v 7 Erhi asinsimuka-atulûka, gabè nka go mango bamulîkûzize, asômerwe yêne n’obwôba bwâge.
\v 8 Oku ngasi ciremwa, kurhenga oku omuntu kuhika oku nsimba, ci bwenêne kali nda oku banya-byâha:
\v 9 lufù, mukò, ntambala n’engôrho, mutula, cizombo, buhanya, ye lwa-boshi!
\v 10 Ebyo byoshi byalemîrwe abanya-byâha, bo barhumaga n’ecihonzi cinene cimirîra igulu.
\v 11 Ngasi hirhenga omu budaka, omu budaka hishubira, na ngasi hirhenga omu mîshi, omu nyanja hijà.
\s1 Emigani
\p 
\v 12 Okuhonga n’okulenganya byâcihwa, ci obuyêmêre bw’omurhima nka­na bwayôrha ensiku n’amango.
\v 13 Abagale b’endyâlya bahuba nka mugezi, bâhirigirha nka mulazo gwa nkuba nyâmûka,
\v 14 Omubî akabumbûla enfune anacîshinge, n’obwo kukola kuhera\f + \fr 40, 14 \ft Okuhera kwâge: omuhwinja w’ensiku…\f* kwâge.
\v 15 iburha ly’ababî lirhaluza mashami, emizî migalu-galu erhabugâna agarhali mabâle.
\v 16 Kasheke akunda amîshi n’ebikunguzo, ye barhangitwa.
\v 17 Okurhona kwo kuli nk’ishwa liyunjwîre mugisho, n’okusholôlera omukenyi, mugisho gw’ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Ebinja
\p 
\v 18 Entagengwa n’ogwêrhe omukolo gwâge bajira akalamo kinjà, ci owarhôzire obuhirhi acirhalusire.
\v 19 Abâna n’olugo lûbake banalamye izîno, ci okuhika oku burhimanya kucilushire. Okushwêka enkafu, okubà n’amashwa, kunajîse irenge, ci okuyanka omukazi nkana kulushire.
\v 20 Erivayi n’obulenga binashagaluse omuntu, ci okuzigira oburhimanya kucilushire.
\v 21 Akarhêra n’oluzihwa binanyunye olwimbo, ci izù linjà lilushire.
\v 22 Iranga n’igenda linjà binashagaluse amasù, ci olwange luli omu ishwa lucilushire.
\v 23 Abîra n’abayumânîne banashimânane, ci okushimânana kw’omulume na mukâge kwo kukulu.
\v 24 Bene winyu n’abunkwa babà bakukurhabâla amango oli omu mbaka, ci okusholôlera omukenyi kunamugalukire bwenêne kulusha.
\v 25 Amasholo n’ensaranga binalimbîse omuntu, ci ihano linjà licikwânîne kulusha.
\v 26 Obugale n’emisî binarhwâlihye omurhima, ci okurhînya Nyamuzinda kulushire.
\v 27 Okurhînya Nyamuzinda kuli nk’ishwa lirimwo omwavu, irenge lyâkwo lilushire agandi goshi kumanyilanga.
\s1 Okujà kwahûna
\p 
\v 28 Mwâna wâni, orhalamiraga okujà kwahûna, okufà kwo kukulu aha kuhûniriza ene n’irhondo.
\v 29 Omuntu okonolera ebya bene amasù, akalamo kâge karhakaderhwa kalamo. Kuli kushâhuka okukalâlira eby’embuga, omuntu balezire banamuhanûla, arhakômera eyo njira.
\v 30 Ekanwa k’owahwîrekwo enshonyi, okuhûniriza kubà kwinjà, ci kwône erhi na muliro omu nda yâge.
\c 41
\s1 Olufù
\p 
\v 1 Lufù mâshi! okukengêra oku h’oli kurhahimwa bululu oku muntu oli n’iragi ekarhî k’ebyâge, kuli kàshêga, oyu byoshi bibêrîre, n’owacîhasha okulya yêne.
\v 2 Mâshi lufù, kàli irhegeko lyâwe licîfinjirwe emwa kàlibwîre\f + \fr 41, 2 \ft Emwa kàlibwîre: amalibuko ganarhuma omuntu acîfinja ôwafîre.\f*, oyu amagala gàrhibire mîra, emw’omushosi civandagwa olâl’arhânya, owarhibire omurhima arhiba n’obulangâlire.
\v 3 Orhayôbohaga olufù, kengêra àbakushokolîre n’abâli nyuma zâwe.
\v 4 Liri irhegeko Nyamuzinda àhebirekwo ngasi muntu cakarhuma wacîkenyagulira obulonza bw’Ow’Enyanya? Olame myâka ikumi, myâka igana erhi myâka cihumbi, ekuzimu barhakutumuze obulamu bwâwe.
\s1 Oluhembo lw’abantu babî
\p 
\v 5 Bâna ba mihera endyâlya ziburha, abakômera enyumpa z’enkola-maligo.
\v 6 Akashambala basigira abâna baburhwa na abanya-byâha kuhera ka­ nahera, iburha lyâbo cijâci ca ngasi lusiku.
\v 7 Omubusi mubî kujâcirwa ajâcirwa n’abâna bâge, bulya kulî ye ecibî carhengaga.
\v 8 Buhanya bwinyu, mwe nkola-maligo, bulya mwalesire irhegeko lya Nyamuzinda w’Enyanya.
\v 9 Mwabusirwe, mwaburhirwa obuhanya, mwâfa, mufâne n’obuhanya.
\v 10 Ngasi hirhenga omu budaka, omu budaka hishubira, enkola-maligo kwo na kwo, bahehêrirwe na kuhera bahera.
\v 11 Emishîbo bajirira abafîre ebà eyêrekîre emigogo yâbo, ci izîno ly’e­mihera kuhera linahera.
\v 12 Oshîbirire izîno lyâwe bulya lyo lyasigala, lyo likulu aha buhirhi bw’e­nsaranga.
\v 13 Akalamo k’iragi kanashinge nsiku, ci izîno ly’irenge libà ly’ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Enshonyi
\p 
\v 14 Bâna bâni, mubîkirire n’omurhûla enyigîrizo zâni, Burhimanya bufulike na buhirhi burhaboneka, makwânane maci byâkabona?
\v 15 Omuntu wafulika oku ali musirhe ye mukulu, oku muntu wafulika oburhimanya bwâge.
\v 16 Ntyo mukaziyumva enshonyi nk’oku namubwîra, bulya enshonyi zibâmo kunji, hali ezikwânîne omuntu, hali n’ezirhamukwânîni, n’aba­ntu boshi barhazibà kuguma.
\v 17 Mubè nshonyi z’obûmaguza embere za sho na nyoko, n’ez’okunywerha embere z’omurhegesi n’omukulu,
\v 18 ez’okuvuna irhegeko embere z’omuzûzi, n’embere z’omurhambo w’a­bazûzi, n’ez’okubà mubî embere z’endêko y’olubaga.
\v 19 Obè nshonyi z’obulyâlya embere z’owinyu n’omwîra, n’ez’obushambo eka;
\v 20 embere z’okuli kwa Nyamuzinda n’endagâno yâge; obè nshonyi z’okuhira engofola oku mêza\f + \fr 41, 20 \ft Engofola oku mêza: kuli kubula bukenge okuhira engofola oku mêza amango walya, kwo kuguma n’okuhira okuboko ah’irhama.\f*,
\v 21 ez’okuhânira embere z’abagayanyi, ez’okurhâgalula omusingo gw’abakulamusize:
\v 22 ez’okulolêreza embaraga, n’ez’okuyôza ow’emwinyu;
\v 23 ez’okunyaga omwanya gw’owundi erhi akantu bamuhîre, ez’okulolêreza omukazi ogwêrhe ibà;
\v 24 ez’okushâsa mwambali-kazi wâwe, omanye encingo yâge.
\v 25 Ez’okuderha kubî embere z’abîra bâwe, n’oyu wahâga orhamukangulaga;
\v 26 ez’okujà kwaderha n’okulumîza omwanzi wayumvîrhe, n’okuderha amahwe ga bene.
\v 27 Ntyo wanamanya enshonyi zikwânîne, n’abandi boshi bânakurhonya.
\c 42
\p 
\v 1 Ci kwône, orhabâga nshonyi z’ebîra bikulikîre\f + \fr 42, 1 \ft Enshonyi zirhakwânîni: hali enshonyi z’obukenge, zo nyinjà; hali n’enshonyi z’obuhwinja n’obwôba, zo mbî, zinayise nnazo.\f*, orhajiraga ecâha erhi bwôba bwa bantu burhuma.
\v 2 Orhabêraga irhegeko lya Nyamuzinda n’endagâno yâge nshonyi, orhabâga nshonyi z’okutwîra enkola-maligo olubanja lwâbo,
\v 3 ez’okushambâla n’abinyu muli mweshi, ez’okuhà abîra bâwe oku byâwe sho àkusigiraga.
\v 4 okulola bwinjà omunzâni n’olugero lwâgwo, okubà n’obunguke busungunu erhi bunene bw’olugero,
\v 5 okuyunguka omu burhunzi bwâwe, okukalihira abâna bâwe, okuhanûla n’akarhi omujà mubî.
\v 6 Embere z’omukazi wakulonzako emyanzi, okuhulika kwo kukulu, n’aha abantu bahumahuma, orhayîbagiraga okufûnikira bwinjà.
\v 7 Okuganja n’okugera bwinjà kwo kumanyibîka, ebyâwe n’ebya bene byoshi biyandikwe.
\v 8 Orhabâga nshonyi z’okuhabûla omuhwinja n’omusirhe, n’omushosi w’emvi wajà kadali n’emisole. Kwo wayêrekana ntyo oku walezirwe bwinjà, n’abandi boshi bakusîma.
\s1 Entanya z’îshe w’omunyere
\p 
\v 9 Buzira kumanya, omunyere ntanya nyinji alêrhera îshe, enkengêro amulêrhera zinamuhanze kujà îrò: nka aciri murhò, bwôba mpu nkaba ârhayishiheruke duba; erhi aheruka, bwôba mpu k’abona obunyumpa bwinjà!
\v 10 Oku aciri munyere, bwôba mpu erhi bakamurhebaga, abêre ifunze aha mwâbo! Amango akol’agwêrhe îba, bwôba mpu erhi akagumbaga
\v 11 Mwâli wâwe arhayumva? Omulange bwinjà, omanye akubonêsa nshonyi emw’abashombanyi bâwe, olek’ibà lwimbo oku lugo, muderhwa w’esêzi n’ow’ebijingo, abantu boshi bakakushunga omunwe!
\s1 Abakazi
\p 
\v 12 Oleke okulolêreza iranga lya ngasi muntu, oleke n’okukâbwârhala haguma n’abakazi.
\v 13 Bulya omwambalo gujira obugukuzimu bwâgwo, n’omukazi naye a­gwêrhe obubî bw’omukazi.
\v 14 Obubî bw’omulume bwo bukulu aha bwinjà bw’omukazi: omukazi analêrhe ihanja\f + \fr 42, 14 \fk Ihanja\ft : Lolà \xt Muh 7, 26-28\xt*\ft .\f* n’ecitumulè.
\ms1 II. Irenge lya Nyamuzinda
\p 
\v 15 Buno, nkolaga naganira ogw’emikolo ya Nyamuzinda, nkola naganira ebi nabwîne. Luderho lwâge\f + \fr 42, 15 \fq Luderho lwâge\ft : lolà \xt Murh 1, 3; Ywn 1, 1\xt*\ft .\f* Nyamuzinda àjiragamwo emikolo yâge, n’ebiremwa byâge oku alonzize kwo bijira.
\v 16 Izûba kumoleka limoleka, libone ngasi kantu, n’omukolo gwa Nyamuzinda guyunjwîre irenge lyâge.
\v 17 Nyamuzinda àrhahâga abatagatîfu obuhashe bw’okuganîra ebinja byâge byoshi, ebi Nyamuzinda, nnawâbo-byoshi, asimbanyize mpu ly’igulu libêra omu irenge lyâge.
\v 18 Alikîre isù omu cirumbi c’enyanga n’omu murhima gw’omuntu, abona amenge gâbo, bulyâl’Ow’Enyanya ye nn’obumanye bwoshi, alolerîze ebimanyîso by’amango.
\v 19 Anayêrekane ebyàgezire n’ebyâyisha; amanyîse n’ebifulike.
\v 20 Ntà nkengêro ahabire, ntà kanwa kamuhuzire\f + \fr 42, 20 \ft Ntà kamuhuzire: Nyamuzinda ntâco ahabire, ayîshi byoshi.\f*.
\v 21 Ebinja byâge byoshi àbirhondesire n’oburhimanya, bulya ali w’ensiku n’amango, ntâco ankayûshûlirwa, na ntâco bankamunyaga, arhalagîrîri oku ihano lya ndi.
\v 22 Emikolo yâge yoshi erhahimwa bwinjà, kw’eri kula omuntu akalolêreza enkunyakunye.
\v 23 Ebyo byoshi ho bibà binali by’ensiku n’amango, na ngasi mango biyumva oku adesire.
\v 24 Ebiremwa byoshi bigenda bibirhi-bibirhi biyêrekerîne, ntâco ajizire cirhayûmânîni.
\v 25 Ngasi ciremwa ciyêrekîne obwinjà bw’ecindi, ndi wankarhama n’okusingiriza irenge lyâge?
\c 43
\s1 Izûba
\p 
\v 1 Okulîmba kw’amalunga, ecirêre cilangashane, ntyo kw’amalunga ga­ bonekana omu irenge\f + \fr 43, 1 \ft Izûba: lolà \xt Dan 3, 52\xt*\ft …: \xt Lul 19; 139\xt*\ft .\f* lyâgo.
\v 2 Izûba erhi lishoshôka sêzi linahamagaze: «Al’obwinjà bw’omukolo gw’Ow’Enyanyal»
\v 3 Erhi lijà omu nkuba-karhî, likaze igulu, ciru ndi wankalinda idûrhu lijira!
\v 4 Cibêye batwâna àbalonza idûrhu linji, izûba lyôhe linayôce entondo kasharhu kalushire; citumbûkemo ecîdûrhu cayôca, lirike emisholo yalyo, amasù gahune.
\v 5 Mushâna, Nyakasane waliremaga ali mukulu, na luderho lwâge luliyêreka enjira lyageramo buhena.
\s1 Omwêzi
\p 
\v 6 Omwêzi nago ngasi mango gwo na gulya, gwo gugaba emyêzi gutwe n’amango.
\v 7 Gwo gumanyîsa ensiku nkulu, cibà cimole cishubira eburhò, n’obwo carhenga ebukulu\f + \fr 43, 7 \ft kurhenga ebukulu: mwêzi gukula gurhôha.\f*.
\v 8 Mwêzi-cimole gurhengako omwêzi-nsiku, gunajè gwâkula-bugenda­ njira, cibà cimanyîso c’engabo z’e malunga, co cimolekera ecirêre oku nkuba.
\s1 Enyenyêzi
\p 
\v 9 Obumoleke bw’enyenyêzi bwo buyêrekana obwinjà bw’emalunga, zirhahimwa kuyinjihya amalunga ga Nyamuzinda.
\v 10 Oku Mwimâna adesire kwo zinahêka, zirhagosa omukolo gwâzo.
\s1 Omutirigongo
\p 
\v 11 Lolà omutirigongo, okuze Lulema, gurhahimwa bwinjà omu myambalo yagwo.
\v 12 Gubà muherho gw’irenge ly’emalunga, kuboko kwa Nyamuzinda kwa­gugokaga.
\s1 Obwinjà bw’ebiremwa
\p 
\v 13 Nyamuzinda oku bulonza bwâge ananiêse olubula, arhume n’emikemezo.
\v 14 Obone enfûnikire zâge zifûnuke, ebitù bibalale nka binyunyi.
\v 15 Oku buhashe bwâge, ebitù binanage, bihinduke mabuye.
\v 16 Oku buhashe bwâge, oku bulonza bwâge, empûsi y’ifô enahûse.
\v 17 Izù ly’omukungulo gwâge linajugumye idaho, kul’omusirûla guhubuka enyanya bo na kalemêra.
\v 18 Kul’orhunyunyi rhugwa oku idaho, kw’arhoza olubula, lugwe nka nzige. Amasù gasômerwe n’okuhona olwêru-lwêru, obukengêre burhangâle n’okulubona.
\v 19 Kandi, idaho alibulagirekwo oguli nka munyu, lumè lwanazire n’emboho, luhinduke rhushûgi-rhushûgi.
\v 20 Empûsi y’emboho y’enyanya yamahûsa, ebigakala byanamera oku mîshi, ngasi cidekêra ca mîshi cinajekwo ebigakala.
\v 21 Wampûsi anayabuke entondo, ahyajire empinga, asingônole ebyâsi nka muliro.
\v 22 Lêro obwo, ebitù nabyo birhinde nka bufumu, olumè lugalule obuzîne ecanda càmâhwa.
\v 23 Nyamuzinda, oku mulâli gwâge, ahima enyanja, n’omu nyanja amezamwo ebirhwa.
\v 24 Abagera omu nyanja banarhubwîre ebibamwo; emyanzi yâbo eri ya kurhusômeza:
\v 25 kutwa batwa oku isî, barhangâle: aha nsimba za ngasi lubero, aha mahirahira g’omu nyanja.
\v 26 Iragi, Nyamuzinda anabihêke bwinjà: na byoshi bishimbe oluderho lwâge.
\v 27 Erhi rhwankaganîra ebyo, bwanaca bunayîre; arhankaderhwa: «Ye byoshi».
\v 28 Mbwîraga aha emisî yarhenga y’okurnukuza? Bulya ye Shabukuru, e­nyanya lya byoshi,
\v 29 Nyakasane, Côbohwa Nnâmahanga, Obuhashe bwâge busômerîne.
\v 30 Mucîtakîrire Nyamuzinda nk’oku munahashire, arhankaderhwa. Mumukuze n’emisî yoshi, murharhamaga, bulya murhayûse.
\v 31 Ndi okol’omubwîne wankaderha oku ali? Ndi wakamukuza oku akwânîne?
\v 32 Amahwe gâge rhurhishi go manji kulusha ebyo; bulya ebi rhubona biri binyi omu mikolo yâge.
\v 33 Nyakasane ye walemaga byoshi, ye hà n’abantu bamurhînya oburhimanya bajira.
\c 44
\ms1 Irenge lya bashakulûza bemêzi
\p 
\v 1 Rhuderhage ogw’abajire irenge, bashakulûza\f + \fr 44, 1 \ft Abakulûkulù bîrhu: balarha, bashakulûza. \f* nk’oku banakulikirine.
\v 2 Nyamuzinda aluzize irenge, ayêrekana obukulu bwâge kurhenga e­nsiku za mîra.
\v 3 Omu balume, baguma bahâbwa obwâmi, banajà irenge erhi burhwâli bwâbo burhuma, abandi babà balenga omu kuhâna ihano, batwa emigani y’obulêbi.
\v 4 Abandi barhegeka olubaga n’amahano gâbo, n’obukengêre burhimanya omu lubaga, banayigîriza n’ebinwa by’oburhimanya.
\v 5 Abandi bashuba bazihi, bayandika n’ebinwa binunu.
\v 6 Abandi bahirhira oku birugu n’oku buhashe, balama n’omurhûla aha mwâbo.
\v 7 Boshi oku banali babà n’olukengwa, emw’abantu b’amango gâbo, bakuzibwa omu kalamo kâbo.
\v 8 Baguma muli bo basiga izîno, izîno liciderhwa n’obukenge kuhika ene,
\v 9 Abandi barhasigaga kashambala; bagenzire nk’abarhahali. Kwo bali nka kuno barhali en’igulu, kwo n’okwo iburha lyâbo enyuma zâbo.
\v 10 Ci lolaga abagâbo, aba aminjà gâbo garhayibagiragwa.
\v 11 Iburha lyâbo lyalanzire akashambala kâbo, omwîmo gwâbo guli mwîmo gwa bulume.
\v 12 Obûko bwâbo bukulikire amarhegeko, n’abâna bâbo omu njira yâbo barhaheze irenge lyâbo.
\v 13 iburha lyâbo lyâbâho ensiku zoshi, irenge lyâbo lirhakageramo citù,
\v 14 Emibiri yâbo yabishirwe n’omurhûla: izîno lyâbo liyôsire lizîne omu maburhwa.
\v 15 Ebihugo byaderha oburhimanya bwâbo, n’endêko emanyîse obukuze bwâbo.
\s1 Henoki
\p 
\v 16 Henoki asîmîsa Nyamuzinda, Nyamuzinda amuhêka, lwinganyo lw’okuhinduka kw’amâburhwa.
\s1 Nûhu
\p 
\v 17 Nûhu abonekana okunali muntu mushinganyanya, omu mango g’obukunizi, abà ye nyamerè: oku burhabâle bwâge, igulu lyayôrhana kasigwa\f + \fr 44, 17 \ft Kasigwa: mwâna îshe afîre amusiga omu izîmi erhi amusiga aciburhwa ntya: Nûhu n’omulala gwâge ali «kasigwa»; kwo kuderha owasigîre yêne abandi boshi bàmafà., lolà \xt Iz 4, 3\xt*\ft .\f*, amango ecihonzi camirîraga igulu.
\v 18 Muli ye, endagâno z’ensiku zoshi zajirwa,: mpu ly’abantu balekishubiholoka n’ecihûsi.
\s1 Abrahamu
\p 
\v 19 Abrahamu, shakulûza w’irenge w’amashanja mwandu, ntâye wahisire oku irenge lyâge.
\v 20 Akulikira irhegeko ly’Ow’Enyanya; àjira n’eciragâne haguma naye. Eco ciragâne acijira omu mubiri gwâge, n’erhi arhangulwa, abonekana oku anali mwemêzi.
\v 21 Co carhumire Nyamuzinda amulaganya n’ecihango, oku agisha amashanja goshi omu iburha lyâge, n’oku aluza obûko bwâge nka katulo k’oku idaho, analengereze iburha lyâge nka nyenyêzi z’emalunga, abahè ecihugo bayîmamwo, kurhenga oku nyanja kuhika oku yindi, kurhenga oku lwîshi kuhika ah’igulu lihekera.
\s1 Izaki na Yakôbo
\p 
\v 22 Kuli Izaki na Yakôbo, erhi îshe Abrahamu orhuma, Nyamuzinda ashub’ishâshula,
\v 23 omugisho gwâge oku bantu boshi muli Izaki, erhi îshe Abrahamu orhuma; adêkereza ecihango oku irhwe lya Yakôbo. Amuyîmika omu mugisho gwâge; amugabira n’ecihugo c’omwîmo, acitwâmwo mpande, acigabanyiza emilala oku enali iku­ mi n’ibiri.
\c 45
\s1 Mûsa
\p 
\v 1 Nyamuzinda arhôlamwo Yakôbo omuntu nkana, musimwa emwa boshi, murhonyi wâge n’ow’abantu, ye Mûsa, mukengêre-okengêrerwa-omugisho.
\v 2 Amuhà irenge liyumânîne n’ery’abatagatîfu, amuhà obuhashe bw’okujugumya abashombanyi.
\v 3 Oku cinwa ca Mûsa, Nyamuzinda ayimanza ebirhangâzo\f + \fr 45, 3 \ft Birhanâzo embere z’abâmi, lolà \xt Lub 8, 8; 9, 33\xt*\ft … oku irenge lyâge: lolà \xt Lub 19, 1; 33, 20\xt*\ft .\f*, amukuza e­mbêre z’abâmi, amuhà amarhegeko oku lubaga lwâge, abà nk’a­muyêreka oku irenge lyâge.
\v 4 Omu bwemêzi n’omu butûdu amuyinjihya, acîshoga-ye ekarhî k’abazîne boshi;
\v 5 amuyumvîsa izù lyâge, amuhêka omu bitù, amuhira embere zâge, amuhà amarhegeko, irhegeko lya kalamo n’obukengêre, ga kuyigîriza Yakôbo endagâno, ga kuyêreka Israheli enjira.
\s1 Aroni
\p 
\v 6 Azûsa Aroni, Mutagatîfu aka Mûsa, mwene wâbo, w’oku mulala gwa Levi.
\v 7 Afundika haguma naye endagâno y’ensiku zoshi, amuhà obudâhwa bw’olubaga. Amujira w’iragi omu myambalo yâge, amubwîka omwambalo gw’irenge\f + \fr 45, 7 \ft Mwambalo gw’irenge: Lolà \xt Lub 28\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 8 Amuhondakwo irenge linene, amuyarnbika ecinya-bugale, emyambalo y’omu ndalâlà, ecirondo c’oku nyanya n’omuroha.
\v 9 Emyambalo yâge ayihirakwo amashondo, n’enzege z’amasholo, nyinjà bwenêne eburharnbi n’obundi: oku agenda zajegera, baziyumve omu ka-Nyamuzinda, kantu olubaga lwakâmukengêrerakwo\f + \fr 45, 9 \ft Lwâkâmukngêrerakwo: kukengêra oku lebè ayôrhaga, oku ayambalaga.\f*.
\v 10 Amuyambika omwambalo gw’amasholo gw’ecirhînyiro, gwa mukara na mudukula, bushanja bwa mulenga; amuhà ecimanyîso c’ekagombe, Urimu na Tumimu\f + \fr 45, 10 \ft Urimu na Tumimu: lolà \xt Lub 28, 6; 1 Sam 14\xt*\ft .\f*, cidukula, kandi bushanja bwa mulenga.
\v 11 Amuhà olunigi lwinjinja lw’enjurna ziyandisirweko n’akali nka kashè, zinarhunzirwe -oku mugozi gw’amasholo, mukolo gwa murhunzi mulenga, mpu ebè nkumbu, haguma n’amandiko mabinje, nk’oku emilala y’Israheli enali.
\v 12 Amuhà ishungwè ly’amasholo mpu akâliyambalira oku citambara bunya-nsirha, baliyandisirekwo oku ali mwîshogwa wa Nyamuzinda, mandiko ga bulenga, mukolo mukornbêre: busîme oku masù eyo myambalo yoshi.
\v 13 Embere zâge barhalisâgibona ebyo bundi, na ntà mango ôw’embuga abiyambirhe: bâna bâge bône n’omulala gwâge ensiku zoshi.
\v 14 Enterekêro zâge z’okusingônoka lwoshi, kabiri omu lusiku amango goshi.
\v 15 Mûsa ye wamuyambikaga akashala k’omwîshogwa\f + \fr 45, 15 \ft Omwîshogwa: lolà \xt Lev 8, 1-13\xt*\ft ; Obukù: kantu kabaya bwinjà, marashi.\f*, anamushîga amavurha matagatîfu, Yâbà ndagâno y’ensiku n’amango kuli ye n’oku bûko bwâge amango amalunga ganacihabà, mpu akulire abarherekêzi, akole omukolo gw’obudâhwa, agishe n’olubaga oku izîno lya Nyakasane.
\v 16 Nyamuzinda acîshoga ye ekarhî k’abazîne boshi, mpu abè murherekêzi wa Nyakasane, atûmbûse enshangi n’obukù bw’akakengêro, arherekêre enterekêro y’olubôle\f + \fr 45, 16 \ft Kuzimiza, kufungira, kubwîra olubaga mpu luciyunjuze, lolà \xt Lev 16, 1\xt*\ft .\f* oku byâha by’olubaga.
\v 17 Amuhà amarhegeko gâge, amubwîra na kurhi gashimbwa, mpu ayigîrize Yakôbo eyo njira, anarnolekere Israheli omu biyêrekîre irhegeko lya Nyakasane.
\v 18 Ebigolo byanaciyisha, byamujira ihinzi\f + \fr 45, 18 \ft Ihinzi: ihano abantu bayumvinyemwo mpu bajire kulebe, kwinjà erhi kubî.\f*, bayâgalwa naye omu irungu, omurhwe gwa Datani na Abirami, n’ogwa Korè, ba bumvu na ba ntambala.
\v 19 Lêro Nyamuzinda ababona, akunira, obukunizi bwâge bwabahungumula. Abahirakwo ebirhangâzo, bahungumuka n’engulumira\f + \fr 45, 19 \ft Ngulumira: lolà \xt Mib 16, 1; 17, 15\xt*\ft .\f* y’omuliro gwâge.
\v 20 Ayûshûla irenge lya Aroni, omuhà omwanya, amushobôza okurhûlwa omwâka muhyâhya\f + \fr 45, 20 \ft Mirhangisârûlwa: busârûlle burhanzi, emyâka erhangiyêra, lolà \xt Mib 18, 12-13\xt*\ft .\f*, burhanzi omugati gwakayîgusa.
\v 21 Enterekêro Nyamuzinda arherekêrwa byo biryo balya, yêne wamuhâga eco cikono aha n’obûko bwâge\f + \fr 45, 21 \ft Obûko bwâge: lolà \xt Lub 29, 28\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 22 Ci omu cihugo arhajiramwo lyâge ishwa, arhajira gwâge mwanya omu lubaga, Nyamuzinda yêne ye mwanya gwâge.
\s1 Pinâsi
\p 
\v 23 Pinâsi naye, mwene Eleyazari, ye wa kasharhu oku irenge, bulya ayêrekîne obushiru bw’okurhînya Nyamuzinda, asimika n’obu­rhwàli embere z’olubaga n’obwo lwamâgoma\f + \fr 45, 23 \ft Lwamâgoma: lolà \xt Mib 25, 7\xt*\ft .\f*, Israheli ababalirwa erhi ye rhuma.
\v 24 Endagâno y’omurhûla yafundikwa naye, yamujira mukulu w’Ecirhinyiro ca Nyamuzinda n’ow’olubaga, na ntyo ye bo n’iburha lyâge, bàgwêrhe ecikono c’omudâhwa mukulu w’ensiku n’amango.
\v 25 Hàbîre endagâno haguma na Daudi, mwene Yese, w’oku mulala gwa Yûda, mwîmo gwa bwâmi; yêne omu bâna îshe aburha, ayambala akashambala. Aroni yêhe, akashambala kâge kali k’obûko bwâge bwoshi.
\v 26 Mâshi, Nyamuzinda ajire mubè barhimanya, murhegeke n’obushinganyanya olubaga lwâge, lyo amalume ga bashakulûza galek’ihera, lyo n’abâna bâbo bakaziyôrha bayambîrhe akashambala k’irenge lya bîshe.
\c 46
\s1 Yozwè
\p 
\v 1 Ali ntwâli omu matabâro\f + \fr 46, 1 \ft Matabâro: matumu, birha, kulwa. Izîno limukwânîne: Yozwè erhi Yezu; kwo kuderha: Nyamuzinda kuciza aciza: ye Muciza, Côkola.\f*, Yozwè, mwene Nûni, mukula wa Mûsa omu mukolo gw’okulêba, izîno lyanamukwânana, acîyêrekana mukulu wa kuciza abîshogwa, ahana abashombanyi bagoma, adêkereza Israheli omu cihugo câge.
\v 2 Nêci, yàli ntwâli, erhi wakamubwîne amaboko enyanya, engôrho omu nfune, ajirhêra ebishagala by’ababisha!
\v 3 Muntu ndi, embere zâge, wahisire aho oku burhwâli? Yêne àshokolera abalwî b’amatumu ga Nyamuzinda.
\v 4 Kali ye wabwîraga izûba mpu liyimange\f + \fr 46, 4 \ft Liyimange: lolà \xt Yoz 10, 13\xt*\ft .\f*: omulegerege muguma yâbà ibiri?
\v 5 Ashenga Nyamuzinda, erhi akol’aminisire abashombanyi hingolengole enyunda zoshi, Nyamuzinda ayumva omusengero gwâge, aniêsa enkuba y’olubula okurhasâgiboneka.
\v 6 Arhibukira oku ngabo y’abashombanyi, abaminikakwo akabayirhira oku mwandagalo: ayêreka amashanja oku amatumu gâge garhajîbwa omu irhwe, mpu lyo bamanya oku Nyamuzinda badwîrhe ba­lwîsa.
\s1 Kalebu ebushosi
\p 
\v 7 Bulya àli muntu wa Nyamuzinda, mîra, amango ga Mûsa, ayêrekana obushiru bw’omurhima nkana, bona Kalebu, mwene Yefunè, go mango bahagalikaga omwandu gw’abantu, bahanza olubaga okujira ecâha, bahulisa n’okucîduduma\f + \fr 46, 7 \ft Okucîduduma kubî: lolà \xt Mib 14, 6-10\xt*\ft .\f* kubî.
\v 8 Bombi bône barhahumagwakwo, ekarhî ka bihumbi magana ndarhu ga balwî, mpu bahike oku kashambala, omu cihugo cihuluza amarhà n’obûci.
\v 9 Nyamuzinda aha Kalebu emisî, n’eyo misî ayiyôrhana kuhika ebushosi, amusôsa oku ntondo ziri omu cihugo, ko kàbîre kashambala abâna bâge bayimiremo buno,
\v 10 mpu ly’Israheli yêshi abona oku nêci, kunali kwinjà okukulikira Nyamuzinda.
\s1 Abacîranuzi
\p 
\v 11 Abacîranuzi, ngasi muguma nk’oku anahamagîrwe, balya boshi baàrhagomaga murhima, barhacîhinduliraga Nyamuzinda, okubakengêra gubè mugisho.
\v 12 Amavuha gâbo gazibuhe ekuzimu, amazîno gâbo galame, abo bany’irenge bagashânize abâna bâbo.
\s1 Samweli
\p 
\v 13 Samweli\f + \fr 46, 13 \ft Samweli: lolà \xt 1 Sam 10, 1\xt*\ft … 16.13.\f* arhona bwenêne emwa Nyamuzinda, ashuba mulêbi wa Nyamuzinda, anayimânika obwâmi, ashîga abâmi b’ecihugo amavurha.
\v 14 Akâtwa emmanja z’endêko omu kukulikira amarhegeko ga Nyamuzinda, na ntyo Nyamuzinda abà haguma na Yakôbo.
\v 15 Omu bwemêzi bwâge, abonekana oku anali mulêbi, omu nderho zâge, acîmanyisa oku ye nyamuderha kubà.
\v 16 Ashenga Nyamuzinda Ogala-byoshi, amango abashombanyi balimu­ gosire enyunda zoshi, arherekêra omwâna-buzi orhalikwo izâbyo.
\v 17 Nyamuzinda, kurhenga emalunga, avuza omukungulo, enkuba yàkungula, izù lyâge lyayumvîkana;
\v 18 àhungumula abakulu b’abashombanyi b’Efilistea, n’Abanya-Tiri.
\v 19 Samweli, embere aluhûke ensiku n’amango, acîgasha emunda Nyamuzinda na mwâmi bali, erhi: «Niono ntà muntu nalenganyize oku hyâge; ciru enkwêrho y’emigozi yo nyi». Na ntâye wamuhêsire lubanja.
\v 20 Abîre amâfà abulirêba, abwîra mwâmi oku obwâmi bwâge bwahwîre; izù lyâge lyarhenga ekuzimu; lyalêba kwa kuzâza obubî bw’olubaga.
\c 47
\s1 Natani
\p 
\v 1 Hâyisha Natani enyuma lya Samweli, alêba oku ngoma ya Daudi.
\s1 Daudi
\p 
\v 2 Kula bananûla amashushi oku cimasha c’enterekêro y’okuvuga omunkwa, kwo Daudi acîshozirwe ekarhî ka bene-Israheli.
\v 3 Ashâsa empangaza kula bashâsa omwâna-hene, eciryanyi kula bajira omwâna-buzi.
\v 4 K’arhabâga aciri murhò ayîrha n’entwâli, akûla ecihugo nshonyi: ahè­ba ehibuye oku muzâreti, ahibanda hyanakoza, atwa Goliyati ifêka?
\v 5 Aho erhi amâshenga Nyamuzinda w’Enyanya, naye Nyamuzinda amuhà emisî y’okuyîrha omulwî mukulu, n’okuzûsa ihembe lya Israheli\f + \fr 47, 5 \fk Israheli\ft : lolà \xt 1 Sam 17\xt*\ft . \f*.
\v 6 Okwo kwarhuma bamuhà irenge lya bihumbi ikumi\f + \fr 47, 6 \fq Bihumbi ikumi, \ft lolà \xt 1 Sam 18, 7\xt*\ft .\f*, bàmukuza omu mugisho gwa Nyamuzinda, bàmuyambika akashala k’irenge.
\v 7 Ashâbira abashombanyi bali eburhambi, aherêrekeza abashombanyi b’e Filisteya, àbalambika burhazûka.
\v 8 Omu mikolo yâge yoshi, akuza Omwimâna w’Enyanya n’ebinwa by’irenge\f + \fr 47, 8 \ft Binwa by’irenge: Nnanga za Daudi, lolà \xt 2 Sam 23, 1\xt*\ft .\f*; acîtakîraye n’omurhima gwoshi, ayêrekana oku azigira Lulema.
\v 9 Ahira ennanga aha luhêro, omulya gwâzo gwakazirhuma izùu ly’abazihi lyayinjiha okurhalusire.
\v 10 Ayinjihya ensiku nkulu, zalangashana okulushîne, Obwimâna bw’Izîno lya Nyamuzinda bwakuzibwa, ecirhînyiro\f + \fr 47, 10 \ft Cirhînyiro: hantu harhînywa, ha lukengwa, aha luhêrero.\f* ca Nyamuzinda cakazidumûka kurhenga sêzi.
\v 11 Nyamuzinda àmubabalira ebyâha byâge\f + \fr 47, 11 \ft Ebyâha byâge: lolà \xt 2 Sam 12, 13.24\xt*\ft , ensiku n’amango, amujirira endagâno y’obwâmi, amuhà entebe y’irenge omu Israheli.\f*, àlengereza obuhashe bwâge ensiku zoshi, amuhà endagâno y’obwami, entebe y’irenge omu Israheli.
\s1 Salomoni
\p 
\v 12 Salomoni, mwene Daudi, muntu mwîrhonzi, ayîma omu by’îshe; n’oku burhabâle bw’îshe alama omu iragi.
\v 13 Salomoni arhegeka ecihugo omu mango g’omurhûla, Nyamuzinda àmuhira omurhûla eburhambi n’obundi, mpu ly’ayûbakira Izîno lyâge enyumpa, anarheganye ecirhînyiro c’ensiku n’amango.
\v 14 Nêci, wali murhimanya omu busole bwâwe, wali wa bukengêre bunji nka mîshi!
\v 15 Obukengêre bwâwe bwahundikire igulu, waliyunjuza migani mizibu.
\v 16 Irenge lyâwe lyahika emahanga, wazigirwa omu murhûla gwâwe.
\v 17 Ennanga, emigani, obulenga omu binwa n’amashuzo gâwe byasômeza igulu.
\v 18 Oku izîno lya Nyakasane Nyamuzinda, ye Nyamuzinda rhuderha w’Israheli, walundika amasholo nka byûma, n’ensaranga zakulugira nka mabuye\f + \fr 47, 18 \ft Nka mabuye: obugale bwa Salomoni bwàli bunji bwenêne: lolà \xt 1 Sam 10, 11\xt*\ft …; \xt Mat 6, 29\xt*\ft . 47, 19: Mujà w’amagene gâwe: lolà \xt 1 Bâm 11, 1-13\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 19 Ci aye! mubiri gwâwe wagurhega abakazi, wacîjira mujà w’amagene gâwe.
\v 20 Ntyo wadôkôza irenge lyâwe, wahira ihanja oku bûko bwâwe, wa­rhuma obukunizi bwacîhonda oku bâna bâwe n’omutula oku iburha lyâwe:
\v 21 amâmimâmi gazûka, Efrayimu azûkamwo obugoma.
\v 22 Ci kwône Nyamuzinda arhayibagiraga obwonjo bwâge, arhatwâga omu kanwa kâge, arhayimaga omwîshogwa wâge iburha, arhaherêrekezagya obûko bw’owalimuzigîre. Ntyo àlekera Yakôbo hikasigwa, na Daudi omuzî gwa kuli ye.
\s1 Roboami
\p 
\v 23 Salomoni ajirhamûka haguma na bîshe, asiga ow’oku mulala gwâge, musirhe bwenêne ekarhî k’olubaga, muntu orhagwêrhi bukengêre buci: ye Roboami, ye wasunikaga ecihugo omu bugoma.
\s1 Yerobwâmi
\p 
\v 24 Yerobwâmi mwene Nebati naye, ajirîsa Israheli ecâha, ayigîriza Efrayimu enjira y’amabî. Kurhenga ago mango, ebyâha byâbo byalugîrira, byarhuma balulizibwa kulî n’ecihugo câbo.
\v 25 Bali bacihêsire omu bibî bya ngasi lubero, byarhuma bahâbwa obuhane.
\c 48
\s1 Eliya
\p 
\v 1 Lêro omulêbi Eliya anacizûka nka muliro, ebinwa byâge bwakâyôca nka ngoke.
\v 2 Ye wabahamagaliraga ecizombo, n’omu bushiru bwâge, abahungumula.
\v 3 Oku luderho lwa Nyamuzinda, àhangamya enkuba, kasharhu koshi àmanula omuliro emalunga.
\v 4 Eliya nêci wali ojire irenge omu birhangâzo byâwe! ndi muntu wa­nkaba n’obucîbone bw’okucîgerera kuli we?
\v 5 We wakûlaga omuntu omu nfune z’olufù, wamurhenza ekuzimu, oku luderho lw’Ow’Enyanya.
\v 6 We washabiraga abâmi, abakulu wabarhenza oku ntebe.
\v 7 We wayumvagya obukali oku Sînayi, n’irhegeko ly’olwihôlo oku Horebu,
\v 8 washîga abâmi b’okucîhôla amavurha, washîga n’abakûla bâwe amavurha g’obulêbi,
\v 9 wahêkwa muli kalemêra w’omuliro\f + \fr 48, 9 \ft By’omuliro: lolà \xt 1 Bâm 2, 1-11\xt*\ft .\f*, oku ngâlè, y’ebihêsi by’omuliro,
\v 10 we wacishogeragwa obukali bwayisha, mpu obè murhûliriza w’obukù­nizi embere buyishe, mpu oshubize omurhima gw’îshe w’omwâna oku mwâna\f + \fr 48, 10 \ft Oku mwâna: lolà \xt Mal 3, 24\xt*\ft .\f*, onayinamule emilala ya Yakôbo.
\v 11 Iragi lyabayishikubona, n’abafânîne obuzigire, bulya nîrhu rhwayish’ibà n’obuzîne.
\s1 Elishaʿ
\p 
\v 12 Ntyo kwo Eliya ali, ye muntu wahekagwa muli kalemêra. Omûka gwâge gwayunjuza Elishaʿ; omu nsiku z’akalamo kâge, ntà murhegesi wakamuyâshire, ntâye wakamugombize.
\v 13 Ntâco camuyabiraga, ciru abîre ali n’ekuzimu omubiri gwâge gwagalilêba!\f + \fr 48, 13 \ft Ali n’ekuzimu: lolà \xt 1 Bâm 13, 20-21\xt*\ft , kandi rhwanaderha nti: «owalêbaga ciru ali n’ekuzimu».\f*
\v 14 Amango àli azîne ajira ebirhangâzo, anabire amâfa ajira n’ebisômerîne.
\s1 Obugoma n’obuhane
\p 
\v 15 Byâbà ntyo, ci omurhima gw’olubaga gurhagalukaga, basera oku byâha byâbo, balinda balulizibwa kuli n’ecihugo câbo, bàbasha­ndabanya omu igulu lyoshi.
\v 16 Hasigala amâhûngà g’olwali lubaga, n’omurhambo w’oku mulala gwa Daudi. Muli bo, baguma baguma basîmîsa Nyamuzinda, ci abandi bashubikaluza ebyâha.
\s1 Hezekiyahu
\p 
\v 17 Hezekiyahu azibuhya ecishagala, ahisa amîshi omu lugo lwâge, arhula ibuye n’ecûma, ayûbaka iriba ly’amîshi.
\v 18 Mw’ago mango, Senakeribu amera omu muherho, arhuma Rabushakè, naye Rabushakè omu bucîbone bwâge, arhêra Siyoni.
\v 19 Lêro bajuguma amaboko n’omurhima, balumwa nka mukazi wajà aha lubako\f + \fr 48, 19 \ft Aha lubako: okujà aha lubako kuli kuhûrha. \f*,
\v 20 bayâkûza Nyamuzinda w’obwonjo, bamurhega amaboko, Omwimâna abayumva kurhenga empingu, abaciza n’okuboko kwa Yesha’yahu.
\v 21 alasa ebihando by’ab’e Sîriya, malahika wâge abahungumula.
\s1 Yeshayahu
\p 
\v 22 Byabà ntyo bulya Hezekiyahu amâsîmîsa Nyamuzinda, acîyêrekana muzibu omu kukulikira enjira y’îshe Daudi, nk’oku omulêbi Yesha’yahu ali amurhegesire, Yesha’yahu mukulu na mutabêsha omu bulêbi bwâge.
\v 23 Omu nsiku zâge, iziûba lyàgenda cinyumanyumà, n’akalamo ka mwâmi\f + \fr 48, 23 \ft Akalamo ka Mwâmi kayûshûka: lolà \xt 1 Bâm 20, 4-11; Iz 38, 4-8\xt*\ft .\f* kayûshûka.
\v 24 Abonera omu buhashe bwa Mûka oku ensiku zahwire, arhûliriza abagogomîrwe b’e Siyoni,
\v 25 amanyîsa ebyâyisha binaciri kuli omu mwizimya gw’ensiku n’amango, n’ebifulike abimanyîsa embere bibonekane.
\c 49
\s1 Yoshiyahu na Yeremiya
\p 
\v 1 Yoshiyahu okumukengêra kuli nka kujira envangè nyinjà y’obubâni kula omuvanzi w’amarâshi anajira; buli nka bûci bwo bununa omu ngasi kanwa, nka lulanga lwazihwa omu idinye.
\v 2 Aj’aho, Yoshiyahu, akulikira enjira nyinjà, erya y’okugalula omurhima gw’olubaga, arhenza obugalugalu bulya bukakabulirwa;
\v 3 omurhima gwâge aguyêrekeza Nyamuzinda, n’omu mango g’amabî, a­lwîsa anahimira obukunda-Lulema.
\s1 Abâmi n’abalêbi bazinda
\p 
\v 4 Kuleka ba Daudi, Hezekiyahu, na Yoshiyahu, abandi boshi baluza obugoma, bajahika irhegeko ly’Ow’Enyanya: abâmi b’e Yudeya bahwa.
\v 5 Obuzibu bwâbo erhi babulekîre abandi, irenge lyâbo erhi balirekîre ecihugo c’emahanga.
\v 6 Ecishagala citagatîfu cîshogwa, abashombanyi baciyôca, emihanda ya­co bayihambya,
\v 7 Kulya Yeremiya anaderhaga. Bâli bamulibuzize n’obwo ali mulêbi mwîshogwa kurhenga omu nda ya nina, mpu akundule, ashâbe analambike, ci kwône kandi mpu ayûbake anarhwere\f + \fr 49, 7 \ft Anarhwera: lolà \xt Yer 1, 10\xt*\ft . \f*.
\v 8 Ezekiyeli abonekerwa n’irenge, Nyamuzinda amuyerekalyo oku nyanya ly’engâlè ya Bakerubi\f + \fr 49, 8 \ft Bakerubi: lolà \xt Eze 1—3; 9—10\xt*\ft .\f*.
\v 9 akengêra abashombanyi omu nkuba y’ecihonzi, mpu lyo ahimira abakulikira enjira nyinjà.
\v 10 Balya balêbi ikumi na babiri nabo, amavuha gâbo gashabuke nka mburho omu nshinda zâbo, bulya barhûlirîze Yakôbo, bamuciza omu buyêmêre n’omu bulangâlire.
\s1 Zorobabeli na Yozwè
\p 
\v 11 Kurhi rhwacitakirira Zorobabeli? Kw’ali nka kashè omu kuboko ku­lyo\f + \fr 49, 11 \ft Kulyo: okuboko kulyo habà hantu ha bukenge, muntu mukengwa bahira ekulyo.\f*;
\v 12 naye owâbo Yozwè, mwene Yosedeki, bombi, omu mango gâbo. bayûbaka aka-Nyamuzinda, bayabulira Nyamuzinda olubaga lutagatîfu, lubaga lubîkîrwe irenge ly’ensiku n’amango.
\s1 Nehemiya
\p 
\v 13 Nehemiya naye ali mukulu w’okukengêrwa, ye warhuzûkizagya enkûta zàli zamâhongoka, ajira enyumvi anazisimbanya, ayînamula eka.
\s1 Okushubûlula
\p 
\v 14 Ntâye en’igulu walemirwe mpu ayumânane na Enoki; ye bàbalalanaga kurhenga igulu.
\v 15 Ntâye kandi wabusirwe oli nka Yozefu, arhona emwa bakulu bâge, abà nyamwegemerwa w’olubaga lwâge, amavuha gâge gajirekwo omugisho.
\v 16 Semu na Seti nabo bajire irenge omu bantu, ci kwône Adamu yenaciri enyanya lya ngasi ciremwa cizîne.
\c 50
\s1 Omudâhwa Simoni
\p 
\v 1 Omudâhwa mukulu, Simoni, mwene Oniasi, ye washakalaga aka-Nyamuzinda, amango acihali, azibuhya n’ecirhînyiro.
\v 2 Ye wabandaga eciriba c’okuyûbaka banyamwegemerwa babirhi omu bulîrî bw’aka-Nyamuzinda.
\v 3 Amango gâge lyo bahumbaga ecibîkiro c’amîshi, bahumba ecîna cigali bwenêne nka nyanja.
\v 4 Ayûbaka buzibu olugo, mpu ly’acingira bwinjà olubaga amango lurhênzire.
\v 5 Arhàhimagwa kukwânana ekarhî k’olubaga, erhi abâga ahuluka arhenga ebwa lusîka,
\v 6 nka nyenyêzi y’esêzi omu bitù, nka mwêzi mukulu\f + \fr 50, 6 \ft Cirhêbo ca mwêzi: gala mango omwêzi gukola mukulu, gukola guyunjwîre, muburungusè, nka cirhêbo c’aha ngombe.\f*,
\v 7 nka myonzi y’izûba oku nyanya ly’aka-Nyamuzinda kw’Ow’Enyanya, nka mutirigongo gwalangashana omu bitù by’irenge,
\v 8 nka bwâso bwa rôza omu mpondo, nka bwâso bwa lisi emezire hôfi n’iriba, nk’ihaji lya murhi gwa kasuku omu canda,
\v 9 nka muliro n’obubâni omu cetêzo, nka kabindi ka masholo, katâke n’ensobeke y’ensobeke y’enjuma za ngasi lubero,
\v 10 nka muzêti gujagalîre malehe, nka murhi gwa nsindani guhisire omu nkuba karhî.
\v 11 Oku akazâgikwânanwa erhi abâga ayambalîre olusiku lukulu, arhôle n’emyambalo y’obukulu, erhi abâga akola ayinamukira aha luhêrero lutagatîfu, amanabumba obululi bw’aka-Nyamuzinda bwoshi irenge!
\v 12 Alà oku ayinjihaga erhi abâga akola ayankirira eby’enterekêro omu maboko g’abadâhwa, erhi abâga ayîmanzire yêne ebwa karhî k’oluhêrero, na bene wâbo bamuzungulusire eburhambi buna-cimanè! onabone ayôsire nka nduluma y’e Libano n’amashami gâyo, nka kula omubô gubà guzonzirwe n’amashami gâgwo.
\v 13 Alà oku ayinjihaga amango bene Aroni boshi omu irenge lyâbo babâga bafumbîrhe entûlo za Nyakasane, baligi embere z’endêko ya bene Israheli,
\v 14 naye yêne adwîrhage arherekêra aha Luhêrero, analiko ashumbiriza n’obukenge Ow’Enyanya entûlo z’obukulu
\v 15 Obone alambûlîre okuboko oku kabehe, ayanke ntonyi nsungunu za murhobo gwa muzâbîbu, azibulagire aha burhambi bw’oluhêrero, hazûke ehisûnunu hy’okusîmîsa Ow’Enyanya, Nnâmahanga goshi.
\v 16 Ago mango lyo bene Aroni bakazâgibanda orhuhababo, babûhe emishekera yâbo minene y’amarhale, izù lishakânye, mpu kabè kakengêzo emw’Ow’Enyanya.
\v 17 Erhi bahikaga aho, onabone olubaga lwoshi, luhwere oku idaho caligumiza, luharâmye Nyakasane Ogala byoshi, Nyamubâho w’Enyanya bwenêne.
\v 18 Abimbiza nabo bayankirire, bayimbe obukuze, ogwo mulenge gwoshi gwakazishuba lwimbo lwinjinja.
\v 19 Olubaga lusengerage Nyamuzinda w’Enyanya obwo, lushenge Nyakasane k’emirenge, kuhika ogwo mukolo gw’okurhumikira Nyamuzinda guhwe.
\v 20 Enyuma ly’aho, onabone ayandagale, alambûlire endêko y’olubaga lw’Israheli kw’amaboko, n’izù linene, abahè omugisho gwa Nyamuzinda, erhi anagwêrhe irenge ly’obuhashe bw’okuderha eryol’izîno.
\v 21 Aho, bukolaga bwa kabiri obwo, olubaga lwanafukama luyankirire omugisho gw’Ow’Enyanya.
\s1 Musêze omurhima
\p 
\v 22 Na bunôla, kuzagi Nyamuzinda Nnâmahanga, yejira ebinja n’ebinênênè ngasi hoshi, ye walengezagya ensiku zîrhu kurhenga omu nda za banyâma, arhujirira nk’oku obwonjo bwâge bunali.
\v 23 Arhuhâge n’omurhima gushagalusire, arhushobôze omurhûla mwa zino nsiku zîrhu, gugandâze omu Israheli ensiku n’amango.
\v 24 Inêma lyâge liyôrhe libà haguma nîrhu, anarhulîkûze mwa gano mango.
\s1 Omugani
\p 
\v 25 Hali mashanja abiri ntabonakwo, erya kasharhu lirhali ishanja:
\v 26 abantu b’entondo y’e Samâriya, Abafilistini, n’olubaga lw’abahwinja b’e Sikemi.
\s1 Enfundika-binwa
\p 
\v 27 Nyigîrizo za burhimanya n’obumanye ezîra Yezu, Mwene-Sira, Eleyazari w’e Yeruzalemu, asiribire mw’eci citabu, adubuliramo oburhimanya bw’omurhima gwâge, nka kul’enkuba enadubuka.
\v 28 Iragi lyâge omuntu ogwêrhe amango g’okucîyigîriza, anabone oburhimanya n’okubuheba e murhima.
\v 29 Akahêka ntyo, âbà ali muzibu ngasi mango, bulya akamole ka Nyamuzinda yo njira yâge.
\c 51
\s1 Okucîtakîra kw’omunkwa
\p 
\v 1 Nkola nilkuvuga omunkwa, Yâgirwa Mwâmi, nakukuza, Nyamuzinda, Muciza wâni,
\v 2 Wàndwirîre, wanfungira, wandîkûza omu mîno ga nyamulûmbà, wantenza omu murhego gw’olulimi lubî, wankûla ekanwa k’abanywesi; wanyimangira embere z’abangosire, wanciza,
\v 3 omu lukogo lwâwe lunji n’oku bukuze bw’izîno lyâwe, wandîkûza omu kanwa k’abayashamire mpu bandye, wantenza omu maboko g’abanshimbire mpu banyîrhe, omu malibuko goshi nabwîne,
\v 4 wankûla ecîko nnankola ndi buhuba, wankûla omu muliro muhangala!
\v 5 wandîkûza oku lulimi lw’obulyâlya, n’oku nderho z’obunywesi.
\v 6 - kalimi ka balenzi omu bwâmi.- Nashugunuka olufù, omûka gwâni gwagalukira aha nshinda-burhambi.
\v 7 Bangorha nieshi, nabula n’ecirhabîre; nalola eyi n’eyi nti nkaba nabo­na owîrhu wantabâla, namubula.
\v 8 Ka lêro ntakengera obwonjo bwâwe, Nyakasane k’emirenge, emikolo yâwe ya kurhenga ensiku n’amango, nakengêra oku we ciza abakulangâlira, obakûle omu maboko g’abashombanyi.
\v 9 Omusengero gwâni gwayînamukira emund’oli, nashenga nti ondîkûze omu lufù.
\v 10 Nashenga Nyakasane, îshe wa Nnâhamwîrhu, nti: «Orhantibe omu nsiku z’amalibuko, omu nsiku z’abacîbonyi n’abalenzi. Nâkuza izîno lyâwe ngasi mango, nâcîtakîriralyo, mvuge omunkwa».
\v 11 Omusengero gwâni gwayankirirwa, wantenza ekuzimu, wandîkûza oku mango g’obubî.
\v 12 Co cirhumire nacîtakîra, nkuvuge omunkwa, nkuze izîno lya Nyakasane.
\s1 Olulanga lw’oburhimanya
\p 
\v 13 Omu busole bwâni, erhi nabaga nabalama, nantangishenga, nsengere n’obwâlagale oburhimanya.
\v 14 Nabusengerera aha lusò lw’ecirhînyiro: na kuhika olusiku lwâni luzinda erhi bwo nankulikire.
\v 15 Amango bwàli buyâsize, nka muzâbîbu guyanyire, omurhima gwâni gwabusîma. Amagulu gâni gajà omu njira ekubûsire, kurhenga ebusole bwâni erhi burhimanya nnongereza.
\v 16 Naburhega okurhwiri, nanabuhâbwa, nahika oku nyigîrizo nyinji.
\v 17 Nagenda bwinjà bwo burhumire, nakuza owampaga oburhimanya.
\v 18 Bulya narhôzire omuhigo gw’okubukulikira, nalongereza n’obushiru enjira y’aminjà, ntà mango nâbulabule.
\v 19 Iroho lyâni lyabulwira, nacîsêza okushimba irhegeko, nayinamulira amaboko enyanya, nahuna obwonjo oku buhwinja bwâni.
\v 20 Omurhima gwâni gwayerekera emunda buli, nabushimâna n’omurhima gucîre; bw’obûla nkulikîre kurhenga emurhondêro, co ca­rhuma ntasigala omu marhabi,
\v 21 Nayekemba enda erhi bwo burhuma, nabushimâna, narhimâna ebinja.
\v 22 Nyamuzinda ampîre, ampà engalo y’olulimi lw’okumukuza,
\v 23 Muyishe emunda ndi, mwe bahwinja, mujè omu masomo gâni.
\v 24 Cirhumire mucijira bakenyi, n’obwo enyôrha y’oburhimanya emugwêrhe?
\v 25 Nabumbwîre akanwa nti nderhe: gulagi, burhafà nsaranga\f + \fr 51, 25 \fq Burhafà nsaranga\ft : lolà \xt Iz 55, 1; Mig 4, 5-7\xt*\ft .\f*,
\v 26 mugombe ecikanyi ah’idako ly’omurhamba, muyigîrizibwe, enyigîrizo hôfi hôfi ninyu ziri.
\v 27 Ninyu mwene mucîbonere: mubwîne okuntarhamaga bwenêne, nabul’ibona obuluhûkiro bw’enkwîra.
\v 28 Muhâne birugu binji oku nyigîrizo, zammuhisa oku mwandu gw’amasholo.
\v 29 Omurhima gwinyu, gurhimûkwe n’olukogo lwa Nyakasane, murhabâga nshonyi z’okumukuza.
\v 30 Mujire omukolo gwinyu oku amango garhacihika, olusiku hano luyisha, ammuhà. oluhembo lwinyu. Nyakasane akuzibwe emyâka yoshi, n’izîno lyâge liyimbwe kurhenga oku iburha kujà oku lindi iburha.
\p Omunwe muzinda: Burhimanya bwa Yezu! Mwene-Sira.
